INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020063659', '哈利·波特与死亡圣器', 'images/哈利·波特与死亡圣器.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '魔幻', '49.5', '66', '<p>《哈利·波特与死亡圣器》是“哈利·波特”系列的第七部，也就是最后一部。</p><p>还有四天，哈利就要迎来自己十七岁的生日，成为一名真正的魔法师。然而，他不得不提前离开女贞路4号，永远离开这个他曾经生活过十六年的地方。</p><p>凤凰社的成员精心谋划了秘密转移哈利的计划，以防哈利遭到伏地魔及其追随者食死徒的袭击。然而，可怕的意外还是发生了……</p><p>与此同时，卷土重来的伏地魔已经染指霍格沃茨魔法学校，占领了魔法部，控制了半个魔法界，形势急转直下……</p><p>哈利在罗恩、赫敏的陪伴下，不得不逃亡在外，隐形遁迹。为了完成校长邓布利多的遗命，一直在暗中寻机销毁伏地魔魂器的哈利，意外地获悉如果他们能够</p><p>拥有传说中的三件死亡圣器，伏地魔将必死无疑。但是，伏地魔也早已开始了寻找死亡圣器的行动，并派出众多食死徒，布下天罗地网追捕哈利……</p><p>哈利与伏地魔在魔法学校的禁林中遭遇了，哈利倒在伏地魔抢先到手的一件致命的圣器之下……</p><p>然而，伏地魔未能如愿以偿，死亡圣器不可能战胜纯正的灵魂。哈利赢得了这场殊死较量的最终胜利……</p>', '<p> \"harry potter and the deathly hallows is the seventh of\" harry potter \"series, which is the last one. </p> <p> there are four days, harry will celebrate her seventeenth birthday, to become a real magician. However, he had to leave early no 4 privet drive, never leave this he had lived 16 years. </p> <p> a member of the order of the phoenix of orchestrating the secret transfer of harry\'s plan, in case of harry attacks by death eaters of voldemort and his followers. However, the terrible accident or have taken place in... </p> <p> at the same time, the return of Lord voldemort has already enter hogwarts school of witchcraft and wizardry, occupied the ministry of magic, control half the wizarding world, the situation turned down... </p> <p> in the company of RON, hermione, harry had to be a fugitive, still invisible. In order to complete the headmaster dumbledore\'s testament, have been in the dark, looking to destroy voldemort horcrux harry was surprised to learn that if they can </p> <p> with the three deathly hallows of legend, voldemort will die. However, voldemort has already started looking for deathly hallows action, and sent many death eaters, networks chase harry... </p> <p> harry and voldemort in the forbidden forest magic school, harry fell in voldemort\'s first hand a deadly hallows under... </p> <p> however, voldemort has not been able to get it, deathly hallows cannot defeat a pure soul. Harry won the final victory and bloody... </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020026906', '白鹿原', 'images/白鹿原.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>这是一部渭河平原五十年变迁的雄奇史诗，一轴中国农村班斓多彩、触目惊心的长幅画卷。主人公六娶六丧，神秘的序曲预示着不祥。一个家族两代子孙，为争夺白鹿原的统治代代争斗不已，上演了一幕幕惊心动魄的活剧：巧取风水地，恶施美人计，孝子为匪，亲翁杀媳，兄弟相煎，情人反目……大革命、日寇入侵、三年内战，白鹿原翻云覆雨，王旗变幻，家仇国恨交错缠结，冤冤相报代代不已……古老的土地在新生的阵痛中颤栗。厚重深邃的思想内容，复杂多变的人物性格，跌宕曲折的故事情节，绚丽多彩的风土人情，形成作品鲜明的艺术特色和令人震撼的真实感。</p>', '< p > this is a change of the grand epic, a shaft for colorful, China\'s rural class alarming picture. The prelude of the protagonist six marry bereavement, mysterious portend ominous. A family of two generations, the fight for the rule of white deer from fighting, staged scenes thrilling whole: taking feng shui, evil honey trap, son for bandits, weng kill daughter-in-law, turned, brothers, in such a lover... Revolution, Japanese invasion, three years of civil war, white deer adultery; Wang Qi fluctuates, the family business countries hate crisscross tangles, handed down by revenge... Ancient land in the throes of new thriller. Thick deep ideological content, complicated and changeable characters, dramatic twists and turns of the plot, colorful folk customs, form the distinctive artistic features and stunning sense of reality. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506309745', '苏菲的世界', 'images/苏菲的世界.jpg', '作家出版社', '文学', '20.1', '26.8', '<p>《苏菲的世界》是讲14岁的少女苏菲某天放学回家，发现了神秘的一封信。—你是谁？—世界从哪里来？就这样，在某个神秘导师的指引下，苏菲开始思索，从古希腊到康德、从祁克果到佛洛佛德等各位大师所思考的根本问题。与此同时，苏菲不断接到一些极不寻常的来信，世界像谜团一般在她眼底展开。苏菲运用少女天生的悟性与后天知识，企图解开这些谜团，然而，事实真相远比她所想的更怪异、更离奇……</p><p>《苏菲的世界》，即是智慧的世界，梦的世界。</p><p>它将会唤醒每个人内心深处对生命的赞叹</p><p>与对人生终极意义的关怀和好奇。</p>', '< p > \"Sophie\'s world\" was about 14 years old girl Sophie came home from school one day and found a mysterious letter. - who are you? - the world come from? In this way, in some mysterious mentor, under the guidance of Sophie began to think about, from ancient Greece to Kant, from kierkegaard to los bathing Buddha you master the fundamental problem thinking. At the same time, Sophie constantly hear from some of the unusual, the world like a mystery in her eyes. Sophie girl born savvy and nurture knowledge, attempt to unravel the mystery, however, the truth is far more than what she thought strange, stranger... < / p > < p > \"Sophie\'s world\", is the wisdom of the world, the dream world. < / p > < p > it will awaken everyone heart to the praise of life < / p > < p > with the ultimate meaning of life care and curiosity. < / p >', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787539982830', '无声告白', 'images/无声告白.jpg', '江苏凤凰文艺出版社', '文学', '26.25', '35', '<p>我们终此一生，就是要摆脱他人的期待，找到真正的自己。</p><p>——————————</p><p>莉迪亚死了，可他们还不知道。</p><p>莉迪亚是家中老二，李先生和李太太的掌上明珠，她遗传了母亲的蓝眼睛和父亲的黑头发。父母深信，莉迪亚一定能实现他们无法实现的梦想。莉迪亚的尸体被发现后，她的父亲内疚不已，母亲则一心报复。莉迪亚的哥哥觉得，隔壁的坏小子铁定脱不了关系，只有莉迪亚的妹妹看得一清二楚，而且，她很可能是唯一知道真相的人……</p><p>——————————</p><p>关于爱与失去，以及我从未告诉你的秘密</p>', '< p > we all the life, is to get rid of others\' expectations, find the real you. < / p > < p > -- -- -- -- -- < / p > < p > Lydia is dead, but they also don\'t know. < / p > < p > Lydia is second in the home, Mr Li and Mrs Li\'s eye, she inherited her mother\'s blue eyes and his father\'s black hair. Parents are convinced that Lydia can achieve their dreams of cannot be achieved. Lydia\'s body was found after, her father by guilt, mother bent on revenge. Lydia brother think, will be about the relationship between the bad boy next door, see clearly only Lydia\'s sister, and she is likely to be the only one who knows the truth... < / p > < p > -- -- -- -- -- < / p > < p > about love and loss, and I never tell you a secret < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108017444', '向左走·向右走', 'images/向左走·向右走.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '文学', '12', '16', '<p>“她习惯向左走，他习惯向右走，他们始终不曾相遇。”《向左走·向右走》是几米首次表现男女感情的长篇图文创作。男女主角彼此在生活中的巧妙关系，构成了整个故事的设计。在页面的衔接上，有许多的巧思安排，在线条与上色上，作了更细致的处理，手法俐落有变化，是几米相当成熟的作品，也是代表作之一。</p><p>幾米表示，这本书的创作灵感始于某一天被隔壁的电钻声吵得无法画画，只好开始发呆，然后天马行空地胡思乱想。突然觉得从不知道我家隔壁住的人是谁，可是每天跟他或她只隔一道薄薄的墙而睡。如果我们在外面偶然相遇，若我们从不曾提及彼此的住处，那么也许我们不会再相逢，也永远不知道其实我们就住在隔壁。</p>', '< p > \"left her habit, he is used to move right, they never meet.\" \"Left right\" is the first time a few meters men\'s and women\'s feelings of graphic creation. Men and women leading role relationship between each other in life is clever, the design of the story. On the cohesion of the page, there are many think of opportunely, on the line and color, made a more detailed processing, almost have change, is a few meters fairly mature work, is also one of the representative works. < / p > < p > a few meters, said the creation inspiration of the book began in one day is next to the electric drill was too noisy to drawing, so we have to start a daze, thinking and unconstrained style. Suddenly feel never know who is the one next to my house to live, but every day and he or she is separated only a thin wall and sleep. If we meet by chance in the outside, if we never mention each other\'s house, then maybe we won\'t meet again, also never know we actually lives next door. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108006721', '天龙八部', 'images/天龙八部.jpg', '生活.读书.新知三联书店', '武侠', '72', '96', '<p>天龙八部乃金笔下的一部长篇小说，与《射雕》，《神雕》等几部长篇小说一起被称为可读性最高的金庸小说。《天龙》的故事情节曲折，内容丰富，也曾多次被改编为电视作品。是金庸作品中集大成的一部。故事以北宋末年动荡的社会环境为背景，展开波澜壮阔的历史画卷，塑造了乔峰、段誉、虚竹、慕容复等形象鲜明的人物，成为武侠史上的经典之作。故事精彩纷呈，人物命运悲壮多变，是可读性很强的作品，具有震撼人心的力量</p>', '< p > tian long ba bu is a novel under the fountain, and \"shoot diao\", \"shendiao\" wait for a few novels together is called the readability of the highest jin yong\'s novels. \"Dragon\" of the plot twists and turns, rich in content, also has repeatedly been adapted for television. The crest of jin yong\'s works. Story north dynasty in turbulent social environment as the background, a magnificent scroll of history, shaped the xiao feng, broken jade, falsely bamboo, MuRongFu vivid characters, become a classic in the history of kung fu. Story, characters tragic fate is changeable, is highly readable works, with impressive power < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787501600069', '茶花女', 'images/茶花女.jpg', '外国文学出版社', '文学', '6.75', '9', '<p>《茶花女》为我们塑造了一些生动、鲜明的艺术形象，而其中最突出、最令人难忘的自然是女主人公茶花女玛格丽特。读者们切莫把玛格丽特和阿尔丰西娜·普莱西小姐混为一谈，阿尔丰西娜的身世固然值得同情，但她的的确确是个堕落的女人，用小仲马的话来说，她“既是一个纯洁无瑕的贞女，又是_个彻头彻尾的娼妇”。但玛格丽特却不同，她美丽、聪明而又善良j虽然沦落风尘，但依旧保持着一颗纯洁、高尚的心灵。她充满热情和希望地去追求真正的爱情生活，而当这种希望破灭之后，又甘愿自我牺牲去成全他人。</p><p>这一切都使这位为人们所不齿的烟花女子的形象闪烁着一种圣洁的光辉，以至于人们一提起“茶花女”这三个字的时候，首先想到的不是什么下贱的妓女，而是一位美丽、可爱而又值得同情的女眭。古今中外的文学名著为人们留下了许许多多不朽的艺术形象，而玛格丽特则完全可以跻身其间而毫无愧色。</p>', '< p > \"La Traviata\" for we created some vivid and distinctive artistic image, and one of the most prominent, the heroine is the most unforgettable natural La Traviata Margaret. Readers don\'t confuse FengXiNa Margaret and arsene miss lacey, al FengXiNa life is worthy of sympathy, but she is really a fallen woman, in dumas\'s words, she \"is both a pure virgin and _ a downright whore\". But Margaret was different, she is beautiful, smart and kind j, although a prostitute, but still maintained a pure and noble spirit. She is full of passion and hope to pursue the real love life, and when the hopes, and willing to sacrifice to help others. < / p > < p > all this makes the contempt for people fireworks woman image of a holy light flashing, that people think about the three words \"La Traviata\", the first thought is not cheap prostitute, but a beautiful, lovely, sympathetic Sui woman. The ancient and modern, Chinese and foreign literary classics for the people left behind many immortal art image, while Margaret can completely into it without regret. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020046089', '了不起的盖茨比', 'images/了不起的盖茨比.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '9', '12', '<p>盖茨比为了久久地抱着的一个梦而付出了很高的代价。他死后，尼克发觉是汤姆暗中挑拨威尔逊去杀死盖茨比。他感到东部鬼影幢幢，世态炎凉，便决定回中西部老家去。这是一个简单的故事，却有着极悲凉的人生况味。</p>', '< p > gatsby in order to hold a long time in a dream and pay a high price. After his death, Nick found Tom secretly provoke Wilson to kill gatsby. He felt the east ghost the narrowest and social change in temperature and then decided to go back to my hometown in the Midwest. This is a simple story, has a very sad life condition. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532712243', '基督山伯爵', 'images/基督山伯爵.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '32.925', '43.9', '<p>小说以法国波旁王朝和七月王朝两大时期为背景，描写了一个报恩复仇的故事。法老号大副唐泰斯受船长的临终嘱托，为拿破仑送了一封信，受到两个对他嫉妒的小人的陷害，被打入死牢，狱友法里亚神甫向他传授了各种知识，还在临终前把一批宝藏的秘密告诉了他。他设法越狱后找到了宝藏，成为巨富。从此他化名为基督山伯爵，经过精心策划，报答了他的恩人，惩罚了三个一心想置他于死地的仇人。</p>', '< p > the novel to the French bourbon dynasty and two period of July dynasty as the background, describes a gratitude revenge story. Pharaon chief Tang Tai last asks by the captain, send a letter for napoleon, framed by two of his jealous man, into death row, inmates faria priests taught all kinds of knowledge, to him also in the last of a batch of told him the secret of the treasure. He managed to escape after finding the treasure, become rich. From then on he known as the count of monte cristo, carefully planning and thanked his benefactor, punished the three thought kill his enemies. < / p >', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532741571', '一个陌生女人的来信', 'images/一个陌生女人的来信.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>这是一部短篇小说集，除《一个陌生女人的来信》，亦按时间顺序收录了《火烧火燎的秘密》、《马来狂人》等名篇，作者的创作历程一目了然。</p><p>《一个陌生女人的来信》讲述一个刻骨铭心的爱情故事，一个女子暗恋男主人公18年，直至临死才决定向他告白。</p>', '< p > this is a collection of short stories, in addition to the \"letter from an unknown woman\", also includes the secret of low-paying jobs in chronological order, such as the Malay men masterpiece, the author\'s creation course be clear at a glance. < / p > < p > \"letter from an unknown woman\" tells a deep-rooted of love story, a woman who has a crush on the hero for 18 years, until he decided to his confession. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020027606', '呼啸山庄', 'images/呼啸山庄.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '20.475', '27.3', '<p>夏洛蒂和传记作者告诉我们，爱米丽生性独立、豁达、纯真、刚毅、热情而又内向。她颇有男儿气概，酷爱自己生长其间的荒原，平素在离群索居中，除去手足情谊，最喜与大自然为友，从她的诗和一生行为，都可见她天人合一宇宙观与人生观的表现，有人因此而将她视为神秘主义者。其实人与自然的关系，从来就是人类文明史上重要的命题，爱米丽不过是步历代哲人、隐者、科学家、艺术家后尘，通过生活和创作，身体力行地探寻人与自然的关系。</p><p>由于爱米丽一生经历简短，她既未受完整系统教育，又没有爱情婚姻实际体验，人们对于她能写出《呼啸山庄》这样深刻独特的爱情绝唱也曾疑惑不解。对这一问题，早有人以“天才说”</p><p>做出解释，而经过百余年的研考据，传记作者和评论家又提出了更加令人信服的凭据。爱米丽以及她的姐妹，虽然生长在苦寒单调的约克郡，她们的父亲帕特里克・勃朗特却来自北爱尔兰，母亲玛丽亚・勃兰威尔是威尔士人。这一对父母所属民族的祖先，同属具有冲动浪漫气质的凯尔特人，而且二人都不乏写诗为文的天分：帕特里克又一向怀有文学抱负，曾自费出版诗集；玛丽亚出嫁前写给帕特里克的情书，也是文采斐然。继承了父母的遗传基因，又受到荒原精神的陶冶哺育，爱米丽的艺术天才无疑并非无源之水；而且她家那座荒原边缘上的牧师住宅，外观虽然冷落寒酸，内里却因几个才智过人的子女相亲相携而温馨宜人。他们自幼相互鼓励、切磋，以读书写作为乐。这一方面大大冲淡了物质匮乏之苦；同时也培养锻炼了他们的写作功力。</p><p>爱米丽的写作，从诗开始，她在着手创作《呼啸山庄》之前十六七年间，陆续写出习作诗文《贡代尔传奇》和短诗，如今所见，仅近二百首诗。姑且不论它们本身的艺术价值，这些文字起码也是创作《呼啸山庄》这部不朽之作的有益准备。换言之，她写《呼啸山庄》，是她写诗的继续。她的诗，真挚、雄劲、粗犷、深沉、高朗，这也是《呼啸山庄》的格调。</p>', '< p > tell us charlotte and biographer, Emily is independent, open-minded, pure, resolute, enthusiasm and introverted. She has a machismo, have a passion for their growth in the waste land, usually in solitude, removing the brotherhood, the most pleased with nature, from her poems and life behavior, is the unity of nature and man and her outlook on life, someone to her as a mystic. In fact, the relationship between human and nature, has always been one important proposition in the history of civilization, Emily is but a step past dynasties philosopher, hermit, scientists, artists, through the life and creation, practice to explore the relationship between human and nature. < / p > < p > because Emily lived through short, she is not a complete education system, there is no love marriage practical experience, for she could write wuthering heights such profound unique love song has puzzled. On this issue, as early as someone with \"genius\" < / p > < p > to explain, but after hundred years of textual research, suggests a more convincing biographers and critics of credentials. Emily and her sister, although growth in Fairbanks drab Yorkshire, their father ・ Patrick Bronte comes from Northern Ireland, mother maria ・ cuny LAN will is welsh. Nationality ancestors, this pair of parents are with impulsive romantic temperament of the celtics, and both are writing poetry for talent: Patrick and literary ambitions have always held, had self-published of poetry; Maria maiden to Patrick\'s love letter, is also a remarkable gift. Inherited their parents\' genetic, and edify feeding by wild spirit, Emily artistic genius is not madrassa reflected; And her family the wilderness on the edge of the parsonage, although the cold shabby appearance, inner is due to their children to be with a few clever pleasant warmth. They have been encourage each other, to learn to read the writing as joy. This aspect significantly dilute the material deprivation suffering; Exercise also cultivate their writing ability. < / p > < p > Emily writing, starting from the poem, she set about writing wuthering heights before 10, 67 in writing assignments poetry \"gong dyer legend\" and a short poem, now can see, only nearly two hundred poems. Whatever their artistic value, the text is creating the masterpiece, wuthering heights of good preparation. In other words, she wrote \"wuthering heights\", is that she continues to write poetry. Her poetry, sincere, XiongJin, rugged, dark, Gao Lang, this also is the style of \"wuthering heights\". < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020068616', '亲爱的安德烈', 'images/亲爱的安德烈.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '情感', '19.5', '26', '<p>安德烈十四岁的时候，龙应台离开欧洲，返回台湾，就任台北市首任文化局长。等她卸任回到儿子身边，安德烈已是一个一百八十四公分高的十八岁的小伙子，坐在桌子另一边，有一点“冷”地看着妈妈。</p><p>他们是两代人，年龄相差三十年；他们也是两国人，中间横着东西文化。失去小男孩安安没关系，但龙应台一定要认识成熟的大学生安德烈。</p><p>于是，母子俩用了三年时间互相通信。龙应台“认识了人生里第一个十八岁的人”，安德烈“也第一次认识了自己的母亲”。</p><p>收入此书的的三十多封书信，感动了无数被“亲子”之间隔阂与冲突深深困扰着的读者，为读者弭平代沟、跨越文化阻隔、两代人沟通交流带来了全新的思维和方法。</p>', '< p > Andre at the age of fourteen, lung ying-tai leave Europe, return to Taiwan, office director of Taipei city\'s first culture. She left to go back to her son, Andre is a boy of eighteen, one hundred and eighty-four centimeters tall, sitting on the other side of the table, looked at his mother is a little \"cold\". < / p > < p > two generations, they are younger than 30 years. They are two people, across the east-west cultural in the middle. Lost little boy in it doesn\'t matter, but lung ying-tai must meet mature students Andre. < / p > < p > so, took three years to communicate with each other both mother and son. Lung ying-tai \"know the life in the first 18\", Andre \"also met for the first time his mother\". < / p > < p > this book income of more than 30 letters, touched countless by gap and conflict between the \"parent\" deeply troubling readers, for the reader to relate the generation gap, cross cultural block, two generations communication has brought the new thinking and method. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787500627098', '沉默的大多数', 'images/沉默的大多数.jpg', '中国青年出版社', '文学', '20.25', '27', '<p>这本杂文随笔集包括思想文化方面的文章，涉及知识分子的处境及思考，社会道德伦理，文化论争，国学与新儒家，民族主义等问题；包括从日常生活中发掘出来的各种真知灼见，涉及科学与邪道，女权主义等；包括对社会科学研究的评论，涉及性问题，生育问题，同性恋问题，社会研究的伦理问题和方法问题等；包括创作谈和文论，如写作的动机，作者的师承，作者对小说艺术的看法，作者对文体格调的看法，对影视的看法等；包括少量的书评，其中既有对文学经典的评论，也有对当代作家作品的一些看法；最后，还包括一些域外生活的杂感以及对某些社会现象的评点。</p>', '< p > this essay essays include ideological and cultural aspects of the article, relating to the intellectual situation and thinking, social ethics, cultural controversy, Chinese learning with the new Confucianism, issues of nationalism; Including excavated from the daily life of all kinds of insights, involving science and heterodox, feminism, etc.; Include comments on the social science research, involving sexual problems, fertility problems, gay and lesbian issues, ethical issues and approaches to the study of the social problems, etc.; Including literature and literary theory, such as the motivation of writing, the author\'s educational background, the author views to the art of fiction, the author view of writing style, view of film and television, etc.; Include a small amount of book reviews, some comments on the literary classics, also have some views on contemporary writers and their works; Finally, also includes some outside life style as well as the recommendations of certain social phenomenon. < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020065394', '无人生还', 'images/无人生还.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '悬疑', '14.25', '19', '<p>十个互不相识的人，被富有的欧文先生邀请到了印地安岛上的私人别墅里。晚餐后，一个神秘的声音揭开了人们心中所各自隐藏着的可怕秘密。当天晚上，年轻的马斯顿先生离奇死去，古老的童谣就像诅咒一样笼罩着所有人，似乎有一双神秘的眼镜在时刻窥视着这场死亡游戏，到访者就像消失的印地安小瓷人一样一个又一个的走向死神……</p>', '< p > ten strangers, is invited to rich Mr Irving Indian private villa on the island. After dinner, a mysterious sound in people\'s minds by their hides a terrible secret. That night, the young Mr Marston\'s bizarre die, old nursery rhymes like curse hangs over all, seems to have a pair of glasses in time upon the mysterious the death game, visitors like disappear of Indian small CiRen one after another to the death... < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020056309', '东方快车谋杀案', 'images/东方快车谋杀案.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '悬疑', '13.5', '18', '<p>午夜过后，一场大雪迫使东方快车停了下来。这辆豪华列车整年都处于满员状态。但那天早上却发现少了一名乘客。一个美国人死在了他的包厢里，他被刺了十二刀，可他包厢的门却是反锁着的。</p><p>随着紧张气氛逐渐增强，侦探赫尔克里·波洛想出了两个侦破此案的方法……</p>', '<p> after midnight, a heavy snow forced stopped on the Orient express. The luxury train all year round in the full state. But the morning only to find a passenger. An American dead in his box, he stabbed 12 knife, yet he balcony door is locked. </p> <p> as the tension gradually increases, the detective hull kerry poirot figured out two methods to solve the case... </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787501408580', '福尔摩斯探案全集（上中下）', 'images/福尔摩斯探案全集（上中下）.jpg', '群众出版社', '悬疑', '51', '68', '<p>最经典的群众出版社的翻译版本，一经出版，立即风靡成千上万的中国人。离奇的情节，扣人的悬念，世界上最聪明的侦探，人间最诡秘的案情，福尔摩斯不但让罪犯无处藏身，也让你的脑细胞热情激荡，本套书获第一届全国优秀外国文学图书奖。</p>', '< p > the classic translation version of the press, publication, immediately popular tens of thousands of Chinese. Bizarre plot, buckle the suspense, the world\'s most clever detective, the world\'s most secretive case, holmes is not only let the criminals nowhere to hide, also make your brain cells agitate enthusiasm, this series of excellent foreign literature prize of the first session of the national book award. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787208072107', '灿烂千阳', 'images/灿烂千阳.jpg', '上海人民出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>私生女玛丽雅姆在父亲的宅院门口苦苦守候，回到家却看到因绝望而上吊自杀的母亲。那天是她十五岁的生日，而童年嘎然而止。玛丽雅姆随后由父亲安排远嫁喀布尔四十多岁的鞋匠拉希德，几经流产，终因无法生子而长期生活在家暴阴影之下。</p><p>十八年后，少女莱拉的父母死于战火，青梅竹马的恋人也在战乱中失踪，举目无亲的莱拉别无选择，被迫嫁给拉希德。两名阿富汗女性各自带着属于不同时代的悲惨回忆，共同经受着战乱、贫困与家庭暴力的重压，心底潜藏着的悲苦与忍耐相互交织，让她们曾经水火不容，又让她们缔结情谊，如母女般相濡以沫。然而，多年的骗局终有被揭穿的一天……</p><p>她们将做出如何的选择？她们的命运又将何去何从？</p><p>关于不可宽恕的时代，不可能的友谊以及不可毁灭的爱。《灿烂千阳》再次以阿富汗战乱为背景，时空跨越三十年，用细腻感人的笔触描绘了阿富汗旧家族制度下苦苦挣扎的妇女，她们所怀抱的希望、爱情、梦想与所有的失落。</p>', '< p > illegitimate daughter Mary jas are waiting at the gate of the father\'s house, home only to see a mother by despair and commit suicide by hanging suicide. That day was fifteen years old birthday, she ended abruptly and childhood. Mary jas, then arranged by father far away in Kabul more than forty years old shoemaker rasheed, abortion, several times with storm shadow unable to have children and live for a long time at home. < / p > < p > 18 years later, the girl laila\'s parents died in the fighting, childhood sweetheart lover is missing in the fighting, without friends of laila had no choice but to marry rasheed. Two Afghan women with their respective belong to different times of the sad memories, common suffering from war, poverty, and domestic violence, the weight of the bottom of my heart hidden bitterness and patience are intertwined, and let them have incompatible, and let them to conclude, as mother and daughter dawei. For many years, however, fraud has been exposed a day... < / p > < p > how they will make a choice? Their fate and go from here? < / p > < p > about inexcusable era, unlikely friendship and the love can\'t be destroyed. \"Brilliant regionalization\" is set in the Afghan war again, space-time spanning 30 years, with detailed describes the moving of the brush Afghan women struggling under the old system of family, they embrace hope, love, dream and all the loss. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108006639', '笑傲江湖（全四册）', 'images/笑傲江湖（全四册）.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '文学', '57.6', '76.8', '<p>《笑傲江湖》是金庸1967年写的一部武侠小说，属于金庸的后期作品。</p>', '< p > \"smile the ao river\'s lake\" is a martial arts novels written by jin yong 1967, belong to jin yong\'s later work. < / p >', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020032044', '巴黎圣母院', 'images/巴黎圣母院.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '16.875', '22.5', '<p>《巴黎圣母院》是法国文豪维克多·雨果第一部引起轰动效应的浪漫派小说。小说以十五世纪路易十一统治下的法国为背景，通过一个纯洁无辜的波希米亚女郎惨遭迫害的故事，揭露了教士的阴险卑鄙，宗教法庭的野蛮残忍，贵族的荒淫无耻和国王的专横残暴。作品鲜明地体现了反封建、反教会的意识和对人民群众的赞颂。</p>', '< p > is the French writer Victor Hugo \"Notre Dame DE Paris\" first caused a sensation effect of romantic novel. Novels in the 15th century under the rule of Louis xi of France as the background, through a pure innocent Bohemian girl suffered persecution, revealed the cleric\'s sinister sneaky and brutality of the inquisition, shameless and nobility of arbitrary brutality. Works vividly embodies the feudalism, the consciousness of the church, and for the people\'s praise. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506335867', '莲花', 'images/莲花.jpg', '作家出版社', '情感', '18.75', '25', '<p>全书收录安妮墨脱之行所拍八张图片，皆沿途所见。</p><p>《莲花》叙述年轻女子庆昭身患疾病，滞留高原，静等死亡。中年男人善生刚刚结束追名逐利的暄腾往日，内心长久压抑的黑暗苏醒，准备去与世隔绝的墨脱，寻访旧友内河。内河是被世界遗忘的女子，命运多舛。一路上善生向庆昭讲述自己和内河的往昔，雅鲁藏布江江河谷的奇崛险阻，恰似叙述中依次展开的一代人苦痛而流离的蜕变过程。</p>', '<p> the book included Anne ink to take off the trip taken eight pictures, all can see along the way. </p> <p> \"lotus\" narrative young woman zhao with a rare disease, stranded plateau, waiting for death. Middle-aged man life just ended our soft old, heart, to revive the darkness of the depressed for a long time to prepare to isolated ink off, after the first friend river. Inland river is forgotten by the world of woman, ill-fated. Live well all the way to the celebration of zhao about yourself and inland river past, Brahmaputra Jiang Jiang valley of singular and obstacles, as a narrative, in turn, the pain of a generation and transformation process. </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787556212743', '我不喜欢这世界，我只喜欢你', 'images/我不喜欢这世界，我只喜欢你.jpg', '湖南少年儿童出版社', '情感', '22.35', '29.8', '<p>◆暖！萌！甜！几乎每一段都令人笑出声来，但也不乏泪点。</p><p>◆真实恋爱成长回忆录，最萌最暖のLovestory。</p><p>◆8张超萌爱心动全彩插图，随书赠送4张F君情怀卡。</p><p>◆硬壳精装，全彩特种纸内页印刷。</p><p>领证的前一晚我问他：“你是什么时候开始喜欢我的？”</p><p>他答：“不记得了。”</p><p>“可是，为什么是我呢？”</p><p>“为什么不是你呢？”</p><p>“我很小气，又爱吃醋。”</p><p>“我也是。”</p><p>“我怕自己不值得你喜欢。”</p><p>“我也是。”</p><p>“我没怎么谈过恋爱，不知道爱情是什么。”</p><p>“我也不知道。”</p><p>他温柔地握住我的手，“但我知道，一想到能和你共度余生，我就对余生充满期待。”</p><p>16岁时我们共用一个课桌，胳膊与胳膊相距不过十厘米，我的余光里全是他。</p><p>26岁时我从清晨醒来，侧头看到阳光落在他脸上，想与他就这样慢慢变老。</p><p>也许这就是爱情吧。</p>', '< p > warm in pieces! MOE! Sweet! Almost every period of laughter, but there is no lack of tears. Pieces < / p > < p > true love grow memoirs, most of the warming の Lovestory. Pieces < / p > < p > 8 Zhang Chaomeng love dynamic full-color illustrations, giving 4 F your feelings card with books. < / p > < p > shell hardcover, full-color pages related to the specialty paper printing. < / p > < p > to license the night before I ask him: \"when did you begin to like me?\" < / p > < p > he answer: \"don\'t remember.\" < / p > < p > \"but, why me?\" < / p > < p > \"why did not you?\" < / p > < p > \"I am very stingy, jealous again.\" < / p > < p > \"me, too.\" < / p > < p > \"I afraid I not worth you like it.\" < / p > < p > \"me, too.\" < / p > < p > \"I haven\'t talked about love, don\'t know what love is.\" < / p > < p > \"I don\'t know.\" < / p > < p > he gently held my hand, \"but I know that the thought of can spend the rest of my life with you, I will for the rest of my life is full of expectations.\" < / p > < p > we Shared a desk at the age of 16, arm and arm but ten centimeters apart, all my Yu Guangli is his. < / p > < p > at the age of 26 from early in the morning I woke up, his head to see the sunlight fell on his face, want to grow old with him so. < / p > < p > maybe this is love. < / p >', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532734191', '海边的卡夫卡', 'images/海边的卡夫卡.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>小说的主人公是一位自称名叫田村卡夫卡——作者始终未交代其真名——的少年。他在十五岁生日前夜独自离家出走，乘坐夜行长途巴士远赴四国。出走的原因是为了逃避父亲所作的比俄底浦斯王还要可怕的预言：尔将弑父，将与尔母、尔姐交合。卡夫卡四岁时，母亲突然失踪，带走了比卡夫卡年长四岁、其实是田村家养女的姐姐，不知何故却将亲生儿子抛弃。他从未见过母亲的照片，甚至连名字也不知道。仿佛是运命在冥冥之中引导，他偶然来到某私立图书馆，遂栖身于此。馆长佐伯女士是位四十多岁气质高雅的美妇，有着波澜曲折的神秘身世。卡夫卡疑心她是自己的生母，佐伯却对此不置可否。卡夫卡恋上了佐伯，并与之发生肉体关系。小说还另设一条副线，副线的主角是老人中田，他在二战期间读小学时，经历过一次神秘的昏迷事件，从此丧失了记忆，将学过的知识完全忘记，甚至不会认字计数，却获得了与猫对话的神秘能力。中田在神智失控的情况下杀死了一个自称焦尼·沃卡（JohnnyWalker）、打扮得酷似那著名威士忌酒商标上所画的英国绅士的狂人，一路搭车也来到此地。小说共分49章，奇数章基本上用写实手法讲述卡夫卡的故事，偶数章则用魔幻手法展现中田的奇遇。两种手法交互使用，编织出极富强烈虚构色彩的、奇幻诡诘的现代寓言。佐伯是将这两个故事联结为一体的结合点，而弑父的预言似乎最终也未能避免，因为狂人焦尼·沃卡居然是卡夫卡生父乔装改扮的，真正的凶手也并非中田……</p>', '< p > the hero of the novel is a called himself tamura kafka - the author never gave its name - young. He alone away from home the night before 15th birthday. Night on long-distance bus to the four countries. Leave the reason is to avoid the father of king theopompus much worse than the bottom of the prophecy: will kill, and mother, elder sister intercourse. Kafka at the age of four, my mother suddenly disappeared, took four years older than kafka, is actually tamura domestic female elder sister, somehow it will own son abandoned. He had never seen mother\'s photos, even the name is also don\'t know. Indirect insofar as if destiny in guidance, he drops by a private library, then stay here. Curator with ms \"is a belle, with elegant look in their 40 s with stir mysterious story twists and turns. Kafka suspect she were his mother, but he was noncommittal about. Kafka crush on his job, and the relation with the occurrence of the flesh. Novel also setting up a line, the main character in the line is the old man once, he was in primary school during the second world war, experienced a mysterious coma, ever lost memory, the knowledge that will completely forget, don\'t even read count, mysterious ability has received a dialogue with the cat. Once out of control in mind killed a claim under the condition of JiaoNi walker (JohnnyWalker), dressed like painted on the labels of the famous whiskey English gentleman madman, a ride all the way here. 49 chapters novel, kafka\'s story of odd chapter basically with realism, even chapter to show he\'s adventure with magic. Two kinds of technique used alternately, weave very strong color fiction and fantasy deceit in wall of modern fable. With \"was to link for the integration of these two stories combining site, and killed his prophecy seems ultimately failed to avoid, because a madman JiaoNi, walker was kafka father, disguise the real murderer is not he... < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787500652045', '城南旧事', 'images/城南旧事.jpg', '中国青年出版社', '文学', '12', '16', '<p>多少年来，《城南旧事》感动了一代又一代的读者，除了再版无数次的小说版外，1985年，本书在中国大陆搬上银幕，电影“城南旧事”获得“中国电影金鸡奖”、第二届“马尼拉国际电影节最佳故事片奖金鹰奖章”、第十四届“贝尔格勒国际儿童电影节最佳影片思想奖”等多项大奖。</p><p>儿童绘本版《城南旧事》由当今中国极具代表性的水彩画家关维兴，运用优雅诗意的风格和穿透人心的独到技巧，将创作的图画全然融入故事的情节。画中举凡服饰、器物和建筑，考据详实，没一点随便或含糊。人物细致的表情、光线和空气的律动、圆熟丰美的调子，使文图呈现无懈可击的呼应。绘本《城南旧事》甫出版即获选1993、1994年“波隆那国际儿童书插画展”、1993年“布拉迪斯国际插画双年展”以及1994年“加泰隆尼亚国际插画双年展”。</p><p>从小说到电影，从成人书到儿童绘本，《城南旧事》是故事、是梦幻，读时仿若音乐，轻轻扣动人心，字里行间所隐涵的深意，更令人撼动，久久不能自已。</p>', '<p> for many years, the city has moved generations of readers, in addition to reprint numerous novel version, in 1985, the book in mainland China to the screen, the movie \"city\" \"China golden rooster\", the second \"Manila international film festival best feature film award, golden eagle award\", the 14th \"Belgrade international children\'s film festival best picture prize\" and so on many awards. </p> <p> children\'s painting \"the city\" by today\'s edition of China\'s most representative GuanWeiXing watercolor painter, using the graceful poetic style and penetrate the heart of the original skill, will create pictures into the plot of the story at all. Paintings include clothing, artifacts, and construction, textual research in detail, not a little casual or vague. Figures and detailed expression, the rhythm, mellow mellow tone in light and air, make the article figure presents impeccable echo. \"City\" publication \"-- that is selected in 1993 and 1994, the\" wave of the international children\'s books illustration exhibition \", 1993 \"blah diss illustrations international biennale\" and 1994 \"international illustrations of Catalonia biennale\". </p> <p> from novel to film, from adult books to children\'s picture books, \"the city\" is the story, is a dream, when reading like music, gently pull the heart, between the lines of the hidden culvert meaning, what is more, for a long time can\'t own. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532129027', '兄弟（上）', 'images/兄弟（上）.jpg', '上海文艺出版社', '社会', '12', '16', '<p>《兄弟》讲述了江南小镇两兄弟李光头和宋钢的人生。李光头的父亲不怎么光彩地意外身亡，而同一天李光头出生。宋钢的父亲宋凡平在众人的嘲笑声中挺身而出，帮助了李光头的母亲李兰，被后者视为恩人。几年后宋钢的母亲也亡故，李兰和宋凡平在互相帮助中相爱并结婚，虽然这场婚姻遭到了镇上人们的鄙夷和嘲弄，但两人依然相爱甚笃，而李光头和宋钢这对没有血缘关系的兄弟也十分投缘。</p><p>李兰去上海看病，而“文革”开始，宋凡平遭受了极其残酷的虐待，但他坚持给病中的妻子写信，隐瞒了事实真相，用想像出的美好生活欺骗着妻子，但最终仍然逃脱不了惨死的命运。李兰为宋凡平守孝，7年不洗头，而李光头和宋钢则在相互照顾中成长……</p>', '< p > \"brothers\" tells the story of two brothers chian head and Song Gang jiangnan town life. Chian head father not to death, and head of chian was born on the same day. Song Gang father Song Fan flat to stand up in public derision, helped the chian\'s mother li LAN, the latter as a benefactor. Song Gang after a few years of his mother was dead, li LAN and Song Fan flat in each other and help each other in love and get married, although the marriage are despised by the people in the town and ridicule, but two people love each other, still the chian head and Song Gang this to not related brother also very congenial. < / p > < p > li LAN go to Shanghai to see the doctor, and the \"cultural revolution\" started, Song Fan suffered extremely cruel abuse, but he insisted on writing a letter to his sick wife, conceal the truth, cheat his wife with the imagine of a better life, but in the end still can not escape the fate of the tragic. Li LAN for Song Fan terribly, 7 years don\'t wash your hair, while chian head and Song Gang grow in to take care of each other... < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544743822', '呐喊', 'images/呐喊.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '27', '36', '<p>《呐喊》收录作者1918年至1922年所作小说十四篇。1923年8月由北京新潮社出版，原收十五篇，列为该社《文艺丛书》之一。1924年5月第三次印刷时起，改由北京北新书局出版，列为作者所编的《乌合丛书》之一。1930年1月第十三次印刷时，由作者抽去其中的《不周山》一篇(后改名为《补天》，收入《故事新编》)。作者生前共印行二十二版次。</p>', '< p > \"scream\", included the authors from 1918 to 1922 novel fourteen articles. In August 1923, published by the Beijing new clubs, the original article 15, listed as one of the club \"series of literature and art\". In May 1924 the third printing, beixin publishing house of Beijing instead, as the author is one of the \"wu or series. On January 13th 1930 printing, the authors draw to one of the \"no island\" a (later renamed for days, income \"new stories\"). The author before publishing 22 edition. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787201048161', '情书', 'images/情书.jpg', '天津人民出版社', '情感', '13.5', '18', '<p>日本神户，渡边博子在未婚夫藤井树的三周年祭日上又一次陷入到悲痛和思念之中。博子在藤井树的中学同学录里找到了他在小樽市读书时的地址。由于抑制不住对爱人的怀念，博子按着这个地址给远在天国的藤井树寄去了一封充满问候和思念的书信。</p><p>不可思议的是，不久博子竟然收到了署名为“藤井树”的回信。经过进一步了解，这个藤井树是一个年轻的女子，而且她还曾经是男性藤井树的同班同学，原来是博子从同学录中误抄了她的地址。为了多了解一些男友在中学时代的情况，博子继续与女性藤井树保持书信来往。而藤井树在不断的回忆中，竟逐渐发现中学时代那个和自己同名同姓的少男曾经对自己产生过一段真挚的感情……</p><p>《情书》由一个同名同姓的误会开始，通过两个女子书信的交流，以含情脉脉的笔触舒缓地展现了两段可贵的爱情。女主角博子对藤井树的眷恋，两个藤井树之间朦胧的情感，都没有由于藤井树的意外死亡而枯萎，而通过细腻感人的影象深深地印在每一个观众的心里，永远不变。</p><p>在精心描绘爱情的同时，岩井俊二还着意表现了对逝去岁月的怀念和追忆。《情书》正象普鲁斯特那本小说的名字，追忆着似水的年华。过往的爱情和青春也正是在主人公的回忆中才逐渐清晰、复活。与现实相比，影片中的过去更为明快优美。在那一幅幅唯美的画面中，漫天飞舞的片片樱花，暗生情愫的少男少女，都唤起我们的无限遐想。而《情书》中所构筑的那个美好的中学时代，可能也正是岩井俊二和很多人最为温馨纯洁的回忆。</p><p>《情书》中对过去的追忆和有关生死的描绘都极具东方气质，含蓄优美、感而不伤地表达了故事的主题——珍惜有限的生命和宝贵的爱情。</p>', '< p > kobe, hiroko watanabe in fiance nice cake on the third anniversary of the death once again plunged into grief and thoughts. Bo son found him in the middle school alumni of nice cake in otaru reading\'s address. Due to the irrepressible you miss love, hiroko according to this address to sent a nice cake in the kingdom of heaven is full of greetings and missing letters. < / p > < p > incredibly, bo son should soon received a signed \"nice cake\" reply. After further understanding and the nice cake is a young woman, and she used to be the classmate of male nice cake, turned out to be bo son from alumni to copy her address by mistake. In order to know more about her boyfriend in high school, hiroko continue to maintain correspondence with the women\'s nice cake. And nice cake in the memory of continuously, and gradually found that middle school the and his namesake boys once had a sincere feelings to myself... < / p > < p > \"love letter\" from a namesake misunderstanding, through the exchange of two women\'s letter, with her amorous showed two Duan Kegui soft love. Actress son to nice cake, hazy feeling between two nice cake, are not due to the accidental death of nice cake wither, and through the exquisite moving image deep into every audience\'s heart, never change. < / p > < p > at the same time of portray love, shunji iwai it.this is also shows the nostalgia for the past days and remembrance. \"Love letter\" as Proust the name of the novel, reminiscing about the softness and mood. Of love and youth is in the memory of the hero to become clear, and the resurrection. In the past compared to reality, the film is more lively and beautiful. In these beautiful pictures, the flying of cherry, dark feelings for boys and girls, arouse our infinite daydream. While in the \"love letter\" build the good high school, may be it is also the shunji iwai and a lot of people are the most sweet and pure memories. < / p > < p > \"love letter\" in the past recall and describe about life and death are extremely Oriental temperament, implicative, beautiful feeling and does not hurt to express the theme of the story, I cherish the love from limited and precious life. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020054985', '肖申克的救赎', 'images/肖申克的救赎.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '22.425', '29.9', '<p>这本书收入斯蒂芬·金的四部中篇小说，是他作品中的杰出代表作。其英文版一经推出，即登上《纽约时报》畅销书排行榜的冠军之位，当年在美国狂销二十八万册。目前，这本书已经被翻译成三十一种语言，同时创下了收录的四篇小说中有三篇被改编成轰动一时的电影的记录。</p><p>其中最为著名是曾获奥斯卡奖七项提名、被称为电影史上最完美影片的《肖申克救赎》（又译《刺激一九九五》）。这部小说展现了斯蒂芬·金于擅长的惊悚题材之外的过人功力。书中的另两篇小说《纳粹高徒》与《尸体》拍成电影后也赢得了极佳的口碑。其中《尸体》还被视为斯蒂芬·金最具自传色彩的作品。</p>', '< p > this book income Stephen king four medium-length novel, is the magnum opus of his work. Its English version, which is on the New York times bestseller list title, sold sold two hundred and eighty thousand copies that year in the United States. At present, the book has been translated into thirty languages, at the same time in the collection of three in four novel was adapted into a blockbuster film of the recording. < / p > < p > is one of the most famous one oscar-winning seven nominations, known as the most perfect film \"the shawshank redemption\" in the history of the cinema, and stimulate the 1995). The novel shows the Stephen king beyond the thriller genre of good at passing capability. The other two novel in the book \"Nazi)\" and \"body\" made into a film after also won a good reputation. The \"body\" was seen as a Stephen king\'s most autobiography color. < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787540211998', '羊脂球', 'images/羊脂球.jpg', '北京燕山出版社', '文学', '10.125', '13.5', '<p>莫泊桑短篇小说的代表作。写普法战争时，法国的一群贵族、政客、商人、修女等高贵者，和一个叫作羊脂球的妓女，同乘一辆马车逃离普军占区，在一关卡受阻。普鲁士军官要求同羊脂球过夜，遭到羊脂球拒绝，高贵者们也深表气愤。但马车被扣留后，高贵者们竟施展各种伎俩迫使羊脂球就范，而羊脂球最终得到的却是高贵者们的轻蔑。小说反衬鲜明，悬念迭生，引人入胜，写出了法国各阶层在占领者面前的不同态度，揭露了贵族资产阶级的自私、虚伪和无耻，赞扬了羊脂球的牺牲精神。</p>', '< p > maupassant short fiction masterpiece. Write the franco-prussian war, a group of French nobles, politicians, businessmen, nun noble person, and a prostitute, called the ball to take a cab to flee PuJun occupied area, stuck in a level. Prussian officer asked with the ball for the night, were refused by the suet ball, noble who also deeply angry. , but the carriage were detained after the noble unexpectedly cast various tactics have pushed the ball fan, and the ball is noble who end up with contempt. Novel contrast and bright, suspending, fascinating, wrote every class in front of the occupier of the French attitudes, reveal the noble bourgeoisie of selfishness, hypocrisy and shameless, praised the sacrifice of the ball. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787801093660', '乌合之众', 'images/乌合之众.jpg', '中央编译出版社', '心理', '12', '16', '<p>古斯塔夫・勒庞GustaveLeBon(1841-1931)法国著名社会心理学家。他自1894年始，写下一系列社会心理学著作，以本书最为著名；在社会心理学领域已有的著作中，最有影响的，也是这本并不很厚的《乌合之众》。古斯塔夫・勒庞在他在书中极为精致地描述了集体心态，对人们理解集体行为的作用以及对社会心理学的思考发挥了巨大影响。《乌合之众--大众心理研究》在西方已印至第29版，其观点新颖，语言生动，是群体行为的研究者不可不读的佳作。</p>', '< p > gustaf ・ le pen GustaveLeBon (1841-1931) French famous social psychologist. Since 1894, he wrote a series of social psychology, in order to book the most famous; Existing in the field of social psychology book, most influential, and this is not very thick \"mob\". Gustav ・ le pen in in his book, he extremely delicate to describe the collective mentality, for people to understand the role of collective behavior and thinking played a big impact on the social psychology. Mob - the psychological research in the west has printed to 29 edition, the idea is novel, vivid language, group behavior researchers must-read works. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532741854', '动物农场', 'images/动物农场.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '政治', '7.5', '10', '<p>《动物农场》是奥威尔最优秀的作品之一，是一则入木三分的反乌托的政治讽喻寓言。</p><p>农场的一群动物成功地进行了一场“革命”，将压榨他们的人类东家赶出农场，建立起一个平等的动物社会。然而，动物领袖，那些聪明的猪们最终却篡夺了革命的果实，成为比人类东家更加独裁和极权的统治者。</p>', '< p > \"animal farm\" is one of the best works of Orwell, is a forceful hand against Ukraine\'s political allegorical fable. < / p > < p > the farm animals successfully conducted a \"revolution\", will press their human owners out of the farm and set up a social equality of animals. Clever pig animal leader, however, that those who are ultimately has usurped the fruits of revolution, become more authoritarian and totalitarian rulers than human club. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020017713', '安徒生童话故事集', 'images/安徒生童话故事集.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '儿童', '18.75', '25', '<p>安徒生是丹麦19世纪著名童话作家，世界文学童话创始人。他生于欧登塞城一个贫苦鞋匠家庭，早年在慈善学校读过书，当过学徒工。受父亲和民间口头文学影响，他自幼酷爱文学。</p><p>“为了争取未来的一代”，安徒生决定给孩子写童话，出版了《讲给孩子们听的故事》。此后数年，每年圣诞节都出版一本这样的童话集。其后又不断发表新作，直到1872年因患癌症才逐渐搁笔。近40年间，共计写了童话168篇。</p><p>安徒生的创作可分早、中、晚三个时期。早期童话多充满绮丽的幻想、乐观的精神，体现现实主义和浪漫主义相结合的特点。代表作有《打火匣》、《小意达的花儿》、《拇指姑娘》、《海的女儿》、《野天鹅》、《丑小鸭》等。中期童话，幻想成分减弱，现实成分相对增强。在鞭挞丑恶、歌颂善良中，表现了对美好生活的执着追求，也流露了缺乏信心的忧郁情绪。代表作有《卖火柴的小女孩》、《白雪皇后》、《影子》、《一滴水》、《母亲的故事》、《演木偶戏的人》等。晚期童话比中期更加面对现实，着力描写底层民众的悲苦命运，揭露社会生活的阴冷、黑暗和人间的不平。作品基调低沉。代表作有《柳树下的梦》、《她是一个废物》、《单身汉的睡帽》、《幸运的贝儿》等。</p>', '< p > Hans Christian Andersen was Denmark in the 19th century, the famous writer of fairy tales, founder of the fairy tale world literature. He was born in odense city, a poor shoemaker family at a charity school read books at a very early age, when the apprentice. Affected by the father and the folk oral literature, he have a passion for literature. < / p > < p > \"generation\" in order to fight for the future, Anderson decided that writes the fairy tale for children, published the story of tell the children. After several years, hereafter, he published a copy of this on Christmas every year. Then issued a new continuously, gradually writing until in 1872 from cancer. In recent 40 years, a total of 168 wrote a fairy tale. < / p > < p > Anderson\'s creation can be divided into early, middle and late three times. Early fairy tale more full of gorgeous fantasy, optimistic spirit, reflects the characteristic of combining realism and romanticism. As flint the box \", \"little meaning of flowers\", \"the thumb girl\", \"the daughter of the sea\", \"wild swans\", \"ugly duckling\", etc. Mid-term fairy tale, fantasy component is abate, relative strengthening of reality. In flay ugly, praising good performance in persistent pursuit of a better life, also reveal the melancholy mood of lack of confidence. Representative works have \"the little match girl\", \"the snow queen\", \"shadow\", \"a drop of water\", the story of his mother, \"play puppet show people\", etc. Mid late than fairy tale more face reality, focus on the description of the underlying people\'s miserable destiny, reveal the social life of the cold, dark, and the human. Work of gloomy tone. Including the dreams under the willow, she is a waste, \"bachelor\'s nightcap\", \"lucky belle\", etc. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108006660', '神雕侠侣', 'images/神雕侠侣.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '武侠', '57.6', '76.8', '<p>《神雕侠侣》是金庸作品集之一。其主人公杨过自然而然地走上了非正统的人生道路，入了“道流”。其特点是“至情至性，实现自我”，即把个人的利益、情感、个性及人格尊严置于人生首位，作为首要目标，亦作为待人处事，评价是非的首要原则。书中将杨过对郭靖的杀父之仇与疼惜之恩难以取舍的复杂心理刻画得维妙维肖；他与“姑姑”小龙女的情感纠葛和他对江湖世事的渴望又令他挣扎不已……</p>', '< p > \"giant\" is one of jin yong\'s collection. The hero Yang guo spontaneously took to the unorthodox path, into the \"flow\". Its characteristic is \"to love to sex, realize self\", namely the individual interest, emotion, personality and dignity in life first, as a primary goal, as well as treat people doing things, evaluation is the first principle. Book Yang guo to guo jing, kill the death of his father and cherish torn by the grace of complex psychology attempt to; He and \"aunt\" little dragon female emotional entanglements and his desire for the river\'s lake things again to his struggling... < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787807023777', '少有人走的路', 'images/少有人走的路.jpg', '吉林文史出版社', '情感', '19.5', '26', '<p>这本书处处透露出沟通与理解的意味，它跨越时代限制，帮助我们探索爱的本质，引导我们过上崭新，宁静而丰富的生活；它帮助我们学习爱，也学习独立；它教诲我们成为更称职的、更有理解心的父母。归根到底，它告诉我们怎样找到真正的自我。</p><p>正如开篇所言：人生苦难重重。M·斯科特·派克让我们更加清楚：人生是一场艰辛之旅，心智成熟的旅程相当漫长。但是，他没有让我们感到恐惧，相反，他带领我们去经历一系列艰难乃至痛苦的转变，最终达到自我认知的更高境界。</p>', '< p > this book is a means of communication and understanding, it across the age limit, help us to explore the nature of love, lead us to live in a brand new, quiet and rich life; It helps us learn love, also study independently; It tells us to be more competent, more understand the parents of the heart. In the final analysis, it tells us how to find the real self. < / p > < p > as the opening: life\'s woes. M. Scott peck makes us more clear: life is a hard journey, mature mental journey is quite long. But, he did not make us feel fear, on the contrary, he led us to experience a series of difficult and painful transformation, ultimately achieve self-knowledge higher realm. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806859988', '爱你就像爱生命', 'images/爱你就像爱生命.jpg', '上海锦绣文章出版社', '情感', '13.5', '18', '<p>王小波书信均选自朝华出版社2004年4月第一版《爱你就像爱生命》，此书系王小波生前从未发表过的与李银河的“两地书”，也是迄今他们夫妇最完整和独立的一本书信集。</p>', '< p > wang letters are selected from zarva press in April 2004, the first edition of \"love you like love life\", the ling wang had never published and li yinhe\'s \"book\", the most complete and independent and so far they couples a volume. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536021440', '红玫瑰与白玫瑰', 'images/红玫瑰与白玫瑰.jpg', '花城出版社', '文学', '9.6', '12.8', '<p>“也许每一个男子全都有过这样的两个女人，至少两个。娶了红玫瑰，久而久之，红的变了墙上的一抹蚊子血，白的还是&#34;床前明月光&#34;；娶了白玫瑰，白的便是衣服上沾的一粒饭黏子，红的却是心口上一颗朱砂痣”。因为《红玫瑰与白玫瑰》这句话成了脍炙人口的名言……本书收录了张爱玲1944年的中短篇小说作品。</p>', '< p > \"maybe every man has all had such two women, at least two of them. Took a red rose, and as time passes, red changed the wall with a mosquito blood, white or', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020031825', '朝花夕拾', 'images/朝花夕拾.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>《小引》</p><p>《狗·猫·鼠》</p><p>《阿长与山海经》</p><p>《二十四孝图》</p><p>《五猖会》</p><p>《无常》</p><p>《从百草园到三味书屋》</p><p>《父亲的病》</p><p>《琐记》</p><p>《藤野先生》</p><p>《范爱农》</p><p>《后记》</p>', '< p > \"traditional operas\" < / p > < p > the dog, cat, mouse < / p > < p > \"the long and seas\" < / p > < p > \"24 filial piety figure\" < / p > < p > \"five cabin will\" < / p > < p > \"capricious\" < / p > < p > \"from herbals to sanwei bookroom\" < / p > < p > \"the father\'s illness\" < / p > < p > \"fragmentary\" < / p > < p > \"Mr Fujino\" < / p > < p > \"Fan Ainong\" < / p > < p > < / p > \"afterword\"', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806222850', '阿Q正传', 'images/阿Q正传.jpg', '上海书店出版社', '文学', '10.875', '14.5', '<p>《阿Q正传》讲述值此世纪末，衷心祈愿这里所议论的人物在下一世纪的中国现实生活中淡出；当然，作为光辉的典型人物，他将和哈姆雷特、唐·吉诃德等不朽的名字一样万古不朽。阿Q，是一个卑微渺小的人物，但却是一个巨大的名字。我不说：“伟大”而说“巨大”，是因为这个小人物的确称不上伟大，但这个名字的历史的和美学的涵容量却真是巨大得无比，我想不出世界任何一个文学人物能有阿Q那样巨大的概括性，把几亿人都涵盖进去。几乎每个中国人，你，我，他，都有阿Q的灵魂的因子。阿Q是一个“做奴隶而不可得的时代”的奴隶，比“做稳了奴隶的时代”的奴隶更可悲。做不稳，就要挣扎。他的挣扎当然不可能有过五关、斩六将或爬雪山、过草地那样的英雄事业，但作为一个小人物，他的一生也够悲壮的了。使阿Q的一生焕发悲壮的光采的是，他不仅呈现了清末民初的一个普通百姓的灵魂，几千年来成群而生、成群而死的默默的生长和枯死的灵魂；更是藉着这个灵魂的勾勒，多方面地全国民性的痼疾爆了光。阿Q虽然枪毙了，但他的阴魂不散，时时附在中国人的身上。因为痼疾的病灶埋藏得既深且久，不时复发，至少在本世纪还是常见病和多发病。但愿即将降临的新世纪，这个人物在中国淡出，只留下无与伦比的形象在艺苑中永生。这肯定也是创造这一典型人物的鲁迅的夙愿。</p>', '< p > \"the true story of ah Q\" on the occasion of the end of the 19th century, sincerely wish here talk about the characters of Chinese real life out in the next century; As a glorious typical character, of course, he will and Hamlet, the immortal name like Don Quixote monumental. Q, is a humble small figure, but it is a great name. Said I don\'t say: \"great\" and \"huge\", because this little guy is not great, but the name of history and aesthetic capacity of culvert is really huge, I can\'t imagine the world any a literary figures have Q as great generality, the hundreds of millions of people are involved. Almost every Chinese person, you, me, him, there is Q factor of the soul. Q is a \"slaves, not the era of\" slave, than \"be a slave of stabilizing the slave age\" is more sad. For instability, will struggle. He struggles, of course, there can be no did, difficulties and climb mountains, grassland hero career, but as a little guy, his life is tragic enough. Make Q life shine the light of the tragic mining is that he not only presented the soul of an ordinary people of qing dynasty, for thousands of years and the growth of birth, and die quietly and the soul of the dead; But also through the outline of the soul, variously national ills burst of light. Q shot, but his ghost, always attached to the Chinese people. Because buried deep and long, as well as the focus of the disease recurrence from time to time, at least in this century or the common disease and frequently-occurring disease. I hope the coming of the new century, the character out in China, leaving only unique image in the lives of eternal life. It must also create a typical character of lu xun\'s wish. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544242820', '当我谈跑步时我谈些什么', 'images/当我谈跑步时我谈些什么.jpg', '南海出版公司', '励志', '18.75', '25', '<p>他以文字名满全球。</p><p>他的“蓝调”令万千人神迷忧伤。</p><p>文字是他的符号，“跑者蓝调”何尝不是？</p><p>不再是浮华迷茫，不再是旖旎感伤，不再羚羊挂角无迹可寻——写了几十年“别人”的文字，他第一次只写自己：小说之外、故事之外、文字之外，均是不施雕琢娓娓道来，清淡如云，宁静如水……</p>', '< p > in writing his name with the world. < / p > < p > god of his \"blues\" of ten thousand people sad. < / p > < p > word is his symbol, blues \"runner\" is true? < / p > < p > is no longer a flashy confusion, boasts beautiful is no longer sad, no longer a gazelle approach move no trace to be found - wrote several decades \"others\", he only for the first time to write yourself, novels, stories, characters, all is without carve, light as a cloud, quiet water... < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806574317', '海底两万里', 'images/海底两万里.jpg', '译林出版社', '文学', '14.625', '19.5', '<p>本书是法国举世闻名的科幻小说作家儒尔·凡尔纳的代表作之一。</p><p>作者让读者登上“鹦鹉螺号”，以平均十二公里的时速，在将近十个月的海底旅行中，随着尼摩船长和他的“客人们”饱览海底变幻无穷的奇异景观和各类生物；航程中高潮迭起，有海底狩猎，参观海底森林，探访海底亚特兰蒂斯废墟，打捞西班牙沉船的财宝，目睹珊瑚王国的葬礼，与大蜘蛛、鲨鱼、章鱼搏斗，击退土著人的围攻等等。</p><p>十九世纪下半叶，“异国风情”曾受到不少作家，画家的青睐和读者的追捧，《海底两万里》的奇妙旅行为异域风情另辟蹊径，使人耳目一新；这就是为什么这部“海洋小说”不仅在当时一出版即成为畅销书，而且日后受到一代又一代读者欢迎的原因。</p>', '<p> this book is the world-famous French science fiction writer of Confucianism, one of the representative work of Jules verne. </p> <p> boarded the \"nautilus\", the author give readers with an average of 12 kilometers an hour, travel, at the bottom of nearly 10 months as captain nemo and his guests\' get a good view of the sea is endless landscapes and all kinds of creatures; Voyage climaxes, has the seabed hunting, the visit seabed forest, the visitation seabed the ruins of Atlantis, salvaging sunken treasure in Spain, witnessed the coral kingdom the funeral, and big spiders, shark, the octopus fight, repel the natives siege, and so on. </p> <p> in the second half of the nineteenth century, \"exotic\" had been a lot of writers, the favour of artist and the reader, the wonderful adventures of the submarine two miles \"for the path of different region amorous feelings, make people find everything new and fresh. This is why the \"ocean\" novels not only at the time a publication that became a bestseller, and welcomed by generations of readers in the future. </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508044019', '遇见未知的自己', 'images/遇见未知的自己.jpg', '华夏出版社', '励志', '21.75', '29', '<p>故事从“冬天的雨夜，在荒郊野外的山区，一个没有手机、没有汽油的孤单女人”开始。</p><p>若菱，自名校毕业，拥有令人羡慕的工作，但心中却不时的自问：为什么我不能拥有想要的生活？为什么我不快乐？我该如何当自己生命的主人？在一个下雨的冬夜，若菱巧遇一名智慧老者，在与智者数度交谈的过程中，她渐渐填补不快乐、挫败的心灵缺口，寻回最真实勇敢的自我……你会不会担心和若菱一样，让身体的疲惫失控于华丽的业绩之中？你是否也想遇见在你心中的智慧老者，穿越心事的重重黑纱，遇见全新的自己？</p>', '<p> stories from \"the winter rainy night, in the wild mountains, a lonely woman\" no phones, no gasoline. </p> <p> if ling, graduating from school, has an enviable work, but in the heart from time to time ask yourself: why can\'t I have wanted to life? Why don\'t I be happy? How can I be the master of his own life? On a rainy night, if ling bumped into a wise old man, in the process of talking with a wise man several times, she gradually fill unhappy, frustration mind gap, to locate the most real brave... If you will not worry and ling, let the body tired is out of control in the magnificent performance? Do you want to meet in your heart the wisdom of the elders, the heavy veil across the heart to meet new yourself? </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787542629586', '民主的细节', 'images/民主的细节.jpg', '上海三联书店', '政治', '18.75', '25', '<p>这本书是作者过去几年给一些期刊报纸写的专栏文章结集，其中主要是给《南方人物周刊》的文章。全书中以讲故事的形式，把“美国的民主”这样一个概念性的东西拆解成点点滴滴的事件、政策和人物去描述。</p>', '< p > this book was in the past few years the authors give some journal newspaper column rally, mainly to the southern people weekly. In the form of a story in the book, \"American democracy\" such a conceptual thing apart into events of dribs and drabs, policy, and to describe characters. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530208922', '梦里花落知多少', 'images/梦里花落知多少.jpg', '北京十月文艺出版社', '情感', '21', '28', '<p>《梦里花落知多少》记录了荷西过世后三毛的生活，共23篇。内容均为台湾皇冠出版社81年至88年的初版。</p><p>荷西的死对三毛又是一场劫难，因此由《背影》到这本书，在文学、心情上都与早期大不相同，说情叙事极其内敛，但在曲折的空间之余，读者当能感受到三毛哀而不伤的笔调里，更多的其实是三毛对人生的坚定。</p>', '< p > the flowers in the dream records the jose SAN MAO\'s life after death, a total of 23 articles. Content of Taiwan crown publishing house, 81-88). < / p > < p > jose to SAN MAO is the death of a disaster, so by the \"back\" to the book, in the literature, the mood is very different from the early, based on the narrative very inside collect, but in the space of the twists and turns, the reader when feel SAN MAO mourning without harming the tone, more is actually three hair to the life of a firm. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787539628042', '鬼吹灯之精绝古城', 'images/鬼吹灯之精绝古城.jpg', '安徽文艺出版社', '悬疑', '18.75', '25', '<p>胡八一上山下乡来到中蒙边境的岗岗营子，带上了家中仅存的一本书——《十六字风水秘术》，闲来无事将书中文字背得滚瓜烂熟。之后参军到西藏，遇上雪崩掉落一条巨大的地沟当中，胡八一利用自己懂得的墓葬秘术逃得不死。复员后，胡八一和好友胖子一起加入了一支前往新疆考古的考古队。一行人历经万险来到了塔克拉玛干沙漠中的精绝古城遗址，进入了地下“鬼洞”。洞中机关重重、陷阱不断，这神秘的鬼洞似乎在住先知的掌控之中……</p>', '< p > hu bayi in the countryside to our border post of the camp, only brought home a book - \"16-character hermetic feng shui\", will be free and at leisure text in the book the back too thoroughly. After the army into Tibet, met avalanche drop a huge gutter, hu bayi to use its own know tombs hermetic fled to die. Demobilized, hu joined together a travel to xinjiang bayi and friend fat man archaeological team. A line of people after all risks to the clue of the taklamakan desert ruins of ancient city, into the underground hole \"ghost\". Cave in and trap, the mysterious ghost cave seems to be in the hands of the prophet... < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787539989891', '巨人的陨落', 'images/巨人的陨落.jpg', '江苏凤凰文艺出版社', '历史', '97.35', '129.8', '<p>在第一次世界大战的硝烟中，每一个迈向死亡的生命都在热烈地生长——威尔士的矿工少年、刚失恋的美国法律系大学生、穷困潦倒的俄国兄弟、富有英俊的英格兰伯爵，以及痴情的德国特工…从充满灰尘和危险的煤矿到闪闪发光的皇室宫殿，从代表着权力的走廊到爱恨纠缠的卧室，五个家族迥然不同又纠葛不断的命运逐渐揭晓，波澜壮阔地展现了一个我们自认为了解，但从未如此真切感受过的20世纪。</p>', '< p > in the smoke of the first world war, every life towards death in growth, welsh miners teenager, warmly just brokenhearted of the school of law students, the poverty of the Russian brothers, rich and handsome England earl, the great German agents and... From dusty and dangerous mines to gleaming royal palace, from representing the corridors of power to love hate the bedroom, the family of five different again entanglements unceasingly gradually revealed, and the fate of spectacular shows a we think about, but never so really had the 20th century. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787531719199', '一只特立独行的猪', 'images/一只特立独行的猪.jpg', '北方文艺出版社', '文学', '14.1', '18.8', '<p>这本书里除了文化杂文，还有给其他书写的序言与跋语。这些序言与跋语也表明了我的一些态度。除此之外，还有一些轻松的随笔。不管什么书，我都不希望它太严肃，这一本也不例外。</p><p>——王小波</p>', '< p > in addition to cultural essays in this book, and the other for the writing of preface and BaYu. The preface and BaYu also shows some of my attitude. Besides, there are some light essays. No matter what, I don\'t want it too seriously, this one is no exception. < / p > < p > - wang < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530208694', '半生缘', 'images/半生缘.jpg', '北京十月文艺出版社', '情感', '21', '28', '<p>他和曼桢认识，已经是多年前的事了。算起来倒已经有十四年了——真吓人一跳！马上使他连带地觉得自己已老了许多。日子过得真快，尤其对于中年以后的人，十年八年都好像是指顾间的事。可是对于年轻人，三年五载就可以是一生一世。他和曼桢从认识到分手，不过几年的工夫，这几年里面却经过这么许多事情，仿佛把生老病死一切的哀乐都经历到了。</p><p>曼桢曾经问过他，他是什么时候起开始喜欢她的。他当然回答说：“第一次看见的时候。”说那句话的时候是在那样的一种心醉的情形下，简直什么都可以相信，自己当然绝对相信那不是谎话。其实他到底是什么时候第一次看见她的，根本就记不清楚了。</p>', '< p > his frame, and the man was already many years ago. Count up and down already has 14 years - was frightening to jump! Immediately made him turn many feel is old. How time flies, especially for middle age people, ten years eight years seem nothing between. But for the young, in a few years can be for life. He and mann frame from the know to break up, but a few years time, in recent years, however, after so many things inside, as if all physical sorrows had arrived. < / p > < p > mann frame once asked him, what time is he began to like her. Of course he replied, \"to see for the first time.\" Say that sentence is situation in such a kind of enchantment, can what all can believe myself, of course, absolutely sure it\'s not a lie. In fact he is when I first saw her, simply can not remember clearly chu. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787802443914', '华胥引（全二册）', 'images/华胥引（全二册）.jpg', '现代出版社', '情感', '29.85', '39.8', '<p>《华胥引(套装共2册)》主要内容包括：华胥一引，乱世成殇。琴弦震响于九州列国之上，无声惊动。这是一个发生在乱世的故事。城破之日，卫国公主叶蓁以身殉国，依靠鲛珠死而复生。当她弹起华胥调，便生死人肉白骨，探入梦境与回忆。幻术构成的曲谱里，尽是人世的辛酸与苦涩。而她与亡她国家的陈国世子一次一次于幻境中相遇，身份两重，缘也两重。清平华胥调，能不能让每个人追回旧日的思念，不再悲伤？</p>', '< p > the China professional led (set of 2 copies) mainly includes: a professional guide, gone into ruin. String moro in kyushu, kingdoms silent alarmed. This is a story of gone with. City break, on the day of the princess wei ye stand with killed, rely on shark bead back from the dead. When she bounces China professional, RouBaiGu is man life and death into dreams and memories. Illusion of a song, but almost all the bitterness of human life and bitter. And she with Chen wu she countries fixed one at a time is inferior to that meet in the dreamland, identity is twofold, edge is twofold. Qingping China professional tone, can let everyone recover old thoughts, no longer sad? < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020019526', '格林童话全集', 'images/格林童话全集.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '儿童', '16.0875', '21.45', '<p>《格林童话全集》是德国民间故事集。由德国的雅各・格林和威廉・格林兄弟根据民间口述材料改写而成。他们搜集、整理、出版这些民间童话的目的，正如威廉所说，是&#34;希望它成为一本有教育意义的书，因为我再也想不出什么更富有教益，更天真无邪，更令人心旷神怡的读物，能比它更适合于儿童的心性与能力了。&#34;作品的主要内容是颂扬勤劳和诚实，鄙弃懒惰和自私，鼓励对暴力和邪恶的反抗，激发对被压迫者的同情和爱护。</p><p>书中的200多个故事，大部分源自民问的口头传说，因而比较正确地反映了当时人民的思想感情。其中的《灰姑娘》、《白雪公主》、《小红帽》、《青蛙王子》等童话故事，脍炙人口，享誉世界。作品问世一百多年来，已被译成70多种文字，在世界各国广为流传，成为各地收集民间故事的范例。</p>', '< p > complete works \"Grimm\'s fairy tales is German folk tales. By German ・ Jacob and Wilhelm Grimm ・ rewrite the brothers Grimm, according to the folk oral material. They the purpose of collecting, organizing, publishing these folk fairy tales, as William said, it is', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544722766', '杀死一只知更鸟', 'images/杀死一只知更鸟.jpg', '译林出版社', '文学', '24', '32', '<p>成长总是个让人烦恼的命题。成长有时会很缓慢，如小溪般唱着叮咚的歌曲趟过，有时却如此突如其来，如暴雨般劈头盖脸……三个孩子因为小镇上的几桩冤案经历了猝不及防的成长——痛苦与迷惑，悲伤与愤怒，也有温情与感动。这是爱与真知的成长经典。</p><p>《杀死一只知更鸟》获1961年普利策奖。</p><p>美国图书馆借阅率最高的书，英国青少年最喜爱的小说之一。</p><p>美国中学推荐课外读物。</p><p>由小说改编的电影获第25届奥斯卡三项大奖。</p><p>美国电影协会评选的“100名银幕英雄与恶人”中，派克主演的芬奇律师名列英雄第一位。</p><p>作为史上最受喜爱的小说之一，《杀死一只知更鸟》已获得显赫声誉。它赢得过普利策奖，被翻译成四十多种语言，在世界范围内售出超过三千万册，并曾被拍成，备受欢迎的电影。</p><p>——哈珀•柯林斯出版集团</p><p>斯塔尔六月对北卡罗来纳州律师协会发表演说时，自比为《杀死一只知更鸟》中勇敢的南方白人律师阿蒂克斯•芬奇。斯塔尔凭着他的道德优越感，不把规则、秩序和正直放在眼里，这样一个人居然自比为芬奇，实在令我和比尔难以忍受。</p><p>——希拉里•克林顿</p><p>年轻时看过《梅岗城故事》（即《杀死一只知更鸟》），对片中法律人为弱势者争取权益奋斗，为恶法非法或恶法亦法辩论的故事感到澎湃不已，更加确定要成为法律人的心愿。</p><p>——许宗力（台大法学院院长）</p>', '< p > growth is always a disturbing proposition. Grow slowly, sometimes like a stream, singing wade ding dong songs, sometimes it is so sudden, as torrential rain swept over... Three children because several errors in a small town in the growth of experienced off-guard, pain and confusion, sadness and anger, have a soft and moving. This is love and the growth of the real classic. < / p > < p > \"to kill a mockingbird\" won the Pulitzer prize in 1961. < / p > < p > the top JieYueLv library books in the United States, one of the most favorite novel British teenagers. < / p > < p > the American high school recommends extracurricular reading. < / p > < p > by the novel won the 25th Oscar awards. < / p > < p > the motion picture association of America\'s 100 hero of the silver screen and the wicked, peck starred Vinci lawyer hero first. < / p > < p > as one of history\'s most popular novels, to kill a mockingbird \"had won a prestigious reputation. It won the Pulitzer prize, has been translated into 40 languages, sold more than thirty million copies worldwide, and has been made into a popular film. < / p > < p > - Harper Collins publishing group < / p > < p > starr in June during a speech to the all China lawyers association to north Carolina since than to kill a mockingbird \"brave in southern whites lawyer Artie, finch. Starr with his moral superiority, defying rules, order and integrity, since such a personal incredibly ratio of Vinci, really and bill unbearable to me. < / p > < p > -- Hillary Clinton < / p > < p > as a young man saw the story seemed to city (that is, \"to kill a mockingbird\"), for which legal rights struggle artificially weak, methods of evil in the illegal or bad law also debate stories are surging, more determined to be a legal person\'s wishes. < / p > < p > - voids (national Taiwan university law school dean) < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787201094359', '你今天真好看', 'images/你今天真好看.jpg', '雅众文化/天津人民出版社', '漫画', '29.25', '39', '<p>《你今天真好看》是一本清新暖萌的漫画集，收录了莉兹•克里莫150多张逗趣漫画。书中集结了所有你能想到的各种萌物，恐龙、棕熊、兔子、企鹅，甚至还有伞蜥、獾、土拨鼠、狐獴……在诙谐的对话中，它们展现出一种与生俱来的幽默感和令人艳羡的生活情趣。</p><p>你可能是书中任何一个动物，而书中的动物可能是你身边的任何一个人。</p><p>谁不曾享受过与父母的温情一刻？</p><p>谁没有被朋友的玩笑弄得一时语塞？</p><p>谁不会因自己反应慢半拍而哭笑不得？</p><p>这本书就是有这样的魔力让你不由自主地会心一笑。</p>', '< p > \"you look really nice today\" is a pure and fresh and warm of ManHuaJi, includes Liz, kerry\'s 150 funny cartoon. Assembled in the book all you can think of all kinds of objects, dinosaurs, bears, rabbits, penguins, and even a frilled lizard, badger, marmots, juveniles... In the witty dialogue, they show a natural sense of humour and enviable life interest. < / p > < p > you could be any animal in the book, and the animals in the book could be any one around you. < / p > < p > who never enjoy a tender moment with your parents? < / p > < p > who have not been friends jokes made was speechless? < / p > < p > who won\'t because their reactions are slower and distress situation? < / p > < p > this book is to have such a magic let you to smile involuntarily. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108012586', '射雕英雄传（全四册）', 'images/射雕英雄传（全四册）.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '武侠', '35.25', '47', '<p>《射雕英雄传》是金庸的代表作之一，作于一九五七年到一九五九年，在《香港商报》连载。《射雕》中的人物个性单纯，郭靖诚朴厚重、黄蓉机智狡狯，读者容易印象深刻。这是中国传统小说和戏剧的特征，但不免缺乏人物内心世界的复杂性。由于人物性格单纯而情节热闹，所以《射雕》比较得到欢迎，被拍成各种语种的电影和电视剧在全球众多国家和地区热播。</p>', '<p> \"the legend of the condor heroes\" is one of jin yong\'s representative works, from 1957 to 1959, in the \"Hong Kong commercial daily\" series. \"Shoot diao\" character of the pure, guo jing honest massiness, huang2 rong2 wit crafty, readers easily impressed. This is the characteristics of the traditional Chinese novel and drama, but not the lack of character of the complexity of the inner world. Due to the character simple plot, so compare with \"shoot diao\" welcome, be made into various languages of film and TV hit so many countries and regions around the world. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787550213524', '一个人的朝圣', 'images/一个人的朝圣.jpg', '北京联合出版公司', '文学', '24.6', '32.8', '<p>★2013年欧洲首席畅销小说，入围2012年布克文学奖，同名电影拍摄中</p><p>★台湾读者表示“很久没有读一本书读到凌晨”、“是一个简单、素朴但会令人深深感动的故事”、“笑泪交织的阅读”</p><p>★2013年春季英国最具影响力“理查与茱蒂”读书俱乐部书单第1名；欧普拉读书俱乐部夏日选书、美国图书馆协会选书；2012年英国最畅销新人小说；《出版人周刊》、《纽约时报》、《泰晤士报》、《嘉人》、《今日美国》等各大媒体高评价推荐</p><p>★他以为人生就这么过去了，直到收到那封信</p><p>★1个人，87天，627英里</p><p>★有关爱的回归、自我发现、日常生活的信念以及万物之美</p><p>★这一年，我们都需要哈罗德安静而勇敢的陪伴</p><p>哈罗德·弗莱，六十岁，在酿酒厂干了四十年销售代表后默默退休，没有升迁，既无朋友，也无敌人，退休时公司甚至连欢送会都没开。他跟隔阂很深的妻子住在英国的乡间，生活平静，夫妻疏离，日复一日。</p><p>一天早晨，他收到一封信，来自二十年未见的老友奎妮。她患了癌症，写信告别。震惊、悲痛之下，哈罗德写了回信，在寄出的路上，他由奎妮想到了自己的人生，经过了一个又一个邮筒，越走越远，最后，他从英国最西南一路走到了最东北，横跨整个英格兰。87天，627英里，只凭一个信念：只要他走，老友就会活下去！</p><p>这是哈罗德千里跋涉的故事。从他脚步迈开的那一刻起，与他六百多英里旅程并行的，是他穿越时光隧道的另一场旅行。</p>', '< p > 2013 European chief best-selling novel, shortlisted for the booker prize in 2012, with the same name in the film < / p > < p > to end Taiwan\'s readers said \"haven\'t read a book to read the morning\", \"is a simple, naive but is deeply moved by the story\", \"laugh tears interweave reading\" < / p > < p > to end the spring of 2013, Britain\'s most influential \"Richard and Judy\" book club books first place; Oprah\'s book club choosing books in summer, the American library association\'s choosing books; In 2012, Britain\'s most popular new novels; Publishers weekly, the New York times, The Times, Marie Claire, USA today, each big media, such as high assessment recommended < / p > < p > u he thought that life is so in the past, until you receive the letter < / p > < p > painted one, 87 days, 627 miles < / p > < p > u about the return of love, self discovery, the beauty of the beliefs and daily life < / p > < p > to end this year, we all need quiet and brave Harold with < / p > < p > Harold fry, 60 years old, in the winery for forty years quietly retired after sales representative, no promotion, no friends, no enemy, retired company even haven\'t open farewell party. He gap is deep and his wife lived in the country, calm life, couples apart, day after day. < / p > < p > one morning, he received a letter, from twenty years did not see old friends queenie. She had cancer, and write goodbye. Under the shock and grief, Harold, I wrote on the way to send him by queenie thought of his life, after a mailbox, another more walk more far, in the end, he came to the northeast, all the way from the southwest of Britain\'s most across the England. 87 days, 627 miles, only by a belief that as long as he walked, the old friends will survive! < / p > < p > this is a story of Harold distances. From the moment he steps towards, more than six hundred miles journey in parallel with him, he is traveling through the time tunnel to another. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535436740', '陪安东尼度过漫长岁月', 'images/陪安东尼度过漫长岁月.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '情感', '13.5', '18', '<p>《陪安东尼度过漫长岁月》收集了作者安东尼在《最小说》上刊登过的部分散文，以及50%以上的最新作品。安东尼以一个普通男生的口吻，讲述了从20到23、从大学到工作、从国内到国外的真诚记载。其中既有生活的零散片段、自言自语，也有对生活的感悟。以时间为载体，散文为格式，将日记、随笔，甚至是墙上的便条联系到一起。带领每位读者陪安东尼度过遥远的旅行、孤独的时刻，以及漫长的岁月。</p><p>插画家ECHO配以温馨童话般的绘图，充满童幻色彩。</p>', '< p > author collected with Anthony in long time Anthony was carried out on the \"most novel\" part of the essay, as well as the latest work on the � 50. Anthony in a tone of ordinary men, tells the story from 20 to 23, from university to work, from domestic to abroad sincerely. Some fragments of life, to himself, also have the feeling of life. With time as the carrier, prose for the format, the diary, essays, and even the note on the wall. Lead every reader with Anthony in distant journey, lonely time, and a long time. < / p > < p > illustrator ECHO with sweet fairy tale plot, full of children\'s unreal colour. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535442215', '这些都是你给我的爱', 'images/这些都是你给我的爱.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '情感', '18.6', '24.8', '<p>《这些都是你给我的爱》讲述兔子男孩安东尼失恋后，为找寻曾经恋人一心向往的那棵“开满鲜花的树”，而环游旅行的故事。延续安东尼一贯深受读者青睐的无标点文字风格，用淡淡的语言，倾吐少年恋慕和成长的酸涩心事。</p>', '< p > \"these are all the love you gave me about the rabbit Anthony brokenhearted, the boy to look for the tree of pilgrimage ever lovers\" full of flowers \", the travel story. Continuation of Anthony has always favored by readers without punctuation character style, with light language, pour out the young to learn and grow the sour. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787100040945', '如何阅读一本书', 'images/如何阅读一本书.jpg', '商务印书馆', '教辅', '28.5', '38', '<p>每本书的封面之下都有一套自己的骨架，作为一个分析阅读的读者，责任就是要找出这个骨架。一本书出现在面前时，肌肉包着骨头，衣服包裹着肌肉，可说是盛装而来。读者用不着揭开它的外衣或是撕去它的肌肉来得到在柔软表皮下的那套骨架，但是一定要用一双X光般的透视眼来看这本书，因为那是了解一本书、掌握其骨架的基础。</p><p>《如何阅读一本书》初版于1940年，1972年大幅增订改写为新版。不懂阅读的人，初探阅读的人，读这本书可以少走冤枉路。对阅读有所体会的人，读这本书可以有更深的印证和领悟。</p>', '< p > under the cover of every book has its own set of skeleton, as an analysis of readers to read, duty is to find out the skeleton. A book appeared on the front, wrapped in bone, muscle clothes wrapped in muscle, is dressed up. Readers don\'t have to reveal its coat or torn off its muscles to get the skeleton set under the soft skin, but must use a pair of X-ray perspective eye to see the book, because it is the foundation of understand a book, grasp its skeleton. < / p > < p > \"how to read a book first published in 1940, 1972, vary significantly for the new. Around people who do not read, read, read the book can go less success. Has experience for reading, reading the book can better support and understanding. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787802282674', '喜宝', 'images/喜宝.jpg', '新世界出版社', '文学', '16.5', '22', '<p>读书就是这样好，无论心不在焉，板着长脸，只要考试及格，就是一个及格的人。你试着拉长脸到社会去试一试。这是一个卖笑的社会。除非能够找到高贵的职业，而高贵的职业需要高贵的学历支持，高贵的学历需要金钱，始终兜回来。</p><p>富家女勖聪慧热情地邀请刚认识的剑桥高材生姜喜宝参加自己的家宴，有意制造机会以撮合她和哥哥勋聪恕。聪慧的父亲勋存姿，也向喜宝展开追求。喜宝在其父亲、儿子的双双夹击下，非常现实地选择了父亲，她得到了想得到的一切甚至更多。喜宝做了勖存姿的女人后，虽然得到了金钱与物质上的满足，但却耐不住感情与生理上的寂寞和空虚。勖存姿发现喜宝另有所爱，竟冷酷地当着喜宝的面，枪杀了她的男友。喜宝绝望了，但她怎么也逃不脱勖存姿的牢笼。几年后，勖存姿去世，喜宝变成最富有的女人，但是……</p>', '<p> reading is so good, no matter in the clouds, board face, as long as you pass the exam, is a man in the exam. You try a long face to the society to give it a try. This is a \'society. Unless I can find the noble career, and noble vocational need noble education support, high degree need money, take back all the time. </p> <p> rich girl Xu intelligent warmly invited just know Cambridge luminaries ginger diary to own family dinner, deliberately opportunity to fix to chung by her and her brother. Wise father stand posture, also to the pursuit of diary. Diary in its combination of both father and son, very realistic chose his father, she got all want even more. Diary do Xu stock after the appearance of a woman, although the money and material meet, but could not bear loneliness and emptiness of emotional and physical. Xu appearance discovered another love diary, unexpectedly ruthlessly in front of the diary, shot and killed her boyfriend. Diary of despair, but she could not flee Xu posture cage. A few years later, the Xu appearance died, become the richest woman diary, but... </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108033635', '孩子你慢慢来', 'images/孩子你慢慢来.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '情感', '21', '28', '<p>作为华人世界最有影响的一支笔，龙应台的文章有万丈豪气，然而《孩子你慢慢来》却令人惊叹，她的文字也可以有款款深情。这本书里的龙应台是一个母亲，作为母亲的龙应台和作为一个独立的人的龙应台有着丰富、激烈的内心冲突，而正是通过对这一冲突的诉说，表现出她内心深处的母爱。但它不是传统母爱的歌颂，是对生命的实景写生，只有真正懂得爱的作家才写得出这样的生活散文。</p><p>十五年前龙应台以一位母亲的亲身经验写下《孩子你慢慢来》，她在书中说：“谁能告诉我做女性和做个人之间怎么平衡？我爱极了做母亲，只要把孩子的头放在我胸口，就能使我觉得幸福。可是我也是个需要极大的内在空间的个人……女性主义者，如果你不曾体验过生养的喜悦和痛苦，你究竟能告诉我些什么呢？”</p><p>十五年过去，龙应台不仅成为华文界最有影响力的一枝笔，也以她自己的智慧走出女性在个人事业和母亲角色的冲突，而这本书也给无数读者带来感动和启迪。</p><p>在《孩子你慢慢来》出版十五周年之际，三联书店推出全新简体版：大开本彩色印刷，精美呈现数十幅龙应台私家珍藏照片；特别收录龙应台的孩子：少年华飞、青年华安在该书出版十周年时所撰的跋——看华文世界最受瞩目的女性，原来她是这样做妈妈的。</p>', '< p > as the world\'s most influential Chinese pen, lung ying-tai articles have great heroism, but the children you take amazing, her words also can have a leisurely affectionate. Lung ying-tai in this book is a mother, a mother of lung ying-tai and as an independent human lung ying-tai has a rich, intense inner conflict, and it is through to the conflict, showing her deep mother love. But it is not the traditional maternal love, is the live of life sketch, if you really understand love prose writer to write such life. Lung ying-tai < / p > < p > 15 years ago in a mother\'s personal experience to write down \"the children you take your time,\" she said in the book: \"who can tell me how to balance between women and do people? I loved being a mother, as long as the child\'s head on my chest, you can make me feel happy. But I am also a requires a great deal of inner space of the individual... Feminist, if you have never experienced the joy of raising and misery, what can you tell me?\" < / p > < p > in the past 15 years, not only become the most influential of a pen HuaWenJie lung ying-tai, also with her own wisdom out of the women in the personal career and mother role conflict, but the book also bring numerous readers moved and enlightenment. < / p > < p > in the 15th anniversary of the publication of children you take your time, sanlian bookstore: a new simplified edition of large-type color printing, exquisitely rendered dozens of images of lung ying-tai private collection; Special features of lung ying-tai child: young lg philips, youth safe when the 10th anniversary of the book was published by colophon - see the Chinese language of the world\'s most high-profile women, she is a mother to do so. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544717731', '这些人，那些事', 'images/这些人，那些事.jpg', '译林出版社', '情感', '21', '28', '<p>吴念真累积多年、珍藏心底的体会与感动。</p><p>他写的每个故事，都蕴藏了我们无法预知的生命能量与心灵启发。</p><p>跟他一起回望人生种种，您将学会包容、豁达与感恩……</p><p>本书是吴念真导演经历过人生的风风雨雨和最大低潮后，所完成的生命记事。</p><p>他用文字写下心底最挂念的家人、日夜惦记的家乡、一辈子搏真情的朋友，以及台湾各个角落里最真实的感动。这些人和事，透过他真情挚意的笔，如此跃然的活在你我眼前，笑泪交织的同时，也无可取代的成为烙印在你我心底、这一个时代的美好缩影……</p><p>特别收录吴念真近年唯一小说创作《遗书》，写下对胞弟离开人间的真情告白</p><p>特别邀请作家雷骧绘制插画，看两位大师以图文激荡出精采火花</p><p>生命里某些当时充满怨怼的曲折，在后来好像都成了一种能量和养分……这些人、那些事在经过时间的筛滤之后，几乎都只剩下笑与泪与感动和温暖。——《这些人，那些事》</p>', '< p > nj wu accumulated for many years, experience and touched his heart. < / p > < p > every story he wrote, is our unpredictable life energy and spirit. < / p > < p > with him back at all the life, you will learn to tolerant, open-minded and thanks... < / p > < p > this book is director of nj wu has experienced the ups and downs of life and maximum lows, done for life. < / p > < p > he used words to write down the family with the bottom of my heart, day and night miss hometown, lifetime beat true friends, in every corner and Taiwan moved most real. These people and things, through his true feelings zhi pen, so vividly alive in front of my eyes, you smile tears interweave, irreplaceable be imprinted in my mind you, this wonderful epitome of an era... < / p > < p > special features nj wu \"suicide note\" in recent years, the only novel, to write brother left earth\'s confession < / p > < p > special invited writer LeiXiang draw illustrations, watching two masters in graphic produced an excellent spark < / p > < p > in my life some twists and turns of hatred at the time, in the later seems to have become a kind of energy and nutrient... These people, those things in the after time of screen, are almost only smile and tears and moved and warm. - \"these people, those things\" < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806812297', '麦琪的礼物', 'images/麦琪的礼物.jpg', '上海社会科学院出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>选收欧·亨利的小说34篇，国外当代文学类重要工具书介绍的有代表性的作品均已收入。欧·亨利是位有独特风格的杰出短篇小说家，以巧妙的构思、夸张和幽默的文笔反映了他那个时代的人和事。</p>', '< p > XuanShou O. Henry\'s novel, 34, foreign important reference book to introduce the representative works of contemporary literature have income. O. Henry is a brilliant short story writer, has a unique style with clever conception, exaggeration and humorous style of writing reflects the people and things in his own time. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535438379', '流浪地球', 'images/流浪地球.jpg', '湖北长江出版集团，长江文艺出版社', '科幻', '21', '28', '<p>此书为刘慈欣获中国科幻银河奖的中短篇科幻小说作品集，收录有《流浪地球》《乡村教师》《全频带阻塞干扰》等获奖佳作。</p>', '< p > this book for Chinese sci-fi galaxy award went to liu\'s collection of science fiction, with the \"rural teacher\" stray globe \"full band blocking interference\" and other awards. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806579060', '查令十字街84号', 'images/查令十字街84号.jpg', '译林出版社', '情感', '13.5', '18', '<p>这本被全球人深深钟爱的书，记录了纽约女作家海莲和一家伦敦旧书店的书商弗兰克之间的书缘情缘。双方二十年间始终未曾谋面，相隔万里，深厚情意却能莫逆于心。无论是平淡生活中的讨书买书论书，还是书信中所蕴藏的难以言明的情感，都给人以强烈的温暖和信任。这本书既表现了海莲对书的激情之爱，也反映了她对弗兰克的精神之爱。海莲的执著、风趣、体贴、率真，跳跃于一封封书信的字里行间，使阅读成为一种愉悦而柔软的经历。来往的书信被海莲汇集成此书，被译成数十种文字流传。</p><p>译者陈建铭是台湾一位古旧书店的工作人员，他在未被出版方邀作译者之前，便凭着自己对《查令十字街84号》的热爱动手开始翻译其中的章节。</p><p>现在世间已无查令十字街84号的旧书店，但英国文学，古本图书，伦敦巷陌，书中的这些话题仍不断激起后来者的思念和共鸣。广播、舞台和银幕也钟情于这本爱书人的掌上明珠，每年都有世界各地的书迷到伦敦查令十字街朝圣，渐渐地，《查令十字街84号》成为全球爱书人之间的一个暗号。</p>', '< p > this book deeply loved by the world people, recorded the New York writer sea lotus and a London bookseller frank put love between old bookstore. Twenty years never seen on both sides, in miles, deep feeling can row is in the heart. Both insipid life for buy ShuLun book, or letters contain difficult emotion to say, give a person with strong warm and trust. This book shows the lotus of the sea of books of passionate love, also reflects the love of her spirit to frank. Sea lotus clinging, funny, thoughtful, sincere, jumping on a bounded letter between the lines, make reading a pleasure experience and soft. Letter is the lotus pool into the book, have been translated into dozens of languages. < / p > < p > the translator chien-ming Chen is a ancient bookstore staff in Taiwan, he was not in the publishers invited the translator before, they with to love of \"84 charing cross street\" to start translating the chapter. < / p > < p > now the world has no 84 charing cross street old bookstore, but the British literature, ancient books, alleys of London, the topic of the book continues to inspire others thoughts and resonance. Radio, stage and screen is passionate about love book people\'s eye, every year there are fans from all over the world to London pilgrimage to charing cross street, gradually, the 84 charing cross street to become the world\'s a secret code between book lovers. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020018567', '雷雨', 'images/雷雨.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '6.9', '9.2', '<p>《雷雨》所展示的是一幕人生大悲剧，是命运对人残忍的作弄。专制、伪善的家长，热情、单纯的青年，被情爱烧疯了心的魅惑的女人，痛悔着罪孽却又不自知地犯下更大罪孽的公子哥，还有家庭的秘密，身世的秘密，所有这一切在一个雷雨夜爆发。有罪的，无辜的人一起走向毁灭。曹禺以极端的雷雨般狂飙恣肆的方式，发泄被抑压的愤懑，毁谤中国的家庭和社会。</p>', '< p > is shown \"thunderstorm\" is a great tragedy in life, fate is cruel torment to people. Authoritarian parents, hypocritical, enthusiasm, pure youth, is love burning mad heart charm of a woman, filled with iniquity without self-knowledge make greater sin constantly chauffeured, and family\'s secret, the secret of life, all that broke out in a thunderstorm night. The guilty and innocent people together to destruction. Works with extreme thunderstorm as hurricane arrogant way, venting is the suppression of anger, curse the family and the society of China. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020008735', '西游记（全二册）', 'images/西游记（全二册）.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '魔幻', '35.4', '47.2', '<p>《西游记》主要描写的是孙悟空保唐僧西天取经，历经九九八十一难的故事。唐僧取经是历史上一件真实的事。大约距今一千三百多年前，即唐太宗贞观元年（627），年仅25岁的青年和尚玄奘离开京城长安，只身到天竺（印度）游学。他从长安出发后，途经中亚、阿富汗、巴基斯坦，历尽艰难险阻，最后到达了印度。他在那里学习了两年多，并在一次大型佛教经学辩论会任主讲，受到了赞誉。贞观十九年（645）玄奘回到了长安，带回佛经657部。他这次西天取经，前后十九年，行程几万里，是一次传奇式的万里长征，轰动一时。后来玄奘口述西行见闻，由弟子辩机辑录成《大唐西域记》十二卷。但这部书主要讲述了路上所见各国的历史、地理及交通，没有什么故事。及到他的弟子慧立、彦琮撰写的《大唐大慈恩寺三藏法师传》，则为玄奘的经历增添了许多神话色彩，从此，唐僧取经的故事便开始在民间广为流传。南宋有《大唐三藏取经诗话》，金代院本有《唐三藏》、《蟠桃会》等，元杂剧有吴昌龄的《唐三藏西天取经》、无名氏的《二郎神锁齐大圣》等，这些都为《西游记》的创作奠定了基础。吴承恩也正是在民间传说和话本、戏曲的基础上，经过艰苦的再创造，完成了这部令中华民族为之骄傲的伟大大文学巨著。</p>', '< p > \"journey to the west\" is mainly about the Monkey King tang\'s monk to obtain buddhist scriptures, through the wringer. Tang\'s monk scriptures is a real thing in history. Dating back about one thousand three hundred years ago, that is, the first year of emperor taizong dynasty (627), the 25-year-old young monk xuan zang to leave the capital chang \'an, alone to travel and study in tianzhu (India). After he set out from changan, via central Asia, Afghanistan, Pakistan, experienced the hardship, finally arrived in India. Where he studied for more than two years, and in a large buddhist classics debate on, by the praise. In drawing nineteen years (645) returned to chang \'an, xuan zang 657 back to the buddhist sutras. He was to obtain buddhist scriptures, nineteen years, before and after the trip in the tens of thousands of, is a legendary long journey, blockbuster. Later xuan zang west to the oral stories by disciple argue machine (into the twelve volumes of \"datang western regions. But this book mainly tells the story of the road can see national history, geography and traffic, no story. And to his disciple hui, YanCong wrote \"datang big temple monk biography of mage, the experience of xuan zang added many myths color, from then on, the story of tang\'s monk scriptures began in the civil widely circulated. Southern song dynasty has the experiences of the tang dynasty monk zhen, \"jin is therefore very helpful with the monk tang, the flat peach will, yuan drama have Wu Changling monk tang to obtain buddhist scriptures, anonymous\" er lang shen JiDaSheng lock \"and so on, these are for the creation of\" journey to the west \"laid a foundation. Wu chengen is on the basis of folklore and story-telling scripts, drama, created by the hard again, completed the makes the Chinese people proud of the great literary masterpieces. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020008742', '水浒传（全二册）', 'images/水浒传（全二册）.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '历史', '37.95', '50.6', '<p>《水浒传》是我国第一部以农民起义为题材的长篇章回小说，是我国文学史上一座巍然屹立的丰碑，也是世界文学宝库中一颗光彩夺目的明珠。数百年来，它一直深受我国人民的喜爱，并被译为多种文字，成为我国流传最为广泛的古代长篇小说之一。</p><p>《水浒传》具体而生动地描写了以宋江为首的农民起义发生、发展直至失财的整个过程，揭露了封建社会的黑暗、腐朽和统治阶级的种种罪恶，热情歌颂了起义英雄的反抗精神和正义行动，塑造了一大批梁山好汉的光辉形象，形象地揭示了封建社会“官逼民反”的客观真理和农民起义失败的内在原因。</p>', '< p > \"the water margin\" is China\'s first depicting the peasant uprising of zhanghui novel, is a monument to stand tall literature history in our country, is also a treasure house of world literature a dazzling pearl. For hundreds of years, it has been was deeply loved by Chinese people, and have been translated into many languages and become one of the most widely circulated in China ancient full-length novels. < / p > < p > \"the water margin\" concrete and vividly describes the development of peasant uprising, led by sung river, until the whole process of the loss of goods, revealed the feudal society of darkness and decay and the evils of the ruling class, warmly praised the rebel spirit of uprising hero and justice action, created a large number of liangshan glorious image, vividly reveals the objective truth of the feudal society \"civil revolt\" and the internal cause of the failure of the peasant uprising. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787100012935', '菊与刀', 'images/菊与刀.jpg', '商务印书馆', '文学', '12', '16', '<p>“菊”本是日本皇室家徽，“刀”是武士道文化的象征。美国人类学家鲁思・本尼迪克特用《菊与刀》来揭示日本人的矛盾性格亦即日本文化的双重性(如爱美而黩武、尚礼而好斗、喜新而顽固、服从而不驯等)……</p>', '< p > this is the royal house of Japan \"chrysanthemum\", \"dao\" is the symbol of bushido culture. American anthropologist ・ Ruth Benedict put the chrysanthemum and the sword to reveal the contradiction of the Japanese character that is the dualism of the Japanese culture (e.g., the love of beauty and bellicose, ShangLi and aggressive, new and stubborn, obedience and unruly, etc.)... < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532741922', '刀锋', 'images/刀锋.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '13.5', '18', '<p>威廉·萨默塞特·毛姆（1874-1965），英国著名小说家、戏剧家。《刀锋》是他的主要作品之一。</p><p>小说写一个参加第一次世界大战的美国青年飞行员拉里·达雷尔。在军队里，拉里结识了一个爱尔兰好友：这人平时是那样一个生龙活虎般的置生死于度外的飞行员，但在一次遭遇战中，因去救拉里而中弹牺牲。拉里因此对人生感到迷惘，弄不懂世界上为什么有恶和不幸，拉里开始了他令人匪夷所思的转变……</p>', '<p> William somerset maugham (1874-1965), a famous British novelist and dramatist. The blade is one of his major works. </p> <p> to write a novel in the first world war America\'s youth pilot larry Darrell. In the army, larry met an Irish friend: this man at ordinary times is such an alive outside of life and death in the degree of the pilot, but during an encounter, for to save larry shot sacrifice. Larry so perplexed at the life, can\'t understand why the world is an evil and unlucky, larry began his odd change... </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787531324362', '我与地坛', 'images/我与地坛.jpg', '春风文艺出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>收有“午餐半小时”、“我的遥远的清平湾”、“命若琴弦”、“第一人称”、“两个故事”等15篇史铁生的代表作。</p>', '<p> to receive a \"half an hour for lunch,\", \"my distant qingping bay\", \"life if the strings\", \"first person\", \"two stories\" and so on 15 shi masterpiece. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787807240648', '狂人日记', 'images/狂人日记.jpg', '京华出版社', '文学', '29.85', '39.8', '<p>《狂人日记》是鲁迅1918年发表的第一篇白话短篇小说，当时正值“五四”运动的前夜。由于辛亥革命的半途而废，特别是帝国主义侵略的加剧，使社会各种矛盾更加复杂尖锐。鲁迅以他锐敏的思想和犀利的笔触，对封建制度及其上层建筑表现了彻底的反抗。</p><p>《狂人日记》是中国现代文学史上第一篇真正的现代白话小说。令人惊异的是，这部中国现代小说史上具有开山意义的作品，已经显示出极其成熟的特色，使后来的许多研究者为之倾倒，究其原因，除了鲁迅深厚的文学素养外，我们也无法不叹服于先生的天才。</p>', '< p > the madman\'s diary is lu xun in 1918 published the first article in the vernacular short stories, just on the eve of the \"May 4th\" movement. Due to the revolution of give up, especially the imperialist aggression and make more complicated sharp social contradictions. Lu xun in his sharp mind and sharp strokes, the feudal system and the superstructure performance thoroughly. < / p > < p > a madman\'s diary is the history of Chinese modern literature the first real modern vernacular novel. Amazingly, the works of Chinese modern novel has a complete meaning, has shown extremely mature characteristics, made many later researchers, investigate its reason, in addition to lu xun\'s profound literary accomplishment, we can\'t not gasp in admiration to Mr\'s genius. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787540462642', '最好的我们', 'images/最好的我们.jpg', '湖南文艺出版社', '情感', '41.25', '55', '<p>你总是说青春从不曾永远，而那时候的我们，就是最好的我们。</p><p>这一次，我们和整个青春做告别。</p><p>八月长安全新力作。</p><p>你还记得高中时的同桌吗？那个少年有世界上最明朗的笑容，那个女生有世界上最好看的侧影。高中三年，两个人的影子和粉笔灰交织在一起，黑白分明，在记忆里面转圈。本书以怀旧的笔触讲述了女主角耿耿和男主角余淮同桌三年的故事，耿耿余淮，这么多年一路走过的成长故事极为打动人心，整个故事里有的都是在成长过程中细碎的点点滴滴，将怀旧写到了极致，将记忆也写到了极致。</p>', '< p > you always say youth never forever, but at that time we, is the best we have. < / p > < p > this time, we say goodbye to the youth do. < / p > < p > changan new works in August. < / p > < p > do you remember during the high school deskmate? The boy has the world\'s most bright smile, that girl has the world\'s most beautiful silhouette. High school three years, two shadow and chalk intertwined, black and white, in memory. Serve this book tells the story of the heroine in nostalgia of the brush and the story of three years, the hero Yu Huai a neighbor Yu Huai), over the years all the way through the growth of the story is, the whole story, some are in the process of growth and finely dribs and drabs, write a nostalgic to perfection, write memory to perfection. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506246743', '富爸爸，穷爸爸', 'images/富爸爸，穷爸爸.jpg', '世界图书出版公司', '社会', '14.1', '18.8', '<p>《富爸爸，穷爸爸》是一个真实的故事，作者罗伯特・清崎的亲生父亲和朋友的父亲对金钱的看法截然不同，这使他对认识金钱产生了兴趣，最终他接受了朋友的父亲的建议，也就是书中所说的。“富爸爸”的观念，即不要做金钱的奴隶，要让金钱为我们工作，并由此成为一名极富传奇色彩的成功的投资家。</p>', '< p > \"rich dad, poor dad\" is a true story, the author ・ Robert kiyosaki\'s biological father and friend\'s father for money have very different views, which made him interested in know money, in the end he accepted his friend\'s father\'s advice, which is what the book said. The idea of \"rich dad\", that is, don\'t be a slave of money, to make money work for us, and thus become a legendary investor of success. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787538262537', '地下铁', 'images/地下铁.jpg', '辽宁教育出版社', '社会', '24', '32', '<p>社会高速发展，来来往往的地下铁路成为了城市文明与社会生活的缩影，从入口到出口，地下铁路将你从起点带到终点，抑或是另一个起点。</p><p>故事讲一个失明的小女孩，在15岁生日当天，决定自己一个人在城市里探险。她战战兢兢地搭乘地下铁，从一个陌生的小站出发，前往另一个陌生的小站。旅途中，她一边回忆、拼凑、感觉、摸索这被黑暗笼罩的世界，“寻找心中隐约闪烁的光亮”，也同时感受到新的希望、新的方向，和新的生命力。随着小女孩的步伐，我们逐渐看清“地下铁”蕴涵的黑暗世界，也看见潜藏在黑暗中的质疑、希望与美丽幻想。</p><p>作者以绚丽的色彩和诗句般的内心读白，为读者创造出一种前所未见的阅读诗意。并通过绘图与文字的双重方式向读者进行述说与沟通，带领大家共同去寻找心中点滴的亮光。</p>', '< p > society high-speed development, and the underground railway became the epitome of urban civilization and social life, from inlet to outlet, underground railway will you from start to finish, or is another starting point. < / p > < p > story about a blind girl, in the 15th birthday, decided to a person in the city in search of adventure. She gingerly on the subway, from a strange station, go to another strange way station. Journey, she recalled, patchwork, groped feeling, this is the world of darkness, \"looking for heart faint flicker of light\", at the same time also feel new hopes, new direction, and a new vitality. With the pace of the little girl, we get to see \"underground\" contain the darkness of the world, also saw hidden in the dark challenge, hope with beautiful fantasy. < / p > < p > the author with gorgeous colour and verses read white inside, create an unprecedented for readers to read poetry. And through the way of graphics and text to the reader, speak and interact with everyone together to find a little light in my heart. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787105077502', '步步惊心', 'images/步步惊心.jpg', '民族出版社', '情感', '18.75', '25', '<p>一脚踏空的少女，穿越千年的时空，从繁华都市的深圳来到风云诡变的宫廷。正处于争位时候的阿哥们，款款深情的目光后，带着探究、带着诱惑也带着几分真真假假的心疼。她努力地想避开着历史的洪流，但那一双双幽暗深邃的眼睛却将拉住……</p>', '< p > a foot empty girl, through one thousand years of time and space, from the busy city of shenzhen to storm deceit in court. Is in the house when her brother, leisurely affectionate eyes, with the exploration, with the temptation also take a few minutes of true love. She trying to avoid the stream of history, but the pairs of darkness deep eyes will hold... < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536455382', '球状闪电', 'images/球状闪电.jpg', '四川科学技术出版社', '科幻', '16.5', '22', '<p>在某个离奇的雨夜，一颗球状闪电闯进了少年的视野。它的啸叫低沉中透着尖利，像是一个鬼魂在太古的荒原上吹着埙。当鬼魂奏完乐曲，球状闪电在一瞬间将少年的父母化为灰烬，而他们身下板凳却是奇迹般的冰凉。</p><p>这一夜，少年的命运被彻底改变了，他将毕其一生去解开那个将他变成孤儿的自然之谜。但是他未曾想到，多年以后，单纯的自然科学研究被纳入进“新概念武器”开发计划，他所追寻的球状闪电变成了下一场战争中决定祖国生存或是灭亡的终极武器！</p><p>当被禁锢在终极武器中的大自然的伟力被释放时，一轮冰冷的“蓝太阳”升起在大西部的戈壁滩上，整个戈壁淹没在它的蓝光中，这个世界变得陌生而怪异。一个从未有人想像过的未来，在宇宙观测者的注视下，降临在人类面前……</p>', '< p > in a surreal rainy night, a ball lightning broke into the young field of vision. It appearing in the the noise low sharp, like a ghost in the wasteland swire blowing two-string fiddle. When the ghost to play music, ball lightning in a moment will be reduced to ashes, young parents while they are on the bench is a miraculous cold. < / p > < p > this night, the boy\'s fate be changed, he will finish his life to solve that will he become orphans natural mystery. But he did not think of, over the years, pure natural science research is introduced into the \"new concept weapon\" development plan, he sought ball lightning decision becomes the next war country survival or the ultimate weapon of destruction! < / p > < p > when imprisoned in the nature of the process in the ultimate weapon is released, a cold \"blue\" the sun rises in the west of the gobi desert, the gobi drowned in its blue, the world become strange and weird. A future, ever imagined, under the gaze of the observer in the universe comes in front of the human... < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020033645', '尘埃落定', 'images/尘埃落定.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '16.5', '22', '<p>一个声势显赫的康巴藏族土司，在酒后和汉族太太生了一个傻瓜儿子。这个人人都认定的傻子与现实生活格格不入，却有着超时代的预感和举止，成为土司制度兴衰的见证人。小说故事精彩曲折动人，以饱含激情的笔墨，超然物外的审视目光，展现了浓郁的民族风情和土司制度的浪漫神秘。</p>', '<p> a most powerful kangba Tibetan tusi, the drunk and han Chinese wife gave birth to a son fools. The everyone that fool with real life, has a super era of foreboding and manners, become the rise and fall of the tusi system of witness. Novel fascinating twists and turns touching, pen and ink with passion, detached look at eyes, showing the rich ethnic customs and chieftain system of romantic mystery. </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020017164', '悲惨世界（上中下）', 'images/悲惨世界（上中下）.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '49.5', '66', '<p>这是法国十九世纪浪漫派领袖雨果继《巴黎圣母院》之后创作的又一部气势恢宏的鸿篇巨著。全书以卓越的艺术魅力，展示了一幅自1793年法国大革命至1832年巴黎人民起义期间，法国近代社会生活和政治生活的辉煌画卷，最大限度地体现了雨果在叙事方面的过人才华，是世界文学史上现实主义与浪漫主义结合的典范。小说集中反映了雨果的人道主义思想，饱含了雨果对于人类苦难命运的关心和对末来坚定不移的信念，具有震撼人心的艺术感染力。</p>', '< p > this is romantic in the 19th century French leader Hugo after \"Notre Dame DE Paris\" creation and a magnificent epic novel. Encyclopedia with outstanding artistic charm, shows a picture of the French revolution in 1793 to Paris in 1832 people\'s uprising period, modern French glory of social life and political life picture scroll, maximum limit embodies the outstanding talent of Hugo in narrative aspect, is the world\'s history of literature model of realism and romanticism combination. The novel reflects the humanitarian thoughts, Hugo from Hugo to concern for human suffering fate and the future unwavering faith, with impressive artistic appeal. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787539931494', '那些回不去的年少时光', 'images/那些回不去的年少时光.jpg', '江苏文艺出版社', '情感', '17.85', '23.8', '<p>最值得珍藏的怀旧读物，写给年少自己的书，纪念我们共同的青春和成长</p><p>您还记得上世纪最后十年的青春是怎样吗？那可是我们独一无二的成长！</p><p>那些回不去的年少时光》以真挚的感情，真实的细节，讲述了一段发生在那个年代精彩扣人的青春和爱——少女罗琦琦天性桀骜，从不妥协。青春期的她游走在两种截然不同的世界里：作业、考试、小团体的校园；游戏机房、歌舞厅、小混混斗殴泡妞的社会。她看着中国第一代歌舞厅开起来，第一批港台娱乐来到身边……</p><p>每个人的生活和思想都发生着剧变。她和伙伴们分享着甜蜜、忧伤、彷徨、迷惑……在本书中，你可以看到所有你曾热爱却正在遗忘的人和事，更可以看到属于自己的青春和成长。</p>', '< p > in the collection of the most worthy of nostalgia, to their own books, young memory of our youth and growth < / p > < p > do you remember the last decade of last century what is youth? That\'s our unique growth! < / p > < p > the time don\'t go to the young, and sincere feelings, real details, tells the story of a happens to people that s wonderful buckle unruly youth and love, young girl Luo Qiqi nature, never compromise. Adolescent she walk in two very different worlds: assignments, exams, clique\'s campus; Game rooms, dance halls, punks fight this society. She look at China\'s first generation of dance halls open up, the first batch of Hong Kong and Taiwan entertainment comes around... < / p > < p > shifting every person\'s life and thought. She and her partners to share the sweet and sorrow, hesitation, confused... In this book, you can see all of you who love the people and things are forgotten, the more you can see our own youth and growth. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563391271', '孤独六讲', 'images/孤独六讲.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '文学', '27', '36', '<p>美学大师蒋勋以美学家特有的思维和情感切入孤独，从情欲、语言、革命、思维、伦理、暴力六个面向阐释孤独美学，融个人记忆、美学追问、文化反思、社会批判于一体。可以说，蒋勋在本书中，创造了孤独美学：美学的本质或许就是孤独。</p><p>自序</p><p>情欲孤独</p><p>语言孤独</p><p>革命孤独</p><p>暴力孤独</p><p>思维孤独</p><p>伦理孤独</p>', '< p > master aesthetic Jiang Xun by aesthetes unique thinking and emotional loneliness, the flesh, language, revolution, thinking, ethical, violence, six for interpretation of the lonely aesthetics, individual memory, aesthetic inquiry, cultural and social criticism. Jiang Xun, as it were, in the book, has created a lonely aesthetics: the essence of aesthetics may be lonely. < / p > < p > introduction < / p > < p > passion alone < / p > < p > language alone < / p > < p > revolution alone < / p > < p > violence alone < / p > < p > thinking alone < / p > < p > ethics alone < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530640470', '呼兰河传', 'images/呼兰河传.jpg', '百花文艺出版社', '文学', '14.25', '19', '<p>萧红，中国现代著名女作家。1911年6月2日生于黑龙江呼兰县，1942年1月22日病殁香港。原名张迺莹，笔名萧红、悄吟等。幼年丧母，父亲性格暴戾，她只有从年迈的祖父那里享受到些许人间温暖，寂寞的童年形成了萧红性格中孤独、敏感、矜持而又倔强的一面。</p><p>1927年到哈尔滨读中学，接触了五四以来的进步思想和中外文学，对绘画和文学产生了浓厚兴趣。由于对封建家庭和包办婚姻不满，1930年秋离家出走，几经颠沛流离。1932年秋与萧军同居，结识了一些进步文化人，1933年开始文学创作，同年10月与萧军自费出版了第一本作品合集《跋涉》。萧红的早期创作多取材于城市失业者或贫苦农民生活，被认为带有鲜明的现实主义的进步倾向。1934年春“两萧”取道大连流亡至青岛，萧红在很短的时间内完成了中篇小说《生死场》。同年11月“两萧”到达上海。在鲁迅的支持和帮助下，1935年12月《生死场》被列为“奴隶丛书”之三出版，鲁迅为之作序，称赞其所描写的：“北方人民的对于生的坚强，对于死的挣扎，却往往已经力透纸背；女性作者的细致的观察和越轨的笔致，又增加了不少明丽和新鲜。”它以沦陷前后的东北农村为背景，真实地反映了农民尤其是农村底层妇女的艰难生存状况，描述了他们的觉醒与抗争。《生死场》使萧红在30年代文坛上崭露头角。这一时期萧红还写作了大量的短篇小说与散文，并结集出版了《商市街》、《桥》等作品集。</p><p>1936年7月，为摆脱精神上的苦闷，萧红只身东渡日本，同年年末返回上海。抗战爆发后即辗转汉口、临汾、西安、重庆等地。1938年8月与萧军离异，与端木蕻良结合。此年被视为萧红创作前后两期的分界。1940年春与端木同抵香港。此时的中篇小说《马伯乐》以犀利的笔锋表现了幽默和讽刺才能；具有独特艺术风格的长篇小说《呼兰河传》则被茅盾称为是“一篇叙事诗，一幅多彩的风土画，一串凄婉的歌谣”。同时，它又表达了对国民团体盲目、愚昧、麻木、残忍等等劣根性的忧愤和悲悯，被越来越多的后人认为是继鲁迅之后对国民心态的开掘和批判的力作。这一时期萧红的创作在艺术上日趋成熟和辉煌，然而她的病体却日渐不支，太平洋战争爆发后在战火纷飞中被病魔夺去了生命，年仅31岁。</p><p>在短短的8年创作生涯中，萧红留下了60万字的文学财富，她的作品乡土气息浓烈，叙事风格细腻深刻、委婉动人，尤其是在小说文体上作出了很大的创新。海内外许多文学批评家认为，萧红以自己的女性之躯跋涉过漫长的道路，以女性的目光一次次透视历史，终于站到了与鲁迅同一的高度，达到了同一种对历史、文明以及国民灵魂的了悟。</p>', '< p > xiao hong, the Chinese modern famous writer. On June 2, 1911, was born in heilongjiang HuLan County, January 22, 1942 illness at Hong Kong. Formerly known as Ian zhang ying, pen name xiao hong, sad songs, etc. Lost his youth, his father violent character, she is only there to enjoy a little human warmth from old grandfather, lonely childhood form the character of xiao hong, sensitive, reserve and stubborn. < / p > < p > to Harbin, 1927 secondary school, contact since the may fourth progress thought and the Chinese and foreign literature, strong interest in painting and literature. Due to dissatisfaction with the feudal family and arranged marriage, in the autumn of 1930 away from home, after several drift from place to place. In the autumn of 1932 with Xiao Jun cohabitation, met some progressive intellectuals, literary creation began in 1933, the same year October and Xiao Jun self-published the first works collection \"journey\". Xiao hong\'s early writing based on urban unemployed or poor farmers life more, considered with vivid realism tendency of progress. In the spring of 1934 \"two shaw\" via between Qingdao and dalian exile, xiao hong in a very short period of time to complete the novella hulanhe. In November the same year \"two shaw\" arrived in Shanghai. In lu xun\'s support and help, in December 1935 hulanhe is listed as \"slave series\" published a third, lu xun as the work order, praised its writes: \"the life of the people\'s strong north, for death struggle, but often has penetrating; Women of the author\'s meticulous observation and deviant touches, it adds a lot of bright and beautiful and fresh.\" It in before and after the fall of northeast countryside as the background, truly reflect the farmers, especially rural women at the bottom of the difficult living conditions, describes their awakening and resistance. Hulanhe make xiao hong in the 30 s literary circles on the map. Xiao hong is writing during this period a large number of short stories and essays, and published the \"commercial street\", a collection of \"bridge\" and so on. < / p > < p > in July 1936, to get rid of mental anguish, xiao hong dongdu Japan alone, at the end of the same year to return to Shanghai. After the outbreak of the Anti-Japanese War is in hankou, linfen, xi \'an, chongqing and other places. In August 1938 and Xiao Jun divorced, and combine with DuanMuHongLiang. This year is seen as xiao hong creation before and after the two issue of the boundary. In the spring of 1940 with the period arrived in Hong Kong. At this time of the medium-length novel maspero with sharp pen shows humor and irony to; Novels with unique artistic style, the hulan river \"by MAO dun is called\" a narrative poem, a picture of a colorful and painting, a string of sad songs \". At the same time, it expressed the national group blind, ignorance, numbness, cruelty, etc etc and compassion, is considered by a growing number of later generations as after lu xun to the national mentality, and critical. Xiao hong\'s creation during this period in art become more mature and brilliant, but her sick body is tired, the Pacific war broke out in the war-torn illness took his life, just 31 years old. < / p > < p > in just eight years writing career, wealth left a 600000 - word literature, xiao hong strong agrestic breath, the works of her narrative style and exquisite profound, euphemism and moving, especially a great innovation in novel style. Many literary critics at home and abroad, xiao hong in their own body of women trudge through long road, with women in her eyes again and again the perspective of history, was standing in the same height with lu xun, has reached the same kind of history, civilization and the realization of the national spirit. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806992197', '飞鸟集', 'images/飞鸟集.jpg', '哈尔滨出版社', '文学', '12.6', '16.8', '<p>《飞鸟集》是泰戈尔的代表作之一，也是世界上最杰出的诗集之一。白昼和黑夜、溪流和海洋、自由和背叛，都在泰戈尔的笔下合而为一，短小的语句道出了深刻的人生哲理，引领世人探寻真理和智慧的源泉。初读这些诗篇，如同在暴风雨过后的初夏清晨，推开卧室的窗户，看到一个淡泊清透的世界，一切都是那样清新、亮丽，可是其中的韵味却很厚实，耐人寻味。</p>', '< p > \"stray birds\" is one of the representative work of tagore, is also one of the most outstanding poetry in the world. Day and night, streams and oceans, freedom, and betrayal, all in tagore\'s one, short statement says the profound life philosophy, to lead the search for truth and a source of wisdom. First read the poem, as in the early summer morning after the storm, pushed open the bedroom window, indifferent to see a clear world, everything is so pure and fresh, bright beautiful, but the flavor is very thick, intriguing. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532739578', '瓦尔登湖', 'images/瓦尔登湖.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '8.25', '11', '<p>这本书的思想是崇尚简朴生活，热爱大自然的风光，内容丰厚，意义深远，语言生动，意境深邃，就像是个智慧的老人，闪现哲理灵光，又有高山流水那样的境界。</p><p>书中记录了作者隐居瓦尔登湖畔，与大自然水乳交融、在田园生活中感知自然重塑自我的奇异历程。读本书，能引领人进入一个澄明、恬美、素雅的世界。</p>', '< p > the idea of this book is advocating simple life, love the beautiful scenery of the nature, content rich, meaningful, vivid language, profound mood, like a wise old man, philosophies of flash light, and there was a mountain stream that realm. < / p > < p > the book records the author reclusive walden lake, in perfect harmony with nature and rural life perception singular course of natural reinvent themselves. Reading a book, can lead a person to the world of a transparent, pleasantness, simple but elegant. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9789577452443', '月亮忘記了', 'images/月亮忘記了.jpg', '格林文学出版社', '文学', '224.25', '299', '<p>看不見的，是不是就等於不存在？</p><p></p><p>記住的，是不是永遠不會消失？每一個黃昏過後，大家焦慮地等待，卻再也沒有等到月亮升起。</p><p></p><p>潮水慢慢平靜下來，海洋凝固成一面漆黑的水鏡，</p><p>沒有月亮的夜晚，世界變得清冷幽寂．但是，最深的黑夜即將過去，月亮出來了……</p><p></p>', '< p > invisible, are they really not there? < / p > < p > < / p > < p > remember, and will never disappear? Every evening after everyone anxiously, never wait until the moon rises. < / p > < p > < / p > < p > the tide to calm down slowly, solidified into the dark water mirror sea, < / p > < p > no moon night, the world becomes cold better claim. However, the most at the end of the night, the moon came out... < / p > < p > < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9788781074519', '金锁记', 'images/金锁记.jpg', '哈尔滨出版社', '历史', '10.125', '13.5', '<p>《金锁记》写于1943年，小说描写了一个小商人家庭出身的女子曹七巧的心灵变迁历程。七巧做过残疾人的妻子，欲爱而不能爱，几乎像疯子一样在姜家过了30年。在财欲与情欲的压迫下，她的性格终于被扭曲，行为变得乖戾，不但破坏儿子的婚姻，致使儿媳被折磨而死，还拆散女儿的爱情。&#34;30年来她戴着黄金的枷。她用那沉重的枷角劈杀了几个人，没死的也送了半条命。&#34;</p><p>张爱玲在本书中在空前深刻的程度上表现了现代社会两性心理的基本意蕴。她在她那创作的年代并无任何前卫的思想，然而却令人震惊地拉开了两性世界温情脉脉的面纱。主人公曾被作者称为她小说世界中惟一的&#34;英雄&#34;，她拥有着&#34;一个疯子的审慎和机智&#34;，为了报复曾经伤害过她的社会，她用最为病态的方式，&#34;她那平扁而尖利的喉咙四面割着人像剃刀片&#34;，随心所欲地施展着淫威。</p><p>作者将现代中国心理分析小说推向了极致，细微地镂刻着人物变态的心理，那利刃一般毒辣的话语产生了令人惊心动魄的艺术效果。《金锁记》在叙述体貌上还借鉴了民族旧小说的经验，明显反映了类似《红楼梦》之类的小说手法已被作者用来表现她所要表现的华洋杂处的现代都市生活。</p>', '<p> golden lock \"written in 1943, the novel depicts the woman of a small businessman family background cao seven artful heart transformation process. Seven artful disabled wife, to love and not love, almost like a madman in the ginger family for 30 years. Under the wealth desire and sexual oppression, her personality was distorted, behavior has soured, not only destroy the son\'s marriage, the daughter-in-law were tortured to die, also break up the daughter of love.', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108012692', '倚天屠龙记(共四册)', 'images/倚天屠龙记(共四册).jpg', '三联书店', '魔幻', '35.25', '47', '<p>《倚天屠龙记》，金庸武侠小说，著于1961年，是“射雕三部曲”系列第三部，现收录在《金庸作品集》中。该书以元末群雄纷起、江湖动荡为广阔背景，叙述武当弟子张无忌的江湖生涯，表现众武林豪杰质朴自然，形态各异的精神风貌，展现其不可替代的人格力量。</p>', '< p > the handheld device maker e-ten slew a dragon to record \", jin yong\'s martial arts novels, written in 1961, is the third \"shoot diao trilogy\" series, is now included in the \"jin yong\'s works. The book to pack at the end of the yuan were struggling, jianghu instability for broad background, wudang disciple zhang mowgli jianghu career, show the wulin hero plain natural, forms the spirit, to show its irreplaceable personality power. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787507515121', '此间的少年', 'images/此间的少年.jpg', '华文出版社', '情感', '18.75', '25', '<p>《此间的少年》讲述的是让人熟悉的大学生活的故事。小说以宋代嘉佑年为时间背景，地点在以北大为模版的“汴京大学”，登场的人物是乔峰、郭靖、令狐冲等大侠，不过在大学里，他们和当代的年轻人没有什么不同。他们早上要跑圈儿，初进校门的时候要扫舞盲，有睡不完的懒觉，站在远处默默注视自己心爱的姑娘……</p><p>在这个学校里，郭靖和黄蓉是因为一场自行车的事故认识的，而这辆自行车是化学系的老师丘处机淘汰下来的，杨康和穆念慈则从中学起就是同学，念慈对杨康的单恋多年无果，最后选择的人却是彭连虎。</p><p>脑中存着金庸小说先前的印象，再徜徉于这样全新的故事中，是一种双重的温习，而这双重的回忆最后归结为一点，便是几乎每个人都经过过或正在经历的轻狂无畏的少年时光。</p>', '< p > \"the teenager here is about to let a person familiar with college life. Novels in song dynasty jia guan as the time background, the location in the north of the great template \"bian city university\", his character is xiao feng, guo jing and make fox blunt, warrior, but in college, they and the contemporary young people are no different. They will run in the morning circle and swept into the school gate at the beginning of time to dance, is a never-ending sleep lie-in, standing in the distance silently watching his beloved girl... < / p > < p > in this school, guo jing and huang2 rong2 because a bicycle accident, and this bike is a chemistry teacher qiu machine selection, yang2 kang and qin nanqin since high school\'s classmate, read kind of yang2 kang unrequited love nothing for many years, the final choice is peng even tiger. < / p > < p > the brain with previous impression from jin yong\'s novels, walking in such a new story, is a kind of double review, and dual memory finally boils down to this point, almost everyone is after experiencing or frivolous intrepid young time. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532733415', '夏洛的网', 'images/夏洛的网.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '12.75', '17', '<p>一个蜘蛛和小猪的故事，写给孩子，也写给大人。</p><p>在朱克曼家的谷仓里，快乐地生活着一群动物，其中小猪威尔伯和蜘蛛夏洛建立了最真挚的友谊。然而，一个最丑恶的消息打破了谷仓的平静：威尔伯未来的命运竟是成为熏肉火腿。作为一只猪，悲痛绝望的威尔伯似乎只能接受任人宰割的命运了，然而，看似渺小的夏洛却说：“我救你。”于是，夏洛用自己的丝在猪栏上织出了被人类视为奇迹的网上文字，彻底逆转了威尔伯的命运，终于让它在集市的大赛中赢得特别奖，和一个安享天命的未来。但，这时，蜘蛛夏洛的生命却走到了尽头……</p><p></p>', '< p > a spider and pig\'s story, written for children, also for adults. < / p > < p > at zuckerman\'s barn, a group of animals lived happily, the pig Wilbur and a spider charlotte has established the most sincere friendship. However, one of the most ugly news broke the peace of the barn, Wilbur\'s future destiny was to become bacon ham. As a pig, Wilbur seems to despair but to accept the fate of the sacrificial, however, seemingly insignificant charlotte said, \"I save you.\" So charlotte with his own weave silk in the pigsty on the human as a miracle on Internet, completely reversed Wilbur\'s destiny, and finally make it won the special prize in the market, and a share the destiny of the future. But, at this time, the spider charlotte\'s life has come to an end... < / p > < p > < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020120130', '我的天才女友', 'images/我的天才女友.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '情感', '31.5', '42', '<p>只有你身为女人才会知道这些丑陋的秘密</p><p>两个女人，50年的友谊和战争</p><p>过去五年，几乎所有欧美读者都在谈论她、</p><p>全球畅销百万册被翻译成40种语言</p><p>《金融时报》2015年度女性</p><p>2016《时代》周刊“世界最有影响力的100人”</p><p>希拉里·克林顿、乔纳森·弗兰岑、詹姆斯·伍德、詹姆斯·弗兰科都是她的粉丝</p><p>----------------------</p><p>《我的天才女友》是埃莱娜·费兰特“那不勒斯四部曲”的第一部，讲述了两个女主人公莉拉和埃莱娜的少女时代。故事一开始，已经功成名就的埃莱娜接到莉拉儿子里诺的电话，说他母亲彻底消失了。埃莱娜想起莉拉对自己命运的预言，于是她写下她们一生的故事……</p><p>莉拉和埃莱娜一起成长于那不勒斯一个破败的社区，从小形影不离，彼此信赖，但又都视对方为自己隐秘的镜子，暗暗角力。</p><p>莉拉聪明，漂亮。她可以毫不畏惧地和欺凌自己的男生对质，也可以去找人人惧怕的阿奇勒﹒卡拉奇要回被他夺走的玩具；埃莱娜既羡慕莉拉的学习天赋和超人的决断力，又一直暗暗模仿莉拉。</p><p>家人不支持莉拉继续求学，因此她到父亲和兄长苦苦维持的修鞋店帮工，又面临几个纨绔子弟的追求。埃莱娜则怀着对朋友的关爱、嫉妒和理解，独自继续学业，却始终无法面对和莉拉竞争的失落。</p><p>最终，十六岁的莉拉决定嫁给肉食店老板，但在婚宴上，她发现了丈夫的背叛。而埃莱娜也站在成人世界的入口，既为前途担忧，也因对思想前卫的尼诺产生朦胧好感而彷徨。</p><p>----------------------</p><p>名家评论</p><p>费兰特将两个贫穷的都市女孩之间的爱、分离和重逢，铸造成她们居住的那个城市的悲剧。</p><p>——《纽约时报》</p><p>埃莱娜·格雷科是一个幸存者，她必须从那些依附和挣脱的戏剧冲突中，让自己幸存下来。她带着一种幸存者的羞愧，就好像她是从莉拉的宝库盗取了对财富的允诺。</p><p>——《纽约客》</p><p>和索福克勒斯或者奥维德一样，费兰特处理的也是命运的问题。莉拉是一个造物主，一个神话般的人物。</p><p>——《大西洋月刊》</p><p>焦虑、疲惫、女性经期……费兰特探索了所有我们恐惧的题材。费兰特笔下的女人们切肤地体验了被抛弃、不公和汹涌的情感——这些不再是被当作弱点、而被作为一种事实来看待。</p><p>——《新共和》</p><p>和卡夫卡一样，费兰特将她的主人公的内心世界揭露得一览无余。</p><p>——《卫报》</p><p>《我的天才女友》是一部单声道（而非双声道）的成长小说；我们从很早就意识到，莉拉还困在自己的世界里，而作者，埃莱娜则会挣脱那个世界。</p><p>——《泰晤士文学增刊》</p>', '<p> just as the women you know the secret of these ugly </p> <p> two women, 50 years of friendship and war </p> <p> in the past five years, almost all the European and American readers is talking about her, </p> <p> the world\'s bestselling millions of books have been translated into 40 languages </p> <p> the ft 2015 women </p> <p> 2016 \"time\" magazine \"the world\'s 100 most influential people\" </p> <p> Hillary Clinton, Jonathan franzen, James wood, James franco is her fans </p> <p> -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- </p> <p> the genius of my girlfriend is Elena, rand \"napoli tetralogy\" first, tells the story of two heroines Lila and Elena girlhood. Story from the start, has established Elena got a call from the Lila son Reno, said his mother disappeared completely. Elena think of la on the predictions of his own fate, so she wrote the story of their life... </p> <p> Lila growing with Elena in Naples a run-down community, grew up together, trust each other, but both see each other as a mirror, a dark secret secretly wrangling. </p> <p> Lila clever, beautiful. She can confront and bullying their boys without flinching, can also go to find everyone afraid Mr Kirchner, Karachi will be he take the toy back; Elena envy Lila learning both talent and superman\'s determination, and has been secretly imitate Lila. </p> <p> your family does not support Lila continue to study, so she went to his father and brother struggled Alfred minas helper, and faces several dude pursuit. Elena is with love, jealousy, and understanding of friends and alone to continue their studies, has been unable to face the lost and Lila competition. </p> <p> in the end, Lila, 16, decided to marry to meat shop owner, but in the wedding banquet, she found her husband\'s betrayal. And Elena is stationed at the entrances to the adult world, worries about the future, both to the idea of the avant-garde for nino also produce hazy goodwill and hesitation. </p> <p> -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- </p> <p> famous comment </p> <p> fee rand will be between the two poor urban girls love, separation and reunion, casting into the tragedy of the city where they live. </p> <p> - the New York times </p> <p> Elena gray is a survivor, she must be from the attachment and break free of drama conflict, to survive. Her survivors with a shame, as if she is from the Lila treasure stole to the promise of wealth. </p> <p> - the New Yorker </p> <p> like sophocles or Ovid, fee rand processing is also the fate of the problem. Lila is a creator, a mythical figure. </p> <p> - the Atlantic </p> <p> anxiety, fatigue, female menstrual period... The subject matter of fee rand explored all of our fear. Fee rand\'s women cut skin to experience the abandoned, injustice and turbulent emotions - these are no longer treated as weaknesses, but be to look at it as a fact. </p> <p> - the new republic, </p> <p> like kafka, reveal the inner world of the fee rand her protagonist have to take in everything in a glance. </p> <p> - the guardian </p> <p> \"the genius of my girlfriend\" is a mono (rather than the double track) on the growth of fiction; We have long been aware that, Lila also trapped in their own world, and the author, Elena will throw off the world. </p> <p> -- The Times literary supplement </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508630069', '史蒂夫·乔布斯传', 'images/史蒂夫·乔布斯传.jpg', '中信出版社', '历史', '51', '68', '<p>这本乔布斯唯一授权的官方传记，在2011年上半年由美国出版商西蒙舒斯特对外发布出版消息以来，备受全球媒体和业界瞩目，这本书的全球出版日期最终确定为2011年11月21日，简体中文版也将同步上市。</p><p>两年多的时间，与乔布斯40多次的面对面倾谈，以及与乔布斯一百多个家庭成员、朋友、竞争对手、同事的不受限的采访，造就了这本独家传记。</p><p>尽管乔布斯给予本书的采访和创作全面的配合，但他对内容从不干涉，也不要求出版前阅读全文的权利。对于任何资源和关联的人，他都不设限，甚至鼓励他所熟知的人袒露出自己的心声。</p><p>“我已经做了很多并不值得自豪的事情，比如23岁时就让我的女友怀了孕，以及我对这件事的处理方式”，他说，“对我而言，没有什么不可以对外袒露的。”</p><p>谈及和他共过事的人以及竞争对手，他直言不讳，甚至尖酸刻薄。他的激情、精力、欲望、完美主义、艺术修养、残暴还有对掌控权的迷恋塑造出的商业哲学一览无余。</p><p>同样，他的朋友、敌人，还有同事得以为我们提供了一个前所未有的毫无掩饰的视角。</p><p>他是一位极具创造力的企业家，他有如过山车般精彩的人生和犀利激越的性格，充满追求完美和誓不罢休的激情，他创造出个人电脑、动画电影、音乐、手机、平板电脑以及数字出版等6大产业的颠覆性变革。</p><p>乔布斯的个性经常让周围的人愤怒和绝望，但其所创造出的产品也与这种个性息息相关，全然不可分割的，正如苹果的硬件和软件一样。</p><p>他的故事既具有启发意义，又有警示意义，充满了关于创新、个性、领导力以及价值观的教益。</p>', '< p > this the only authorized official biography of Steve jobs, in the first half of 2011 by the American publisher Simon &schuster release to the news, the global media and industry attention, the world of the book publishing date finally confirmed for November 21, 2011, simplified Chinese will also be launched. < / p > < p > more than two years, with more than 40 jobs and talk face to face, and with more than one hundred family members, friends, jobs\'s competitors, colleagues is not limited to interview has created this exclusive biography. < / p > < p > although jobs offer book interview and writing a full match, but he never interfere with the content, nor the right to demand to read the full article before publication. For any resources and associated person, he will not set limits, and even encouraged him to familiar people showing their voice. < / p > < p > \"I have done a lot of it is not proud of things, such as the age of 23 let my girlfriend became pregnant, and I am\'s handling of the matter\", he said, \"to me, have no what can\'t foreign exposed.\" < / p > < p > when it comes to the man who has worked with him and rivals, he calls a spade a spade, even vitriolic. His passion, energy, desire, perfectionism, artistic accomplishment, cruelty and love of control model a business philosophy of take in everything in a glance. < / p > < p > in the same way, his friends, enemies, and colleagues to provide us with an unprecedented unreservedly perspective. < / p > < p > he is a creative entrepreneur, he is like a roller coaster, and sharp agitation of the personality, the splendid life with passion, the pursuit of perfection and shi don\'t stop until he created personal computers, animated movies, music, phones, tablets, and digital publishing and so on six big industry of disruptive change. < / p > < p > jobs personality often let the people around you anger and despair, but the products created by also is closely related to the individual character, completely indivisible, just as apple\'s hardware and software. < / p > < p > his stories are instructive, and alarming, filled with lessons about innovation, character, leadership, and values. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530209578', '人生', 'images/人生.jpg', '北京十月文艺出版社', '历史', '15', '20', '<p>《人生》是路遥的一部中篇小说，发表于1982年，它以改革时期陕北高原的城乡生活为时空背景，叙述了高中毕业生高加林回到土地又离开土地，再回到土地这样人生的变化过程。高加林同农村姑娘刘巧珍、城市姑娘黄亚萍之间的感情纠葛构成了故事发展的矛盾，也正是体现那种艰难选择的悲剧。</p>', '< p > \"life\" is a medium-length novel of lu yao, published in 1982, northern shaanxi plateau, it in the period of reform of urban and rural life as the background of time and space, describes the high school graduates Gao Jialin back to the land and leave, returned to their land so that the change process of life. High lam dong rural girl qiao-zhen liu, the emotional entanglement between the city girl Huang Yaping constitutes the story of the development of the contradiction, is also reflect that the tragedy of the hard choices. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787805678313', '荆棘鸟', 'images/荆棘鸟.jpg', '译林出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>《荆棘鸟》是一部澳大利亚的家世小说，以女主人公梅吉和神父拉尔夫的爱情纠葛为主线，描写了克利里一家三代人的故事，时间跨度长达半个多世纪。拉尔夫一心向往教会的权力，却爱上了克利里家的美丽少女梅吉。为了他追求的“上帝”，他抛弃了世俗的爱情，然而内心又极度矛盾和痛苦。以此为中心，克利里家族十余名成员的悲欢离合也得以展现。</p><p>小说情节曲折生动，结构严密精巧，文笔清新婉丽。在描写荒蛮广漠的澳大利业风光时，颇有苍凉悲壮之美；同时女作家对女人爱情心态的探索，又十分细腻感人，故而这部作品有澳大利亚的《飘》之誉。</p>', '< p > the thorn birds is an Australian family novel to the heroine meggie and father Ralph love entanglement as the main line, describes the story of a three generations in Cleveland, the time span for more than half a century. Ralph addicted to the power of the church, but fell in love with the beautiful young girl meggie cleary\'s house. For the sake of his pursuit of \"god\", he abandoned the worldly love, however and extreme contradictions and inner pain. As the center, the cleary family members of more than ten kinds of joys and sorrows.there are also displayed. < / p > < p > plot twists and turns vivid, the structure is exquisite, the writing is pure and fresh and beautiful. In wild open Australian industry landscape, there is quite a desolate tragic beauty; Women writers love to a woman mentality exploration at the same time, and very delicate and touching, so this work has the reputation of \"gone with the wind\" of Australia. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806399071', '哭泣的骆驼', 'images/哭泣的骆驼.jpg', '哈尔滨出版社', '文学', '11.85', '15.8', '<p>在《哭泣的骆驼》中，三毛依然恋恋着墨沙漠生活周遭的人与事，《收魂记》、《搭车客》、《逍遥七岛游》、《一个陌生人的死》、《大胡子与我》等篇，情趣盎然；《沙巴军曹》与《哑奴》所刻画的主角，给人留下了难以磨灭的印象；而压轴的《哭泣的骆驼》，以游击战事为背景，细细铺写一对沙漠情鸳的生死盟，竟犹如史诗般的磅礴。</p>', '< p > in the cry of a camel, SAN MAO still love love lis desert life people and things around, \"the soul\" and \"a lift guest\", \"free and unfettered seven island Tours\", \"a stranger\'s death\", \"beard and I\", such as paper, interest is full. The sabah sergeant \"and\" dumb slaves \"portrayal of the protagonist, left an enduring impression; Of the axis and the cry of a camel, to guerrilla war as the background, shop carefully write a pair of people spend their honeymoons. / / death au, unexpectedly like epic. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535732309', '时间简史', 'images/时间简史.jpg', '湖南科学技术出版社', '历史', '33.75', '45', '<p>《时间简史》讲述是探索时间和空间核心秘密的故事，是关于宇宙本性的最前沿知识，包括我们的宇宙图像、空间和时间、膨胀的宇宙不确定性原理、基本粒子和自然的力、黑洞、黑洞不是这么黑、时间箭头等内容。第一版中的许多理论预言，后来在对微观或宏观宇宙世界观测中得到证实。</p><p>自1988年首版以来，《时间简史》已成为全球科学著作的里程碑。它被翻译成40种文字，销售了近1000万册。此版更新了内容，把许多观测揭示的新知识，以及霍金最新的研究纳入，并配以250幅照片和电脑制作的三维和四维空间图。</p>', '< p > \"a brief history of time\" tells the story of the core secret is to explore the time and space, is about the nature of the universe at the forefront of knowledge, including our universe, space and time, the expanding universe uncertainty principle, the basic particles and force of nature, the black hole, the hole is not so black arrow, time, etc. Many theory predicts that in the first edition, and later in the micro or macro cosmos observation confirmed. < / p > < p > since the first edition in 1988, \"a brief history of time\" has become a milestone in the global scientific works. It has been translated into 40 languages and sold nearly 10 million copies. Contribute to update the content, many observations of the new knowledge, as well as into the latest research, hawking and 250 images and computer generated three and four dimensional space. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806553404', '鹿鼎记（全五册）', 'images/鹿鼎记（全五册）.jpg', '广州出版社花城出版社', '历史', '81', '108', '<p>《鹿鼎记》是金庸创作的最后一部小说，也是他最重要的代表作。</p><p>小说讲的是一个从小在扬州妓院长大的小孩韦小宝，他以不会任何武功之姿态闯江湖各大帮会、周旋皇帝朝臣之间并奉旨远征云南、俄罗斯之故事，书中充满精彩的对白及逆思考的事件。</p><p>韦小宝笑称自己“不学无术却处处有术”，他靠着这不学之术在太监、钦命大臣、帮会堂主、和尚、甚至七个美女的共同老公这些角色上游刃有余。这个人物挑战了真实的人性，说明武功和权力不是这世上唯一的可取之道。</p>', '< p > \"the deer and the cauldron\" is jin yong\'s last novel, is also his most important representative works. < / p > < p > novel is about a child who grew up in yangzhou brothels inspired, he won\'t be any fighting skill of attitude from place to place, each big gang, and moves between the emperor courtier and purport expedition, Russia, the story of yunnan, the book is full of wonderful dialogue and inverse thinking about events. < / p > < p > weixiabao smile said he \"competent but everywhere in the art\", he by this study of secretary in the eunuchs, nominees, help main synagogue, monks, even the common husband these roles of the seven beauties. The character of the challenge the real human nature, that fighting skill and power not of this world the only option. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9789882075696', '海贼王', 'images/海贼王.jpg', '浙江人民美术出版社', '漫画', '5.625', '7.5', '<p>路飞所生长的小村庄里曾经是一群以「红发香克斯」为首的海盗们的暂居地，而幼年路飞一直希望可以成为他们的一员，可在一次意外的情况下，他吃了一种叫做「橡皮果实」的恶魔果实变成了橡胶人。恶魔果实给予了他这样奇特的本领，但是吃了恶魔果实的人是再也没有能力游泳的…这样还能成为海盗吗？「没有关系，我只要不掉到海里去就行了…」天性乐观的路飞并没有放弃他的海贼之路，他和香克斯约好，总有一天他会带着他的伙伴们成为海贼王。（听上去好像很有道理，可是……我真的给这个单细胞的家伙打败了）。</p><p>名声，财富，权力，曾经拥有世界上一切的“海贼王”哥尔·D·罗杰，在临死前留下了一句话，让全世界的人们，趋之若鹜奔向大海：“想要我的财宝吗？想要的话可以给你，去找吧！我把一切都放在那里了！”于是所有的人们开始起航，驶入伟大航路，世界迎来了『大海贼时代』。</p><p>蒙其.D.路飞——一个以成为海贼王为目标的男孩，为了兑现与救了他命的杰克的承诺，戴着杰克留给他的草帽只身一人向着大海出发了！可路飞却因小时候误食了恶魔果实而无法游泳了，就是在这种情况下，路飞展开了他的冒险……一路上他先后结识了一位又一位可靠的伙伴，打倒了一个又一个强大的敌人，经历一次又一次殊死的恶斗，路飞也离那财宝“ONEPIECE”越来越近了……</p>', '<p> luffy is the growth of the small village was once a group headed by \"red hair,\" pirates of the tabernacle, and luffy youth always hope to be one of them, but in the case of an accident, he ate a demon called \"eraser\" fruit fruit into rubber. The devil gave him such a strange fruit ability, but people eat the devil fruit is no ability to swim... This can also become a pirate? \"There is no relationship, as long as I don\'t fell to just go to the sea...\" Nature optimistic luffy hadn\'t given up his road of the pirates, he have an appointment with incense, and one day he will be one piece with his fellows. (sounds like a lot of sense, but... I\'m really beat) to the single guy. </p> <p> the fame, wealth, power, once has the world all the \"one piece\" elder brother, d. Roger, before she died left a word, let people around the world, have run into the sea: \"want me to treasure? Can give you, if you wish to find! I put everything there!\" So all the people began to set sail, and into the great route, the world ushered in the \"era of big pirates\". </p> <p> it. D. luffy, a one piece as the goal to become the boy, in order to deliver on the promises of jack and saved his life, with jack to his straw hats alone set out towards the sea! But because of when I was a child eating luffy demonic fruit to swim, is in this case, luffy opened his adventures... Along the way he met a and a reliable partner, struck down one after another powerful enemies, experience a desperate fight again, luffy also is getting closer and closer to the treasure \"ONEPIECE\"... </p>', '9.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563334421', '伊豆的舞女', 'images/伊豆的舞女.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '文学', '17.85', '23.8', '<p>收录“十六岁的日记”、“参加葬礼的名人”、“春天的景色”、“温泉旅馆”、“花的圆舞曲”等15篇短篇小说。</p>', '< p > \"sixteen diary\", \"celebrities attended the funeral\", \"spring scenery\", \"hot springs hotel\", \"flower of waltz\" 15 short stories. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020035878', '红与黑', 'images/红与黑.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>小说主人公于连,是一个木匠的儿子,年轻英俊,意志坚强,精明能干,从小就希望借助个人的努力与奋斗跻身上流社会。</p><p>在法国与瑞士接壤的维立叶尔城，坐落在山坡上，美丽的杜伯河绕城而过，河岸上矗立着许多锯木厂。市长德瑞那是个出身贵族，在扣上挂满勋章的人。</p><p>他五十岁左右，他的房子有全城最漂亮的花园，他的妻子是最有钱而又最漂亮的妻子，但他才智不足，“他只能办到严格地收讨他人的欠债，当他自己欠人家的债时，他愈迟还愈好”。在这座城市还有一个重要人物，是贫民寄养所所长——哇列诺先生。他花了一万到一万两千法郎才弄到这个职位，他体格强壮棕红色的脸，黑而精粗的小胡子，在别人眼中他是个美男子，连市长都惧他三分。但市长为了显示自己高人一等，决心请一个家庭教师。</p><p>木匠索黑尔的儿子于连，由于精通拉丁文，被选作市长家的家庭教师。他约十八九岁，长得文弱清秀，两只又大又黑的眼睛。在宁静时，眼中射出火一般的光辉，又象是熟思和探寻的样子，但一瞬间，又流露出可怕的仇恨，由于他整天抱着书本不放，不愿做力气活，因而遭到全家的嫌弃与怨恨，经常被父亲和两个哥哥毒打。他小时疯狂地崇拜拿破伦，渴望像拿破仑那样身佩长剑，做世界的主人。认为拿破仑“由一个既卑微又穷困的下级军官，只靠他身佩的长剑，便做了世界上的主人”。但后来他又想当神甫，因为“如今我们眼见四十岁左右的神父能拿到十万法郎的薪俸。这就是说他们能拿到十万法郎，三倍于拿破仑当时手下的著名的大将的收入。”于是，他投拜在神甫西朗的门下，钻研起神学来。他仗着惊人的好记性把一本拉丁文《圣经》全背下来，这事轰动了全城。</p>', '< p > novel heroine in even, is the son of a carpenter, young, handsome, strong, smart, hope that through the childhood personal efforts and struggles among the high society. < / p > < p > in the French and the Swiss border Ye Ercheng, located on the hillside, and the beautiful Du Bohe ring, on the Banks of the river stand many sawmills. The mayor driver that\'s a noble blood, people in accounting. < / p > < p > he is about fifty years old, he is the most beautiful garden city, his wife is the richest and most beautiful wife, but his talent is not enough, \"he can only do it strictly for the debt of others, when he owe debts, the more he later also the better\". Still has an important figure in this city, it is people, director of the foster care - wow, Mr. He took ten thousand to twelve thousand francs to get this position, his strong physique palm red face, black and thick mustache, in the eyes of others, he is a handsome man, even the mayor, fear him three points. But the mayor to display own superiority, determined to please a tutor. < / p > < p > the carpenter, the son of Mr. Hale even, because in Latin, was chosen for the mayor\'s home tutor. About his late teens, weak and comely, two big black eyes. In the eyes of tranquility, shoot fire radiance, deliberation and looking like is like, but in a flash, and reveals the terrible hatred, because he is holding the books all day, don\'t want to do LiQiHuo, consequently abandon and resentment from the family, often maltreated by father and two brothers. His desire hours crazily worship of napoleon, like napoleon jian, do the master of the world. Think napoleon \"consists of a humble and poor junior officers, just by his long sword at length, and become the master of the world\". But then he wanted to be a priest, because \"we now see the father can get around the age of forty thousands francs salaries. This means that they can get thousand francs, three times the napoleon\'s famous general income.\" So, he worshipped in the class of the abbe west lang, to study theology. He trusted in surprisingly good memory to recite all the Latin bible, this sensation all over the city. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9789574557806', '一個人住第5年', 'images/一個人住第5年.jpg', '大田文学出版社', '历史', '165', '220', '<p>一個人住了五年的過來人的日常生活。一個人的生活輕鬆也寂寞，卻又難割捨。</p><p>作者利用可愛的圖畫搭配生活化的文字描寫一個人住的生活點滴，只要你曾經一個人住過，一定會有深刻的感覺。一個人住不用跟家人搶浴室洗澡，愛洗多久就洗多久、一個人住偶爾不小心看了恐怖電視而害怕的睡不著覺、一個人住感冒的時候孤單寂寞的心情如潮水般的湧上心頭、一個人住到超商去買菜還會會貨比三家、一個人住會努力想記帳，卻因為偷懶而想出每天存「50元」的計畫、一個人住常會想變換擺設也是不錯而忙到凌晨三點，有點自由隨性卻又有點苦惱，這就是一個人住的生活。</p><p>作者希望可以透過這本書跟读者分享又寂寞又美好的單身生活。</p>', '< p > a person lived for five years a n experienced person\'s daily life. Easy a person\'s life is lonely, but to give up. < / p > < p > the authors use a lovely picture with life of text describing a person lives life intravenous drip, as long as you have been a person lives, there must be a deep feeling. A person lives don\'t have to take a shower with my family, love how long wash wash how long, a person lives occasionally accidentally saw horror TV cannot sleep and fear, when a person lives a cold lonely mood such as poured on the heart, a person lives to the convenience store to buy food also will shop around, a person lives will be trying to chalk it up, but because of laziness and come up with a deposit of 50 yuan every day plan, a person lives often want to transform the decoration is good and busy to three o \'clock in the morning, a little free along with the gender is a bit upset, this is the life of a person lives. < / p > < p > the author hope can through the book to share with readers and lonely and single life. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544225502', '长恨歌', 'images/长恨歌.jpg', '南海出版公司', '情感', '16.5', '22', '<p>一个女人四十年的情与爱，被一枝细腻而绚烂的笔写得哀婉动人，其中交织着上海这所大都市从四十年代到九十年代沧海桑田的变迁。生活在上海弄堂里的女人沉垒了无数理想、幻灭、躁动和怨望，她们对情与爱的追求，她们的成败，在我们眼前依次展开。王安忆看似平淡却幽默冷峻的笔调，在对细小琐碎的生活细节的津津乐道中，展现时代变迁中的人和城市，被誉为“现代上海史诗”。</p><p>本书荣获第一届世界华文文学奖，并于2000年获得我国文坛上最具荣誉的大奖——茅盾文学奖。</p>', '< p > 40 years of affection and love, a woman is a delicate and gorgeous pen write pathetically, in which mixed with the Shanghai metropolis from the passage of the changes of the 40 s to ninety s. Women living in Shanghai lilong sink base countless ideal, disillusionment, restlessness and resentment, their pursuit of love and love, their success or failure, in front of us in turn. Wang anyi\'s seemingly plain but humor cold tone, in the tiny little details of life with relish, show the people and the cities of the era of change, has been hailed as a \"modern Shanghai epic\". < / p > < p > this book won the first world Chinese literature, and in 2000 China\'s literary world the most honor awards - MAO dun prize for literature. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535445582', '东霓', 'images/东霓.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '情感', '20.1', '26.8', '<p>《东霓》和《西决》一样，还是在讲发生在那个永远的龙城的，郑家人的故事。但是不同于西决的隐忍，东霓是个活色声香的女人。这本《西决》的姐妹篇，却完全转换了主人公以及第一人称叙述的视角，呈现出来一个东霓眼中完全不同的郑家，完全不同的世界。东霓是一个经历坎坷、自私势利，却又坚韧勇敢、情深似海的女人。残酷的生活教会她精明和算计，但是在真正紧要的转折点上，她却依然把自己交付给生命深处燃烧着的冲动和本能。所以她才要不择手段地和前夫争夺，所以她机关算尽却把自己绕了进去，所以她才能勇敢地用伤痕累累的心热切地去爱，所以她才能只是因为一时冲动，给真正最关心她的人留下永远难以磨灭的伤害。</p><p>故事结尾处，东霓放弃了很多，失去了很多，唯一剩下的，却还是她的勇气和热情。她带着自己的秘密重新出发了，龙城依旧是个静默的古老城市，这一次，变成了一个荒凉的戏台，东霓粉墨登场，像个张扬的花旦，在万里晴空之下，上演了一出古老的戏码：北方，有佳人。</p>', '< p > \"east neon\" and \"west\", or talking about in the liuzhou forever, Zheng Jiaren story. But different from the west should forbear, east neon is a living voice sweet woman. The west never served, has completely changed the hero and the first-person narrative point of view, presented a completely different beep east neon eyes, completely different world. East neon is an experience bumpy, selfish snob, yet tough courage, the woman of the oceans. Cruel life taught her shrewd and calculating, but in the real critical turning point, but she still give yourselves to life deep in the burning of impulse and instinct. So she didn\'t want to do anything with her ex-husband, so her authority to calculate all around himself, so she can boldly with scarred heart eager to love, so she can just because on impulse, leaving really care most about her man forever enduring. < / p > < p > the end story, east neon gave up a lot and lost a lot of, the only remaining, but her courage and enthusiasm. She set out with his secret again, liuzhou, ancient city, is still a silent this time, into a desolate stage, east neon, a flamboyant actress, under a sunny, staged an ancient drama: the north, with the wind. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532752805', '寻路中国', 'images/寻路中国.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '历史', '24.75', '33', '<p>我叫彼得·海斯勒，是《纽约客》驻北京记者。这本书讲述了我驾车漫游中国大陆的经历。</p><p>2001年夏天，我考取了中国驾照，在此后的七年中，我驾车漫游于中国的乡村与城市。这七年也正是中国汽车业的高速发展期，单在北京一地，每天申领驾照的新人就有一千多，其中有好几年，乘用车销售额的年增长率超过了百分之五十。仅仅两年多的时间，中国政府在乡村所铺设的公路里程数，就超过了此前半个世纪的总量。</p><p>《寻路中国》一书有几条不同的线索。它首先叙述了我由东海之滨沿着长城一路向西，横跨中国北方的万里行程；另一条线索集中讲述了一个因中国汽车业的高速发展而发生巨变的乡村，在这里，我特写了一个农民家庭由农而商的变化经历；最后，则是中国东南部一个工业小镇的城市生活场景。书中所描述的这种由农而工而商、乡村变身城市的发展，正是1978年改革以来中国所发生的最重要的变化。</p><p>《寻路中国》是我的中国纪实三部曲之尾曲。它探讨经济，追踪发展的源头，探究个人对变革的应对。如前两本书那样，它研究中国的核心议题，但并不通过解读著名的政治或文化人物来实现这个目的，也不做宏观的大而无当的分析。它相信通过叙述普通中国人的经历来展现中国变革的实质。我经常在一地连续呆上数月、甚至数年，跟踪变化。我不会仅仅听主人公自己讲述，我会睁大眼睛，看着他们的故事在我面前一点点展开。</p><p>这三本书横跨了我的中国十年，从1996至2007。我们可以看出，这个处于世纪之交的十年是中国历史上最关键的时期之一。正是在这十年中，中国经济实现了腾飞，中国对外部世界的影响力开始增大。更重要的是，这是邓小平去世后的第一个十年。在这十年中，中国历史的面貌开始变化，大规模的政治事件与强力领袖开始从中退却。相反，中国巨变的推动者变成了普通人——走向城市的农民、边学边干的企业家，他们的能量与决心是过去这十年中的决定因素。从《江城》到《甲骨文》再到《寻路中国》，我所讲述的都是他们的故事。</p>', '<p> my name is Peter Hays, is the New Yorker correspondent in Beijing. The book tells the story of my cruising in mainland China. </p> <p> in the summer of 2001, I passed the driver\'s license in China, in the next seven years, I cruising in the Chinese countryside and city. The seven years of rapid development of China\'s auto industry, also in Beijing alone, apply for a driver\'s license of the couple has more than one thousand a day, there are several years, the annual growth rate of more than fifty percent of passenger car sales. Just more than two years, the Chinese government in the country by paved highway mileage, total more than half a century before. </p> <p> book pathfinding China has several different clues. It first describes me by the shore of the east China sea west of the Great Wall, wanli travel across northern China; Another clue concentrates on a changes due to the rapid development of China\'s auto industry country, here, I wrote a peasant family by the change of the agricultural and commercial experience; Finally, it is an industrial town in southeast China city life scenes. Described in this book by farmers and workers and business turns into the development of the city and countryside, it is what happens to China since the 1978 reform of the most important changes. </p> <p> \"pathfinding China\" is the end of my Chinese documentary trilogy. It discusses the economic, tracing the source of development, to explore the individual to cope with change. As the first two books, it studies the core issues of China, but not by reading a famous political or cultural figures to achieve this goal, don\'t do the macro analysis of the white elephant. It believes that by described the experience of ordinary Chinese people to change the essence of China. I often spend months in a continuous, even years, to track changes. I don\'t just listen to the hero about myself, I will open your eyes and look at their story unfold in front of me. </p> <p> across the three books in my 10 years in China, from 1996 to 2007. We can see that this decade at the turn of the century is one of the most critical period in Chinese history. It is in this decade, China\'s economy has realized the take-off, China began to increase the influence of the outside world. More importantly, this is the first ten years after the death of deng xiaoping. In this decade, China began to change the face of history, large-scale political events and strong leaders began to retreat from it. Instead, China change enabler into ordinary people - to the city of farmers, to learn while stem of entrepreneurs, their energy and determination is a determinant in the past ten years. From the river to the oracle to the pathfinding China, what I have is their story. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506360876', '陆犯焉识', 'images/陆犯焉识.jpg', '作家出版社', '文学', '26.25', '35', '<p>《陆犯焉识》内容简介：陆焉识本是上海大户人家才子+公子型的少爷，聪慧而倜傥，会多国语言，也会讨女人喜欢。父亲去世后，年轻无嗣的继母冯仪芳为了巩固其在家族中的地位，软硬兼施地使他娶了自己的娘家侄女冯婉喻。没有爱情的陆焉识很快出国留学，在美国华盛顿毫无愧意地过了几年花花公子的自由生活。毕业回国后的陆焉识博士开始了风流得意的大学教授生活，也开始了在风情而精明的继母和温婉而坚韧的妻子夹缝间尴尬的家庭生活。</p><p>五十年代，陆焉识因其出身、更因其不谙世事的张扬激越而成为&#34;”反革命“”，在历次运动中，其迂腐可笑的书生气使他的刑期一次次延长，直至被判为无期。这位智商超群的留美博士由此揣着极高的学识在西北大荒草漠上改造了二十年。精神的匮乏、政治的严苛、犯人间的相互围猎与倾轧，终使他身上满布的旧时代文人华贵的自尊凋谢成一地碎片。枯寂中对繁华半生的反刍，使他确认了内心对婉喻的深爱。婉喻曾是他寡味的开端，却在回忆里成为他完美的归宿。</p><p>“文革”“结束后，饱经思念的陆焉识和冯婉喻终于可以团聚，然而回到上海家中的陆焉识却发现岁月和政治彻底改变了他的生活，他再也找不到自己存在的位置：一生沉沦、终成俗庸小市民的儿子一直排斥和利用他，才貌俱佳、终成大龄剩女的小女儿对他爱怨纠结，态度几经转变，唯一苦苦等待他归来的婉喻却在他到家前突然失忆。</p><p>《陆犯焉识》编辑推荐：被中西方文坛誉为；“华文世界最值得期待的作家”；严歌苓颠覆性转型之作；当政治与人生相撞，孰是孰非……最大胆的笔触，直逼人类精神的灰色地带；最温情的回眸，抚摸岁月带给爱情的伤痕。</p><p>严歌苓近年来一直萦怀于对自身家族史特别是对其祖父人生遭际和精神世界的探寻。依此多年的功课，《陆犯焉识》以深远的济世情怀，将知识分子陆焉识的命运铺展在中国近当代政治这块庞大而坚硬的底布上，检视了残酷岁月里生命可能达到的高度。她的笔触往返于主人公盛年时流连的浮华地美国、上海和其后半生被禁锢的流放地西北大荒漠，世态的炎凉和命运的多诡尽收眼底。她的讲述，冷静与幽默同行，温情与练达并重，大有“翻手为苍凉，覆手为繁华”之概。</p>', '< p > lu made how knowledge content abstract: lu yan know this is a large house in Shanghai who childe master, intelligent and charming, will be many languages, ladies. After his father died, no heir young stepmother Feng Yifang in order to consolidate its status in the family, carrot and stick to that he had married her maiden niece yu feng wan. No love how to go abroad to study soon, lu in Washington over the years without meaning too playboy free life. Returned home after graduation how general Dr Lu started love satisfiedly, a professor at the university of life, began in the amorous feelings and canny stepmother and wen wan and tough wife cracks awkward family life. < / p > < p > 50 s, lu how knowledge because of its origins, more because of the make public of agitation and become', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787549501076', '你一定爱读的极简欧洲史', 'images/你一定爱读的极简欧洲史.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '历史', '18.75', '25', '<p>“欧洲，为什么老是抢第一？”澳大利亚知名历史学家约翰•赫斯特在本书中的一场引人入胜的探索，为我们梳理出欧洲文明所以能改变全世界的各种特质。</p><p>作者从三大元素：古希腊罗马文化、基督教教义以及日耳曼战士文化开篇，描述了这三大元素如何彼此强化，又相互对立，最终形塑为欧洲文明的内核；继而在诸多世纪以来催生帝国与城邦，激发征服与十字军东侵，造就出许多性格截然分明的人物──如仁慈的皇帝、好斗的教皇、侠义的骑士，乃至世上第一批享受繁荣和启蒙果实的公民。哲学思维、民主制度的渊源、政治权力的传递、甚至是医学、生物学使用拉丁文的源始，这种种欧洲因素不断形塑了现代文明的各种特质，使欧洲遥遥走在现代世界的前列。</p><p>本书以清晰、幽默、发人深省的笔调，杂以活泼的插图，叙述了一个不同凡响的文明，及其对人类社会的巨大冲击与巨大贡献。</p><p>.</p><p>编辑推荐：</p><p>1.《你一定爱读的极简欧洲史》是一部“最短”的欧洲史。它以极简练的文字，却从不同的角度，把欧洲历史的精要述说透彻！雅典的民主、罗马的共和，差别在哪里？蛮族入侵是如何发生？中古时期的政教之争到底争什么东西？罗伯斯庇尔时期的法国为什么叫“美德共和国”？——所有这些问题的答案，《你一定爱读的极简欧洲史》将以非常轻松的方式告诉你。</p><p>2.有很长一段时间，中国文明要比欧洲文明进步，然而世上第一波稳健的经济发展首度发生在欧洲，工业革命继之而起，其他许多代表现代的标记也是发轫于欧洲。《你一定爱读的极简欧洲史》将以令人信服的方式为你解答：为什么欧洲对现代文明的影响这么深？</p><p>3.《你一定爱读的极简欧洲史》热销欧美，中文繁体版2010年4月出版，即跃居台湾诚品连锁书店、金石堂连锁书店、博客来网络书店畅销榜Top10超过半年。</p><p>.</p><p>名家推荐：</p><p>这是一本有见地、理解深入、值得好好读一读的书。</p><p>——北大中文系教授、著名学者钱理群</p><p>我乐于向读者推荐这样一本写得深入浅出、给人启发的好书。</p><p>——百家讲坛名家、著名学者、复旦历史系教授钱文忠</p><p>处在新一波全球化方兴未艾的今日，回头看欧洲的历史，似乎比回顾中国历史更有启发性，且正因本书之“极简”，感想越发强烈。……面对瞬息万变的时代，没有可资借镜的前例，每个人都在摸着石头过河，历史，在这个时候就派上大用场了。在过去的相似情境中，前人犯过那些错误，我们可以从历史上学到，从而加以回避。有这么一本“极简”的避险秘笈，我们真是幸运，不是吗？</p><p>——历史评论家公孙策</p><p>所有“还”对历史有兴趣，或是想要利用短时间了解今天欧洲文化渊源、发展的人，本书绝对是一本可以快速上手的入门书。相信透过这样一本小书，可以让已经学习过欧洲史的人，更加生动的重新唤醒自己脑海中的记忆，甚至产生不同的看法；没有学过欧洲史的人，也可以在故事中产生对欧洲变化的兴趣。</p><p>——台湾中山女高历史教师李彦龙</p><p>本书对于青年学子尤其受用，当今中、高等教育逐步将公民与社会、地理与历史学科整合为社会领域学科，本书的整合性正能符合各界对基础知识（社会领域通论）的渴求，无论是哲学思维、民主制度的渊源、政治权力的传递、甚至是医学、生物学使用拉丁文的源始，说是“极简”的欧洲史，本书却也可从众多学门进出，可谓深入浅出，面面俱到。</p><p>——台湾福和国中历史教师吴瑞元</p>', '< p > \"Europe, why always grab the first?\" Australian famous historian John hirst a fascinating exploration in the book, to tease out the European civilization so we can change the world of all kinds of traits. < / p > < p > the author from the three main elements: ancient Greek and Roman culture, Christianity, and Germanic fighters, describes how the three elements reinforce each other, and contradictory, the final shape of the kernel of European civilization; Then in many centuries gave rise to the empire and the polis, stimulate the conquest and the crusade, produce many distinct characters personality ─ ─ such as benevolent emperor, aggressive Pope, chivalrous knight, and even the world\'s first citizens enjoy the fruits of prosperity and enlightenment. Philosophical thinking, the origin and development of democracy, political power transmission, and even medicine, biology, the use of Latin origin, this kind of European factors constantly shaping the various characteristics of the modern civilization, Europe is walking in the forefront of the modern world. < / p > < p > this book with clear, humorous and thought-provoking tone, in a lively illustrations, recounting a outstanding civilization, and its huge impact on human society and the great contribution. < / p > < p >. < / p > < p > edit recommendation: < / p > < p > 1. \"you must love reading minimalist European history is a history of Europe\" shortest \". It with extremely concise words, but from a different Angle, related to the essence of European history thoroughly! The democracy of Athens, the Roman republic, where is the difference? Barbarian invasion is how to happen? Medieval battle over the church and state what for? Robespierre\'s why is called \"virtue\" of the republic of France? - all the answers to these questions, \"you must love reading minimalist European history will tell you in a very easy way. < / p > < p > 2. It\'s a long time, the Chinese civilization than European civilization progress, however, the first wave of the steady economic development in the world for the first time in Europe, followed the industrial revolution, many other representative modern tag is also began in Europe. \"You must love reading minimalist European history will be in a convincing way for you to answer: why Europe\'s influence on modern civilization so deep? < / p > < p > 3. \"you must love reading minimalist European history of Europe and the United States sell like hot cakes, traditional Chinese version published in April 2010, namely become Taiwan\'s eslite bookstore chain, Jin Shitang chain bookstore, bookstore of blog to the network, seller may need more than half a year. < / p > < p >. < / p > < p > famous recommendation: < / p > < p > this is an intelligent, understanding, worth the read book. < / p > < p > -- Beijing university Chinese department professor, famous scholars changyoucian < / p > < p > I am happy to recommend to the readers such a simple, give a person the good books inspired. < / p > < p > - lecture room famous, famous scholar, professor of history at fudan Qian Wenzhong < / p > < p > at the beginning to a new wave of globalization today, looking back the history of Europe, seems to be more enlightening than review of the history of China, and because of the book \"minimalist\", feeling more strongly. ... In the face of rapidly changing era, there is no possibility of the sharing from precedent, everyone in the touch stone across the river, history, at this time are great. , previous similar situations in the past of those mistakes, we can learn from history, thus to avoid them. Have so a \"minimalist\" safety tips, we are so lucky, isn\'t it? </p><p>——历史评论家公孙策</p><p>所有“还”对历史有兴趣，或是想要利用短时间了解今天欧洲文化渊源、发展的人，本书绝对是一本可以快速上手的入门书。 Believe that can make through this small book has studied history of Europe, more vivid resurrects of memory in your mind, or even produce different views; Not studied the history of the European people, also can generate interest in European change in the story. < / p > < p > - Taiwan zhongshan since history teacher yen-lung lee < / p > < p > this book for young students, especially in today\'s higher education, gradually will citizens and society, geography and history subject integration in areas for social subject, the book\'s integration is to meet people from all walks of life to the basic knowledge of general theory (social sciences), whether in philosophical thinking, the origin and development of democracy, political power transmission, and even medicine, biology, the use of Latin origin, saying is \"minimalist\" European history, book is also available at many learning in and out of the door, is easily understood, please everyone. < / p > < p > - Taiwan and junior high school history teacher Wu Ruiyuan < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563379637', '常识', 'images/常识.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '政治', '28.5', '38', '<p>梁文道先生近两年来撰写的时评文字结集，谈及政治、民主、民族、教育、新闻自由、公民道德等社会诸多方面。文字风格犀利，文章主旨清晰、论述简洁有力，往往一针见血命中问题之要害，其文字在带给读者阅读快感之余，还催人省思，给人启示。本书名曰《常识》，正如梁氏自言：“本书所集，卑之无甚高论，多为常识而已。若觉可怪，是因为此乃一个常识稀缺的时代。”</p>', '< p > Mr For writing editorial text collected in the past two years, when it comes to politics, democracy, freedom of the press, nationality, education, and moral social many aspects such as citizens. Sharp writing style, the gist is clear, concise and powerful, often hit the nail on the head hit the point, the text bring readers reading pleasure, also people reflection, give a person. Book called \"common sense\", as the propositions said: \"this book is set, the British had little remark, for more common sense. If you feel strange, because this is a common sense of scarcity era.\" < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108015280', '中国历代政治得失', 'images/中国历代政治得失.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '历史', '9', '12', '<p>《中国历代政治得失》为作者的专题演讲合集，分别就中国汉、唐、宋、明、清五代的政府组织、百官职权、考试监察、财经赋税、兵役义务等种种政治制度作了提要勾玄的概观与比照，叙述因革演变，指陈利害得失。既高屋建瓴地总括了中国历史与政治的精要大义，又点明了近现代国人对传统文化和精神的种种误解。言简意赅，语重心长，实不失为一部简明的“中国政治制度史”。</p>', '< p > the author for political gain and loss in China s keynote speech collection, respectively, on China\'s han, tang, song, Ming and qing five generations of government organization, baiguan authority, examination and supervision, finance and taxation, military service a variety of political system, such as feed hook xuan an overview and comparison, from narrative in evolution, Chen stakes. Both to sum up the essence of Chinese history and politics\'s sense of honor, and point out the modern people to the traditional culture and spirit of misunderstanding. Concise, earnest, can yet be regarded as a simple \"history of Chinese political system. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532744756', '罗生门', 'images/罗生门.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '9', '12', '<p>芥川龙之介(1892—1927)，日本新思潮派代表作家，创作上既有浪漫主义特点，又具有现实主义倾向。以其名字命名的“芥川奖”成为日本文坛的重要奖项之一。作品以短篇小说为主，多为历史题材，情节新奇甚至诡异，以冷峻的文笔和简洁有力的语言让读者关注到社会丑恶现象，这使得他的小说既具有高度的艺术性，又成为当时社会的缩影。《罗生门》是其代表作。本书收录芥川的中短篇小说共十三篇。《罗生门》以风雨不透的布局将人推向生死抉择的极限，从而展示了“恶”的无可回避，第一次传递出作者对人的理解，对人的无奈与绝望。书山稗海，文史苑囿，于中沉潜含玩，钩没抉隐，一日发而为文，自是信手拈来，随机生发，纵横捭阖，不可抑勒。由庙堂高官到市井小民，由紫宸之深到江湖之运，其笔下无不呼之即来，腾跃纸上。芥川生性敏感，一般来说，他不重描绘而意在发掘，疏于叙述而工于点化，少的是轻灵与潇洒，多的是沉郁与悲凉。这点不难从其作品中窥其一斑。</p>', '< p > his dragon interface (1892-1927), Japan\'s new trend representative writer, creation has the characteristics of both the romantic and realistic tendency. Named after the \"prize for his\" become one of the important prizes in the Japanese literary world. Work is given priority to with short stories, more for historical themes, plot novel, even to his style of writing and pithy language to let the readers attention to the social evils, which makes his novels not only has high artistic quality, has become a microcosm of society at that time. \"Rashomon\" is the masterpiece. This book of his novellas were thirteen. \"Rashomon\" to wind and rain will not through the layout of the people to the limits of life and death choice, which shows the \"evil\" inevitable, convey the author\'s understanding of people for the first time, to the person\'s helplessness and desperation. Everybody barnyard grass sea, pestered him, literature and history in fallow contain play, hook centuries implicit, hair for a day, naturally, and random germinal, shifting alliances, not suppression. From top temple official to the dorks and from deep to the river\'s lake of zichen, the pen is forthcoming, cavort paper. His naturally sensitive, generally speaking, he is not heavy and aims to explore, failing to narrative and gaiety and attunements, less light spirit and natural and unrestrained, more is depressed and sad. This is not difficult to peek at the one spot from his work. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787514205039', '自控力', 'images/自控力.jpg', '文化发展出版社(原印刷工业出版社)', '心理', '29.85', '39.8', '<p>《自控力》内容简介：作为一名健康心理学家，凯利•麦格尼格尔博士的工作就是帮助人们管理压力，并在生活中做出积极的改变。多年来，通过观察学生们是如何控制选择的，她意识到，人们关于自控的很多看法实际上妨碍了我们取得成功。例如，把自控力当作一种美德，可能会让初衷良好的目标脱离正轨。所以，麦格尼格尔要求她的学生了解影响自控的生理学基础、心理陷阱和各种社会因素。麦格尼格尔吸收了心理学、神经学和经济学等学科的最新洞见，为斯坦福大学继续教育项目开设了一门叫做“意志力科学”的课程，参与过这门课程的人称其能够“改变一生”。这门课程就是《自控力》一书的基础。本书为读者提供了清晰的框架，讲述了什么是自控力，自控力如何发生作用，以及为何自控力如此重要。</p><p>海报：</p>', '< p > \"self-control\" content abstract: as a health psychologist, Dr Kelly, McGonagall nigel\'s job is to help people manage stress, and make a positive change in your life. Over the years, through the observation of the students is how to control the selection, she realised that a lot of people about self-control view actually interfere with our success. For example, the self-control as a virtue, might be a good goal deviate from the original. So, McGonagall nigel asked her students to understand the effect of self-control physiological basis, psychological traps and all kinds of social factors. McGonagall nigel absorbed psychology, neuroscience and economics and other disciplines of the latest insights, opened a door for Stanford university to continue education project called \"willpower science\" course, involved in the course of said he could \"change life\". This course is the foundation of \"self-control\". This book offers readers a clear framework, tells the story of what is self-control, and self-control how to interact, and why self-control is so important. < / p > < p > posters: < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787500830146', '父与子全集', 'images/父与子全集.jpg', '中国工人出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>内容简介</p><p>1934年12月，第二次世界大战前夜的德国，到处充满了火药味，正是在这样的一个背景下，一套取材于日常生活反映父子间感情的漫画作品开始在《柏林画报》上连载，它的幽默温情犹如一片人性的绿洲，拂过万千民众的心，这便是德国漫画大师埃·奥·卜劳恩的传世名作《父与子》。它的幽默感和人情味表露得如此纯真，以致在问世近70年后，依然不断征服着世界各地的读者，散发出不衰的艺术魅力。</p>', '< p > description < / p > < p > in December 1934, the eve of world war ii Germany, powder filled everywhere, it is in such a background, a set of based on daily life reflect the relationship between father and son comics began serialised in the Berlin illustrated, its humorous warmth like a oasis of humanity, across all the hearts of the people, this is the German comic master, Mr, BuLao\'s masterpiece \"the father and son\". It is so pure, the sense of humor and human show that appeared in nearly 70 years later, still conquer the readers all over the world, send out an enduring artistic charm. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020040346', '一千零一夜', 'images/一千零一夜.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '魔幻', '16.5', '22', '<p>《一千零一夜》又名《天方夜谭》。&#34;天方&#34;是从前中国对阿拉伯的称呼。这本书中的故事，多是阿拉伯地区国家的传说。公元9世纪时，是阿拉伯帝国的全盛时期，它横跨亚洲、欧洲和非洲，有着独特而辉煌的文化。《一千零一夜》是阿拉伯地区的古代民间传说。从9世纪开始，经过搜集整理，至16世纪结成集子。到了18世纪，传播至欧洲、亚洲许多国家。全书共有两百多个故事，这里所选的是其中最著名的几个。这些故事有什么特色呢？它们反映了东方文化的瑰丽色彩：神秘、奇异、幻想丰富、语言优美。它们把神奇的想像和当时阿拉伯的现实结合起来，读故事便可了解那个时期阿拉伯人的生活风貌。书中同情贫苦大众的遭遇又称赞他们的智慧；书中歌颂冒险精神，特别是航海者的勇敢，因为那时候许多国家都是由于海上贸易而发达起来的。虽然书里把富有、享福作为最高理想，但是认为只有好心的人才应当享有。</p>', '< p > \"one thousand nights\" also known as the Arabian nights.', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020060504', '时间旅行者的妻子', 'images/时间旅行者的妻子.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '历史', '22.425', '29.9', '<p>相遇那年，她6岁，他36岁；</p><p>结婚那年，她23岁，他31岁；</p><p>离别后再度重逢时，她82岁，他43岁。</p><p>相对于如此真实、强烈的感觉，时间，微不足道……</p><p>亨利，一位年轻帅气、爱冒险的图书管理员，可是他有慢性时间错位症，会不知不觉地游离在时间之间。</p><p>克莱尔，亨利的妻子，一位生活秩序很规律的艺术家。</p><p>亨利以为他在28岁时第一次遇到他20岁的妻子克莱尔，而克莱尔却说：“我从小就认识你了”。和克莱尔结婚多年的亨利，却又突然发现自己回到了童年，遇见了他6岁的妻子。</p><p>如果生命是一场旅行，亨利的旅程肯定比常人更迂回更深刻，那些不由自主地消失，不得不一再体验曾经遭受的经历，他只能旁观、重复品味着那些快乐、悲伤和痛苦。可是在时间的正常旅途中行走的克莱尔呢？她只能被亨利远远抛在了后面，渴望，焦急，等着爱人回到她的身边。她虽然拥有时间，却只能通过捉摸亨利来触摸时间。</p><p>时间过滤着这一对恋人炙热的爱意，他们在时间与爱的复杂交错中勇敢地探索，最终谱写了一曲高昂的颂歌，踏上常人不可思议的浪漫之旅。</p>', '< p > meet that year, she was 6 years old, he is 36 years old; < / p > < p > when he was married, she is 23 years old, he is 31 years old; < / p > < p > when we meet again after parting, her 82 - year - old, he is 43 years old. < / p > < p > relative to so real, strong feeling that time, small... < / p > < p > Henry, a handsome young librarian, love adventure, but he had chronic time identity disorder, unknowingly dissociation between the time. < / p > < p > Clare, Henry\'s wife, a very regular life order artist. < / p > < p > Henry thinks he is at the age of 28 first met his wife, Clare, 20 and Clare said, \"since I was young, I know you. Henry and Clare married for years, but suddenly find themselves back to childhood, met his wife of 6 years old. < / p > < p > if life is a journey, a journey of Henry\'s certainly more circuitous deeper than normal people, those who disappear spontaneously, had to repeatedly experience have been through, he can only on the sidelines, repetitive taste to the happiness, sadness and pain. But at the time of normal walking journey Clare? She can only be Henry far left behind, desire, anxious, waiting for love to return to her side. Although she has time, they can touch time through thinking about Henry. < / p > < p > time filter with hot love this pair of lovers, they are time and love bravely explore complex crisscross, wrote a carols of the high end, the ordinary person incredibly romantic journey. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787533917067', '变形记', 'images/变形记.jpg', '浙江文艺出版社', '社会', '12', '16', '<p>1判决</p><p>2变形记</p><p>3司炉</p><p>4在流放营</p><p>5乡村医生</p><p>6饥饿艺术家</p><p>7铁桶骑士</p><p>8万里长城建造时</p><p>9一条狗的研究</p><p>10中国人来访</p><p>……</p>', '< p > 1 < / p > < p > 2 metamorphosis of < / p > < p > 3 stoker < / p > < p > 4 camp in exile < / p > < p > 5 village doctor < / p > < p > 6 hunger artist < / p > < p > 7 iron drum knight < / p > < p > 8 built the Great Wall < / p > < p > 9 a dog study < / p > < p > 10 Chinese visiting < / p > < p >... < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787543425651', '项链', 'images/项链.jpg', '河北教育出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>莫泊桑被尊称为“世界短篇小说之王”，他将短篇小说的趣味提升到前所未有的高度。在他的笔下，各种社会事件，如战争、政变、普选等，都得到了如实的表现；各个阶层的生活，如上层人士的纸醉金迷，中产阶级的锱必较，乡人村姑的朴素自然，都得到了形象的描绘；各种各样的人物，贵族、官僚、职员、店主、乞丐、妓女，都得到了逼真的刻画；各种各样的场景，如豪华的晚会、精致的沙龙、荒蛮的原野、喧哗的集镇、森严的官府、热门的街道，都得到了生动的写照。可以说，莫泊桑的短篇小说，是一幅栩栩如生的19世纪下半叶法国社会风俗长卷。</p>', '< p > maupassant is regarded as the \"king of the world short stories,\" he will increase the interest of short stories to unprecedented levels. In his works, various social events, such as war, coup, universal suffrage, got performance according to the facts; Each class of life, such as material, the upper echelons of the middle class Zi will more, fellow villager into plain natural, got image portrayed; All kinds of characters, noble, bureaucrats, staff, shopkeepers, beggars, prostitutes, got lifelike portrait; A variety of scenarios, such as luxury party, delicate salon, wild field, noise, guarded the rulers, hit the streets of the town, got vivid portrayal. Maupassant\'s short story, is, as it were, a picture of a life long curly French social custom in the second half of the 19th century. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508618081', '失恋33天', 'images/失恋33天.jpg', '中信出版社', '情感', '18.75', '25', '<p>黄小仙儿，27岁的大龄少女，从事高端婚庆策划；胸前无大物，姿色平平，家境也一般，唯一拿得出手的，就是一口刻薄言辞，和对这世界满腔的乐观。长途恋爱谈了七年，没有修成正果，反而在商场里看到了男友和自己闺蜜喜笑颜开的走在一起。</p><p>黄小仙儿的失恋日记，就这样一天一天的开始写了下去。工作上困难重重，刚刚惨遭失恋，却要替一对恋爱同样谈了很多年但现在仍然如胶似漆的新人策划婚礼；同事王小贱，既冷酷又毒舌，看起来是一个同性恋，对黄小仙儿的惨况一直冷眼旁观……黄小仙儿的人生还没拍摄到高潮部分，是不是就要这么被迫收工了？</p><p>但黄小仙别的没有，有的是自尊心和盲目乐观。疼过之后擦擦眼泪，就算新的一天是前一天的翻版，不会豁然开朗或是跳出一个闪闪发光的奇迹，她依然决定，老老实实走下去。</p>', '<p> yellow small XianEr, older girl, 27, is engaged in high-end wedding planning; No big chest, feminine beauty, family circumstances also generally, only take shots, is a vitriol, and full of optimism about the world. Long-distance love for seven years, no Promised Land, but in the mall to see the boyfriend and his best friend be happy together. </p> <p> yellow small XianEr lovelorn diary, so day by day began to write it down. Work hard, has just been brokenhearted, but for a pair of love also talked about for years but still cling to the couple planning the wedding; Colleague wang, is both cruel and poison tongue, seems to be a gay man, have been the consequences of small yellow XianEr look on coldly... Yellow small XianEr life hasn\'t taken to the climax, why so was forced to call it a day? </p> <p> but is huang, have a plenty of pride and optimism. Pain after wiping tears, even if is a new day, will not be suddenly enlightened, or out of a shiny miracle, she still decided, honestly. </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532729357', '一九八四·动物农场', 'images/一九八四·动物农场.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '17.25', '23', '<p>《一九八四》和《动物农场》是奥威尔的传世之作，堪称世界文坛上最著名的政治讽喻小说。他在小说中他创造的“老大哥”、“双重思想”、“新话”等词汇都已收入权威的英语词典，甚至由他的姓衍生了一个形容词“奥威尔式”不断出现在报道国际新闻的记者笔下，足见其作品在英语国家影响之深远。“多一个人看奥威尔，就多了一份自由的保障”，有评家如是说。</p>', '< p > \"1984\" and \"animal farm\" is Orwell\'s masterpiece, the world\'s most famous in the literary world of political satire novel. He created in his novels of \"big brother\", \"doublethink\", \"new words\" and other words have income authoritative dictionary of the English language, even by his family name is derived an adjective \"Orwellian\" appear constantly in the coverage of international news reporters, indicating the works profound impacts in english-speaking countries. \"More than one person see Orwell, as much a free security\", said a critic. < / p >', '9.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787800875830', '人性的弱点全集', 'images/人性的弱点全集.jpg', '中国发展出版社', '心理', '18.75', '25', '<p>《人性的弱点全集》汇集了卡耐基的思想精华和最激动人心的内容，是作者最成功的励志经典，出版后立即获得了广大读者的欢迎，成为西方世界最持久的人文畅销书。主要内容包括：与人相处的基本技巧、平安快乐的要诀、如何使人喜欢你、如何赢得他人的赞同、如何更好地说服他人、让你的家庭生活幸福快乐等十篇。</p>', '< p > \"the complete works of the weakness of human nature brings together the Carnegie\'s thought essence and the most exciting content, is a classic, the most successful self-help author published immediately after received the welcome of the readers, the western world the most enduring bestseller. Main contents include: basic techniques of getting along with people, and peace, the key to happiness, how to make people like you, how to win others\' approval, how to persuade others, make your family life happiness and so on ten articles. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506030328', '匆匆那年（上下）', 'images/匆匆那年（上下）.jpg', '东方出版社', '情感', '21.75', '29', '<p>80年代生人的张楠因大学毕业找不到好工作而留学澳洲，在那里他认识了同样留学的方茴。就在他被方茴的神秘感吸引时，却听说她竟然是同性恋。阴错阳差，他与方茴住在了同一屋檐下，并且通过其他朋友知道方茴并不是真正的同性恋者，而是曾经深受伤害，有过一段难以忘怀的经历。一次偶然的机会，在张楠的房间里，方茴给他讲述了自己的故事……</p><p>作品通过诙谐的文字，以方茴和陈寻的爱情故事为主线，描述了80后的情感与生活历程。方茴过去的回忆让人仿佛再次回到了90年代末的北京，在时间跨度长达十年的叙述中有美好的青春校园生活，有涉及青少年犯罪的探讨警示，有建国五十年大庆、迎接新世纪、北京申奥成功的历史事件，有大学时代的颓废迷茫，有工作以后的艰难奋斗，有婚姻生活的现状等等，以独特的视角真实记录了80后的成长轨迹和他们富有时代感的印记。</p>', '< p > nan born in the 80 s because of graduation from university can not find a good job while studying in Australia, where he met the same study Hui. As he was being party Hui mysterious attraction, we heard that she was gay. Erroneously, he and his party Hui live under the same roof, and through other friends know party Hui is not really a gay, but deeply hurt once, had an unforgettable experience. A chance in the room of nan, square Hui give him about his story... < / p > < p > works by witty words, the Israeli Hui and Chen found love story as the main line, describes the emotion and life history after 80. Party Hui past lets a person as if returned to the Beijing, in the late 90 s, the time span of a decade of narrative wonderful campus life, the youth have involved in the discussion of juvenile crime alert, 50th anniversary, to greet the new century, Beijing\'s Olympic bid success of historical events, a university of the decadent confusion of The Times, have work hard struggle, with the current situation of the marriage life, etc., with unique Angle of view after real recorded 80 growth trajectory and their time. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787300072487', '影响力', 'images/影响力.jpg', '中国人民大学出版社', '心理', '33.75', '45', '<p>政治家运用影响力来赢得选举，商人运用影响力来兜售商品，推销员运用影响力诱惑你乖乖地把金钱捧上。即使你的朋友和家人，不知不觉之间，也会把影响力用到你的身上。但到底是为什么，当一个要求用不同的方式提出来时，你的反应就会从负面抵抗变成积极合作呢？</p><p>在这本书中，心理学家罗伯特·B·西奥迪尼博士为我们解释了为什么有些人极具说服力，而我们总是容易上当受骗。隐藏在冲动地顺从他人行为背后的6大心理秘笈，正是这一切的根源。那些劝说高手们，总是熟练地运用它们，让我们就范。</p>', '< p > politicians use influence to win the election, businessmen use influence to sell goods, the salesman use influence to tempt you to put the money in. Even if your friends and family, unconsciously, will use the influence you. But what is the reason why, when a request is put forward in a different way, your response will be from negative resistance into positive cooperation? < / p > < p > in this book, psychologist Robert b. west audi, Dr. Explains why some people are very convincing for us, and we are always gullible. Hidden in the impulse to obey six psychological secrets behind the behavior of others, it is the root of it all. Those who persuade experts, always use them skillfully, let us into submission. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108010186', '历史深处的忧虑', 'images/历史深处的忧虑.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '历史', '14.25', '19', '<p>美国的面积和中国差不多。和大多数留学生及新移民一样，当我们一脚踏上这块广袤的陌生土地时，最初落脚点的选择是十分偶然的。我们落在了一个普通的地方，居住的环境平常而宁静。周围的美国人老老少少都在辛勤劳作，过着普通得不能再普通的生活。要想谋出一番好的光景，对他们也不是一件轻而易举的事情。</p><p>还来不及作任何思索，新移民所面临的生活压力就立即把我们投入了同样的辛勤劳作之中。这样，我们和周围的普通美国人之间，自然就有了共同谋生而产生的共同语言，也有了共同的经历，共同的喜怒哀乐。不少美国人还成了我们的好朋友。我们无形中发现，美国已经渐渐地从一堆抽象的概念中走出来，变成了脚下实实在在的土地，变成了一片片森林牧场，变成了一个一个美国人。</p><p>我们也有过被称之为“边缘人”的苦闷。我们显然不可能在进入这一块国土的同时，就在一瞬间也进入它的文化，而原来的文化背景又由于天长地远而渐显陌生。在实际生活中，两种截然不同的文化，会经常骤然直率地在我们面前相遇碰撞，一开始真有无所适从亦无可躲避的窘迫。然而，时间长了，我们开始对“边缘人”的处境逐渐坦然，甚至悟出了些什么。冷静下来，我们发现自己第一次能够这样坐在一个安静的地方，同时和两个文化保持一个不远也不近的距离，它们不仅开始有可能化为一片风景，而且第一次向我们呈现出前所未有的意义。</p><p>“边缘人”的苦恼在新移民中十分普遍，它只是两个强势文化聚焦在一个小人物身上而产生的悲剧性效应。我们庆幸自己能够脱身出来。但是，我们的处境使我们不可能不想到，作为一个夹缝中的移民，尚且感受到矛盾与压力，那么，当这两种文化两个大国真的正面遭遇，彼此实际上是多么陌生和困惑，说是危机四伏似乎也并不过分。我们所处的位置，使我们有可能更多地看到它们的差异。我们发现，它们不仅有各自圆满的价值体系，甚至有各自不同的语汇、语境和逻辑。有时，从一个大前提出发，顺着各自的逻辑走去，竟会走出风马牛不相及的结果来。在这样的基础上，对话只可能显得痛苦而吃力。</p><p>因此，好像在作出举手相迎或严辞相拒的决定之前，还有一段相当艰苦而漫长的互相了解的路必须去走。否则，轻易称“是”显得没有根据，动辄言“不”也容易文不对题。更何况，历史已经规定了它们不可能永远回避。它们都已尝试过这样做，但是，眼看着毫无结果，于是，它们又试图相互走近。有时，如果不暂时和自己的习惯思维方式生生拉开一段距离，就无法在相互了解的路上走出一步。</p><p>我们则是以一个普通新移民的身份去了解这个陌生的国家。既来之则安之，这也是我们的必由之路，我们也别无选择。</p><p>美国不是一个善于遮羞的国家，它投出一片阳光，就落下一片阴影。它全部的阴影都毫无遮掩地暴露在所有的人面前，哪怕你是一个陌生人。所以，即使是像我们这样的平常外来者，也会一眼就看出～大堆毛病来。但是我们马上就明白自己必须从沾沾自喜中醒来，因为后来很快发现，这并不见得就～定是自己比美国人更高明且目光更敏锐。他们似乎也很清楚有这么一片阴影，他们只是迫不得已在承认一个简单的道理，如果你追求阳光，你就躲不开身后的阴影。我们开始奇怪，美国人在容忍这片阴影的时候(这种容忍常常使他们痛苦不堪)，什么是他们心中不熄的光明呢?他们在寻求着什么，以至于不惜支付出沉重的代价呢?对于我们，这真是一个问题。在了解它的过程中，我们对这个历史短短的陌生国家产生了与日俱增的兴趣。</p><p>根据自己作为一个平民的经验，我们发现，了解的第一步就是简单的交往。不论一个大国看上去有着多么坚硬的外壳，它的人民都是一个个平平常常，而再大的大国也就是这些平常人组成的。当人民成为朋友，交流变成友谊，相互了解自然就开始了。任何一方，能以更宽广的视角去看这个世界，总是一件好事情。</p><p>去年，我们逐渐给自己在国内的好朋友写了这些信。希望能和朋友们分享我们的所读所见所闻所思。在此，衷心感谢三联书店的编辑和所有帮助这本书出版的朋友。</p>', '<p> the area of the U.S. and China. Like most international students and new immigrants, a pedal on the vast strange when we land, the choice of initial foothold is quite by accident. We landed in an ordinary place, living environment of ordinary and peaceful. Around the young American in toil, lived a too common ordinary life. If you want to find out a good sight, for they are not an easy thing. </p> <p> could make any thinking, life pressure facing new immigrants immediately put us in the hard work of the same. So, between us and the ordinary americans around, naturally have a common to make a living and have a common language, have Shared experiences, the joys and sorrows of the common. Many americans also became our good friends. Virtually, we found that the United States has gradually come out from a pile of abstract concepts, turned into a real at the foot of the land, into a forest farm, into a an American. </p> <p> we have referred to as \"marginal people\" in yours. We obviously can\'t be in this piece of land at the same time, in an instant into its culture, and the original cultural background due to last far faded in unfamiliar. In real life, two completely different culture, often a sudden encounter in front of us in plain English, a began to really have and also is to avoid embarrassment. However, after a long time, we started to \"marginal people\" situation gradually calm, even figured out something. That was the first to calm down, we find ourselves able to sit in a quiet place, and two cultures at the same time maintain a not far also not close, not only do they start may be turned into a landscape, but also for the first time presents the unprecedented significance to us. </p> <p> \"marginal people\" distress is widespread in the new immigrants, it\'s just two strong culture focused on a little and the tragic effect. We are glad to be able to get away. But our situation that we could not think of, as a crack is the immigration, still feel contradiction and pressure, so, when the two cultures two powers really confronted each other is actually how strange and confused, crisis seems to be not too. We are in the position, that we may see more of their differences. We found that not only do they have a complete value system, and even have different vocabulary, context and logic. Sometimes, starting from a major premise, go down the respective logic, should get out of the wind to the results of horse and. On the basis of this, the dialogue can only appear painful and difficult. </p> <p> therefore, seemed to be greeted with hands or rejects a spirited phase decision before, there is a fairly long and hard way have to go get to know each other. Otherwise, easy to say \"yes\" is not according to, often say \"no\" easy \"alchemists. Moreover, history has set can never avoid them. They have tried to do this, but seeing no results, so they try to approach each other. Sometimes, if not temporary and their habits thinking living away a certain distance, cannot be on the way to get to know each other step. </p> <p> we are in a normal the identity of the new immigrants to know this strange country. An when, this is the only way for us, we also have no other choice. </p> <p> is not a good at aims of the United States, it threw a piece of sunshine, just drop a shadow. All it\'s shadow without covering exposed in front of the person all, even if you are a stranger. So, even if is ordinary like us outsiders, at first glance will also see that ~ of fault. But we knew he must immediately waking from a smug, because soon found that this does not mean they ~ is better than americans, and his eyes. They also seem to be very clear that there was a shadow, they just had to admit that a simple truth, if you\'re looking for the sun, you can\'t hide behind the shadow. We began to strange, when americans tolerate this shadow (this tolerance often makes them miserable), what is in their heart does not extinguish the light? The search for something, he\'ll pay a heavy price to pay? For us, it\'s really a problem. In the process of understanding it, we just strange country on the history created a growing interest. </p> <p> according to their own experiences as a civilian, we found that the understanding of the first step is a simple communication. No matter how hard a superpower looks has a shell, it is each ordinary people, and again big powers which is composed of the rest. When people become friends, exchange into friendship and mutual understanding nature begins. Can any one party, in a more broad perspective to see the world, is always a good thing. </p> <p> last year, we gradually to oneself at home good friend wrote these letters. Hope I can share what we read and his friends saw thinks. At this point, heartfelt thanks to the joint of the editor and all the friends help the book was published. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806737842', '那些年，我们一起追的女孩', 'images/那些年，我们一起追的女孩.jpg', '花山文艺出版社', '情感', '15', '20', '<p>柯景腾读国中时是一个成绩暴烂而且又调皮捣蛋的男生，老师将他“托付”给班里最优秀的女生沈佳仪。只要他不认真学习，沈佳仪就会用钢笔戳他的衣服。</p><p>在沈佳仪的监督和鼓励下，柯景腾的成绩就像芝麻开花节节高，渐渐地，他也喜欢上了气质优雅的沈佳仪。但是柯景腾却不敢向心爱的女生表白，因为几乎被所有男生喜欢的沈佳仪对追求她的男生一律有一种反感，她只想好好学习，不希望别人介入自己的生活。</p><p>但是，为何沈佳仪唯独愿意把心事与柯景腾分享呢？她对他究竟有没有别样的感觉呢？柯景腾暗恋沈佳仪八年最终能否修得正果呢？让我们走进《那些年，我们一起追过的女孩》，一起来寻找最纯真的感动吧！</p>', '< p > when the author read countries is a result of bad and naughty boy, the teacher will he \"surrender to the best girl in the class Shen Jiayi. As long as he doesn\'t study, Shen Jiayi will use pen poked his clothes. < / p > < p > in Shen Jiayi supervision and encouragement, Mr. Ko grades like now rising, gradually, he also fell in love with the elegant temperament of Shen Jiayi. But Mr. Ko but dare not to beloved girl to vindicate, because almost all the boys like Shen Jiayi to pursue her boys all have a bad feeling, she just want to good good study, don\'t want to others in their life. < / p > < p > but for He Shenjia meter only willing to put the heart to share with Mr. Ko? She actually have different feeling? Mr. Ko has a crush on Shen Jiayi eight years could eventually made fruit? Let us walk into \"in those years, together we overtake girl\", to find the most pure moved together! < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508672069', '未来简史', 'images/未来简史.jpg', '中信出版集团', '历史', '51', '68', '<p>进入21世纪后，曾经长期威胁人类生存、发展的瘟疫、饥荒和战争已经被攻克，智人面临着新的待办议题：永生不老、幸福快乐和成为具有“神性”的人类。在解决这些新问题的过程中，科学技术的发展将颠覆我们很多当下认为无需佐证的“常识”，比如人文主义所推崇的自由意志将面临严峻挑战，机器将会代替人类做出更明智的选择。</p><p>更重要的，当以大数据、人工智能为代表的科学技术发展的日益成熟，人类将面临着从进化到智人以来zui大的一次改变，绝大部分人将沦为“无价值的群体”，只有少部分人能进化成特质发生改变的“神人”。</p><p>未来，人类将面临着三大问题：生物本身就是算法，生命是不断处理数据的过程；意识与智能的分离；拥有大数据积累的外部环境将比我们自己更了解自己。如何看待这三大问题，以及如何采取应对措施，将直接影响着人类未来的发展。</p>', '< p > after entering the 21st century, has long-term threat to human survival and development of the plague, famine and war have been overcome, homo sapiens, faced with new backlog issue: never dies, happiness, and become a human with \"divine\". In solve these new problems in the process, the development of science and technology will overturn many of our present think without evidence of \"common sense\", such as humanism, as free will face serious challenges, the machine will replace human, make a wise choice. < / p > < p > it is more important, as represented by big data, artificial intelligence in the development of science and technology matures, human face from evolution to homo sapiens zui big a change, since the vast majority of people will become a \"useless\", only a few can evolve into quality change of \"god\". < / p > < p > in the future, human will be faced with three major problems: life itself is algorithm, life is a process of constantly dealing with data; The separation of consciousness and intelligence; With large data accumulation of the external environment will than we know more about yourself. How to view these three problems, and how to respond, will directly affect the future development of the human. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536671256', '冰与火之歌（卷一）', 'images/冰与火之歌（卷一）.jpg', '重庆出版社', '文学', '51', '68', '<p>《冰与火之歌》由美国著名科幻奇幻小说家乔治·R·R·马丁所著，是当代奇幻文学一部影响深远的里程碑式的作品。它于1996年刚一问世，便以别具一格的结构，浩瀚辽阔的视野，错落有致的情节和生动活泼的语言，迅速征服了欧美文坛。迄今，本书已被译为数十种文字，并在各个国家迭获大奖。</p><p>本书主要描述了在一片虚构的中世纪大陆上所发生的一系列相互联系的宫廷斗争、疆场厮杀、游历冒险和魔法抗衡的故事，全书七卷（包括未出的各卷）浑然一体，共同组成了一幅壮丽而完整的画卷。书名“冰与火”，为的是突出人性挣扎的含义，书中塑造了无数的人物，但其着眼点，却并非孤立地凸现英雄主义，奉献精神或奸猾阴谋，而是将书中人物放在一个“真人”的角度，写出他或她在时代和社会的旋涡中不同的境遇与选择。从写作上说，本书与莎翁的《哈姆雷特》颇有共通之处。从中，读者便能与之产生呼应，共同经历这冰与火的洗礼。</p>', '< p > \"song of ice and fire\" by the famous American science fiction fantasy novelist George r. r. Martin, is the landmark of contemporary fantasy literature a far-reaching works. In 1996, it just comes out, with a unique structure, the vast vast field of vision, strewn at random have the plot and vivid language, to conquer the European and American literary world. So far, this book has been translated into dozens of languages, and overlapping won awards in various countries. < / p > < p > this book describes in a fictional medieval continent by a series of interconnected court battle, fought battles, travel against the story of adventure and magic, the book seven volumes (including not the mane) one integrated mass, constitute a splendid and complete picture scroll. The title \"ice and fire\", in order to highlight the meaning of human struggle, created many characters in the book, but its starting point, not protruding heroism in isolation, dedication or cunning plot, the characters in the book but in the perspective of a \"reality\", write his or her in the vortex of era and the social different circumstances and choices. In writing, this book with Shakespeare\'s \"Hamlet\" to have in common. Readers can, and the resulting from echo, experiencing the baptism of the ice and fire together. < / p >', '9.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532524808', '人间词话', 'images/人间词话.jpg', '上海古籍出版社', '文学', '7.35', '9.8', '<p>《人间词话》一书乃是王氏接受了西洋美学思想之洗礼后，以崭新的眼光对中国旧文学所作的评论，具有划时代的意义，向来极受学术界重视。本书并约请当今著名专家黄霖为之导读，不仅梳理其理论框架，剔抉其精义要眇，更着重揭橥其学术源流、历史文化背景，及撰作者当时特定的情境与心态，从而在帮助读者确切理解原著的同时，凸现词学大师王国维的学术个性。</p>', '< p > \"art\" but after the baptism of the wang accepted the western aesthetic thought, with a new vision for China\'s old literature comments, is of epoch-making significance, has great academic value. Book and invite the famous experts Huang Lin takeaway, combing its theory framework, not only take centuries its gist to Miao, more focus on expanding its academic origin, history and culture background, and written by the author when a particular situation and mentality, to help readers understand the original exactly at the same time, highlight the ci master wang guowei\'s academic character. < / p >', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535446794', '橙', 'images/橙.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '文学', '21.6', '28.8', '<p>想定做一个刻着“不过如此”的章到处盖盖</p><p>记录了23到26岁的一些生活点滴感受</p><p>2007~2010NOTHINGNEW</p><p>ajourney,throughtime,withanthony</p>', '< p > would like to order a \"but\" engraved chapter full cap < / p > < p > recorded 23 to 26, some life feeling < / p > < p > 2007 ~ 2010 nothingnew < / p > < p > ajourney, throughtime, withanthony < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532730001', '世界尽头与冷酷仙境', 'images/世界尽头与冷酷仙境.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '17.25', '23', '<p>《世界尽头与冷酷仙境》是村上春树最重要的小说之一，与《挪威的森林》、《舞舞舞》合称为村上春树三大杰作。小说共40章，单数20章“冷酷仙境”，双数20章为“世界尽头”，这种交叉平行地展开故事情节的手法是村上春树小说的特征，而这部作品是这种特征最典型的体现。“冷酷仙境”写两大黑社会组织在争夺一个老科学家发明的控制人脑的装置，老人躲到了地底。主人公“我”是老人的实验对象，他受到黑社会的恐吓，在老人的孙女帮助下，经过了惊心动魄的地底之旅，好容易找到老人，却被告知由于老人的计算错误，他24小时后离开人世，转往另一世界即“世界尽头”。“我”回到地面上,与女友过了最后一夜告别，然后驱车到海边静候死的到来。“世界尽头”是另一番景象，这里与世隔绝，居民相安无事，但人们没有心，没有感情，没有目标。“我”一直想逃离这里，但在即将成功时选择了留下，因为“我”发现“世界尽头”其实是“我”自己造出的。书中想象力奇特，艺术水准高超，情节极其荒诞而主题极其严肃，用变形的手法写出人们对当代资本主义社会的混乱现状逃避无门的真实心态。</p>', '< p > \"at the end of the world and cold fairyland\" is one of the most important novel of haruki murakami, and \"Norwegian wood\", collectively known as \"dance dance dance\" haruki murakami three masterpieces. Chapter 20 of 40 chapters of the novel, singular \"cold fairyland\", dual chapter 20 as the \"world\'s end\", the cross on the plot of the story in parallel technique is characteristic of haruki murakami novels, and this work is a reflection of the characteristics of the most typical. \"Cold fairyland\" write two big underworld organization in the competition for control of an old scientist invented the device of the brain, the old man into the underground. Hero \"I\" is the old man, he was intimidation by gangsters, the old man\'s granddaughter help, after a thrilling trip to earth, very easy to find the old man, only to be told that the old man calculation error, he died after 24 hours, moving to another world is \"at world\'s end\". \"I\" back to the ground, and his girlfriend say goodbye last night, and then drive to the beach waiting for the arrival of death. \"At world\'s end\" is another story, isolation, residents are peaceful, but there is no heart, no feelings, no goals. \"I always wanted to escape from here,\" but when they are about to successfully chose to leave, because \"I\" discovered \"at world\'s end\" is actually \"I\" I created. Book strange imagination, superb artistic level, a very bizarre plot theme extremely seriously, in the style of the deformation of contemporary capitalist society chaos status to avoid that the real state of mind. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535432896', '大地之灯', 'images/大地之灯.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '文学', '16.5', '22', '<p>雪域高原深处长大的孤儿卡桑，父母在一次朝圣的途中双双遇难；出生在北大荒的孩子简生，父母是北大荒的插队知青，在他出生之后先后被急于返城的父母遗弃，一直到十岁，才被母亲接回大城市。十九岁时简生的母亲因为受贿案件而自杀。简生将卡桑带回城市，由于父母缺席的家庭抚养，两人在整个成长过程中充满了欠缺。在成年之后的岁月依旧伴随着内心阴影，一直都艰苦地进行自我扶正与探索。最终他们用回报或者付出的方式，获得了各自的终极救赎和解脱。</p>', '< p > brought up deep in snow area plateau orphan qassam, parents both died on the way of going on a pilgrimage in time; JianSheng was born in the wilderness of a child, parents is wilderness cut in line of educated youth, after he was born has been eager to return to the city\'s parents abandoned, until ten years old, was mother back to big cities. At the age of nineteen JianSheng mother committed suicide because of the bribery case. JianSheng will she back to the city, because the parents are absent family upbringing, two people in the whole growing process is full of lack. Years in adulthood, still with the inner shadow, has always been hard to self righting and exploration. They eventually with return or pay for their ultimate salvation and liberation. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532756728', '江城', 'images/江城.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '纪实', '27', '36', '<p>1996年8月底一个温热而清朗的夜晚，我从重庆出发，乘慢船，顺江而下来到涪陵。</p><p>涪陵没有铁路，历来是四川省的贫困地区，公路非常糟糕。去哪里你都得坐船，但多半你哪里也不会去。在随后的两年，这座城市就是我的家。</p><p>在这里，我有时是一个旁观者，有时又置身于当地的生活之中，这种亲疏结合的观察构成了我在四川停留两年的部分生活。</p><p>2001年，也就是这本书在美国出版的时候，一条通往重庆的高速公路通车了，一条铁路也正在修建之中，基本上再也没有人坐船去涪陵了。这座城市正在飞速发展着，在过去的二十年，那样一种转型变化的感觉——接二连三、冷酷无情、势不可挡——正是中国的本质特征。很难相信，这个国家曾经完全是另外一种模样，是19世纪西方人眼中“永远停滞的民族”。</p><p>2003年，三峡大坝一期完工后，不断上涨的江水将陆续淹没那些江畔之城，这多少令我有些伤感。而对于大多数中国人来说，这正是不断变革的对应面：贫穷、烂路、慢船。</p><p>这并不是一本关于中国的书，它只涉及一小段特定时期内中国的某个小地方。从地理和历史上看，涪陵都位于江河中游，所以人们有时很难看清她从何而来，又去往何处。</p><p>在1996年至1998年间，我学会了热爱涪陵。能再次回到长江上的感觉真好，哪怕它的旧时激流只存于我的记忆之中。</p>', '<p> at the end of August 1996, a warm, clear night, I from chongqing, take a slow boat, Yangtze river and down to fuling. </p> <p> fuling no railway, has always been poor areas in sichuan, and roads are very bad. Where you have to sail, but you probably wouldn\'t. During the next two years, the city is my home. </p> <p> here, I sometimes is a bystander, sometimes in the local life, this kind of feeling of combining observation constitutes the part stay in sichuan for two years of my life. </p> <p> in 2001, that is, when the book was published in the United States, a path to chongqing expressway opened to traffic, a railway is being built, basically no one to go by ship fuling. Is rapid development, the city in the past 20 years, as a feeling of transformational change - a barrage, ruthless, overwhelming - it is the essence of China. It is hard to believe that this country has completely is another kind of appearance, is in the 19th century western eyes \"stagnant\" forever. </p> <p> in 2003, after the completion of the three gorges dam is a period of rising river will be flooded the city of the river, that how much I am sad. But for most Chinese, that is constantly change the corresponding surface: poverty, bad road, slow boat. </p> <p> this is not a book about China, and it involves only a small piece of specific period of time China\'s a small place. From the point of view of geography and history, fuling are located in river middle reaches, so it is sometimes difficult to see she come from, and where you are going. </p> <p> in 1996 and 1998, I learned to love the fuling. Can once again return to the feeling is really good in the Yangtze river, even if its old stream only exist in my memory. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532736201', '香水', 'images/香水.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>小说叙述一个奇才怪杰谋杀了26个少女的故事。其中每一次谋杀都是一个目的：只是因为迷上她们特有的味道。对格雷诺耶来说，每次都是一场恋爱，但是他爱的不是人，而是她们身上的香味；谋杀她们只是为了永远占有，并且拥有他所钟爱的那种没有感觉，没有生命的“香味”……</p><p>这本书不是一部通俗的惊险小说，而是一部构思奇特，充满幻想，离意深刻的严肃作品；自1985年出版以来，始终高居德国畅销书排行榜前列，已被译成30余种文字。</p>', '<p> novel narrative of a teenage wizards grinch murdered 26 stories. In which every murder is one purpose: it\'s just because their own fans. For Renault also, every time is a love, but he isn\'t a person of love, but the smell of them; Murder them just for the sake of possession forever, and have their beloved that do not have a feeling, not the \"flavor\" of life... </p> <p> this book is not a popular thriller, but a strange idea, full of fantasy, meaning deep serious works; Since its publication in 1985, has always been high on best-seller list in Germany, have been translated into more than 30 languages. </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020125265', '新名字的故事', 'images/新名字的故事.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '44.25', '59', '<p>只有你身为女人才会知道这些丑陋的秘密</p><p>两个女人50年的友谊和战争</p><p>如何成为那个更强大的她，又不被她战胜</p><p>那不勒斯四部曲NO.2</p><p>《我的天才女友》后续，意大利最神秘的作家费兰特</p><p>探索青年时代的激情、困惑、挣扎、背叛和失去</p><p>全球畅销近千万册被翻译成40多种语言</p><p>希拉里·克林顿、乔纳森·弗兰岑、詹姆斯·伍德、詹姆斯·弗兰科都是她的粉丝</p><p>-------------------------</p><p>《新名字的故事》是埃莱娜·费兰特的“那不勒斯四部曲”的第二部，描述了埃莱娜和莉拉的青年时代。在她们的人生以最快的速度急遽分化的那些年里，她们共同体验了爱、失去、困惑、挣扎、嫉妒和隐蔽的破坏。</p><p>莉拉在结婚当天就发现婚姻根本不是她想象的那样，她的初夜几乎是一场强奸。她带着一种强大的破坏欲介入了斯特凡诺的家族生意，似乎成为了她和埃莱娜小时候都想成为的那种女人。久未有身孕的莉拉，和埃莱娜去海边度假休养。而在伊斯基亚岛的那个夏天，改变了所有人的一生……</p><p>出于对莉拉所拥有的爱情的愤怒，“我”（埃莱娜）奋力摆脱这个破败、暴力、充满宿仇的街区。“我”成了街区的第一个大学生，并和一个高级知识分子家庭的男孩订婚，甚至出版了第一本小说。“我”以胜利者的形象回到那不勒斯，却发现告别了丑陋婚姻的莉拉，在一家肉食加工厂备受屈辱地打工。</p><p>当“我”发现自己的小说，其实完全窃取了莉拉交托给“我”的秘密笔记本里那些独特的力量和灵感，“我”被迫面临一个极度痛苦的问题：“我”和莉拉，到底谁离开了，又是谁留下了？</p><p>--------------------------------</p><p>无论是生活还是小说中，一段友谊里，更强大、性格更丰富的那个人会让软弱的那个人的形象变得模糊。但是在埃莱娜和莉拉的关系中，处于弱势的埃莱娜，从自身的从属位置中获得了某种才智——那让莉拉失去了方向，心晕目眩。这种过程很难描述，但也正是这一点让我着迷。可以这么说：在莉拉和埃莱娜的生命中，有很多事件显示了一个人如何从另一人身上汲取力量。但要记住这一点：这不仅表现在她们帮助彼此的层面上，同样也体现为她们互相洗劫，从对方身上窃取情感和知识，消耗对方的力量。</p><p>——埃莱娜•费兰特答意大利《晚邮报》采访（2011）</p><p>那不勒斯四部曲精彩而又持久地探索了嫉妒——这种最为致命的情感，因它有时候会将自己伪装成爱。</p><p>——《纽约书评》</p><p>关于女性友谊和命运的意大利史诗……在荷马和奥维德之后，我们第一次有了一个女性史诗作者。</p><p>——《大西洋月刊》</p><p>费兰特的行文如此清澈，她的叙述如此率真，摄人心魄，引人入胜。——《经济学人》</p><p>对于费兰特而言，小说的首要目的，就是就搅动那些感染的、敞开的伤口，捅开它，让你意识到自己的伤口在哪里，这伤口又从何而来。</p><p>——《洛杉矶书评》</p><p>埃莱娜必须挣脱她从小要面对的那些令人难以忍受的价值，抵抗世俗意义上的成功的诱惑，并从莉拉身上获得知识和力量，却又不能被她压倒……现代小说中对友谊最丰富的描写。</p><p>——NPR</p><p>每个人都应该看有埃莱娜·费兰特署名的任何文字。</p><p>——《波士顿环球报》</p>', '<p> just as the women you know the secret of these ugly </p> <p> two women 50 years of friendship and war </p> <p> how to become the stronger her, nor was she beat </p> <p> Naples quartet NO. 2 </p> <p> \"the genius of my girlfriend\" follow-up, the most mysterious Italian writer fee rand </p> <p> exploring the passion of youth, confusion, struggle, betrayal and lose </p> <p> the world\'s bestselling nearly thousands of books have been translated into more than 40 languages </p> <p> Hillary Clinton, Jonathan franzen, James wood, James franco is her fans </p> <p> -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- </p> <p> the story of a new name is Elena, rand \"napoli tetralogy\" second, describes Elena and Lila\'s youth. In their life as fast as a sharp differentiation of those years, together they experience the love and lost, confused and struggling, jealousy, concealed damage. </p> <p> Lila marriage was found in their wedding day, isn\'t she think her virginity is almost a rape. She took a great damage to the stefano involved in the family business, seemed to be her and Elena the woman wants to be as a child. Lila is not pregnant, and Elena went to the seaside resort. In the summer Mr Phosphite island, changed all one\'s life... </p> <p> out of love for Lila have anger, \"I\" (Elena) to get rid of the broken, violence, full of feud blocks. \"I\" became the first college students of blocks, and a senior intellectual family boy engaged, even published the first novel. \"I\" to the winner of the image return to Naples, only to find that she said goodbye to the ugly marriage, in the work at a meat processing plant is humiliating. </p> <p> when I found her novel, in fact completely stole the Lila entrust my secret notebook the unique strength and inspiration, \"I\" was forced to face a problem of extreme pain: \"I\" and the Lila, who left, who left? </p> <p> -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- </p> <p> both in life and in the novel, a friendship, more powerful, more rich character of the man will make the image of the weak become blurred. But in the relationship between Elena and Lila, weak Elena, from their subordinate position some intelligence - that let Lila lost the direction, the heart is dizzy dizzy. This process is very difficult to describe, but is this fascinate me. Can say so: in la and Elena in life, there are a lot of events shows a person how to draw strength from another person. But remember this: it is not only helping each other in their performance level, are also embodied in their mutual ransacked and theft of emotion and knowledge from each other, consumed each other\'s strength. </p> <p> -- Elena, rand a Italy\'s corriere Della sera newspaper interview (2011) </p> <p> Naples tetralogy wonderful and lasting to explore the affection of jealousy - this is the most deadly, because it will sometimes disguised as love myself. </p> <p> - the New York review </p> <p> about women and the fate of the Italian epic friendship... After Homer and Ovid, for the first time we have a female epicist. </p> <p> - the Atlantic </p> <p> fee rand writing is so clear, her narrative so forthright and sincere, engaging and entertaining. - the economist </p> <p> for fee rand, the primary aim of the novel, is stirring the infection, open wounds, open it and make you aware of where is the wound, the wound and come from. </p> <p> -- the Los Angeles review </p> <p> Elena to free her from those unbearable value of face, resist the temptation of secular sense of success, and from la to get (obtain) knowledge and power, but can\'t be her down... In the modern novel one of the most abundant description of friendship. </p> <p> - NPR </p> <p> everyone should see how Elena, rand signed any text. </p> <p> - the Boston globe </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787540478315', '长安十二时辰上', 'images/长安十二时辰上.jpg', '湖南文艺出版社', '历史', '59.7', '79.6', '<p>唐天宝三年，元月十四日，长安。</p><p>大唐皇都的居民不知道，上元节辉煌灯火亮起之时，等待他们的，将是场吞噬一切的劫难。</p><p>突厥、狼卫、绑架、暗杀、烈焰、焚城，毁灭长安城的齿轮已经开始转动。而拯救长安的全部希望，只有一个即将被斩首的独眼死囚和短短的十二个时辰……</p>', '< p > began three years, on January 14, changan. < / p > < p > datang emperor residents don\'t know, the Lantern Festival bright lights light up, waiting for them, will be a devouring everything. < / p > < p > turkic, wolves, who, kidnappings, assassinations, flame, burning city, destruction of the chang \'an gear has begun to turn. And save the changan all hope, there is only one is about to be beheaded one-eyed monster and short twelve hour... < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530208960', '雨季不再来', 'images/雨季不再来.jpg', '北京十月文艺出版社', '情感', '21', '28', '<p>《雨季不再来》以三毛的生命历程为主题，记录了三毛17岁到22岁的成长过程，真实呈现出三毛少女时代的成长感受，辍学、自闭、叛逆，游学西班牙、德国、美国后，渐渐成长为独立自信的青年，这本书中透露的纯真情怀和异质美感，可以清楚地印证她传奇性格的痕迹。</p>', '< p > monsoon no longer come to SAN MAO\'s life story as the theme, recorded three hair 17 to 22 years old, the growth of real presents three hair teenager\'s growth experience, dropping out of school, autistic, rebellious, travel to Spain, Germany, the United States, after gradually grow into independent self-confident youth, revealed in the book of the pure feelings and distinctive aesthetic feeling, can clearly confirm the trace of her legendary character. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787229050238', '面纱', 'images/面纱.jpg', '重庆文艺出版社', '文学', '24', '32', '<p>《面纱》由W.萨默塞特·毛姆编著。</p><p>《面纱》讲述了：容貌娇美而又爱慕虚荣的英国女子凯蒂，为了避免自己变成一位老姑娘，接受了生性孤僻的医生瓦尔特·费恩的求婚。她离开了上世纪20年代伦敦浮华而空虚的社交圈，随瓦尔特远赴神秘的东方殖民地——香港。</p><p>对婚姻感到不满和无趣，凯蒂开始悄悄与令她芳心摇动的香港助理布政司查理·唐生偷情。瓦尔特发现妻子的不忠后，孤注一掷，开始了他奇特而可怕的报复计划：凯蒂必须随他前往遥远的中国内地，去平息一场正疯狂流</p><p>行的霍乱瘟疫。在异国美丽却凶险的环境中，他们经历了在英国家乡的舒适</p><p>生活中无法想象和体验的情感波澜……在爱情、背叛与死亡的漩涡中挣扎的凯蒂，亲历了幻想破灭与生死离别之后，终将生活的面纱从她的眼前渐渐揭去，从此踏上了不悔的精神成长之路。</p><p></p>', '< p > \"veil\" by w. somerset maugham compiled. < / p > < p > \"veil\" tells the story: Katie looks beautiful and flamboyant British woman, in order to avoid themselves into an old maid, accepted by nature private doctors walter Finn to marry him. She left the glitz and empty circle in London in the 1920 s, along with walter to mysterious Oriental colonies, Hong Kong. < / p > < p > in unhappy marriages and boring, Katie began quietly and made her heart moved to Hong Kong, assistant chief secretary Charlie no cheating. Walter found after his wife\'s infidelity, put all your eggs in one basket, began his strange and terrible revenge plan: Kitty must follow him to faraway China to quell a frantic flow < / p > < p > the cholera epidemic. In exotic beautiful but dangerous environment, they have gone through the British home comfort < / p > < p > I can\'t imagine my emotion and experience in life... In the vortex of love, betrayal and death struggle Katie, witnessed disillusioned with life and death to leave after, will life veil gradually lifted from her eyes, from now on on the road to the spiritual growth of no regrets. < / p > < p > < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787545202267', '阿狸·梦之城堡', 'images/阿狸·梦之城堡.jpg', '上海锦绣文章出版社', '漫画', '27.6', '36.8', '<p>阿狸童话绘本为纯手绘创作，画风成熟稳定，颜色精美靓丽。阿狸绘本的文字脚本立足于挖掘人们内心深处的柔软与坚强，围绕亲情、爱情、友情主题，风格温暖，有发人深省的力量。</p>', '< p > o raccoon dog fairy tale picture books is pure hand-painted creation, drawing style mature and stable, exquisite color beautiful. O raccoon dog painted this script writing based on the mining soft and strong, deep in the hearts of people around the family, love, friendship, theme, style, warm, and a thought-provoking. < / p >', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544700603', '看不见的城市', 'images/看不见的城市.jpg', '译林出版社', '历史', '12', '16', '<p>《看不见的城市》的第一版是在1972年11月由都灵的埃伊纳乌迪出版社出版的。在这本书出版的时候，从1972年底到1973年初，卡尔维诺曾在多家报纸的文章和访谈中谈到它。\n</p><p>下面用卡尔维诺1983年3月29日在纽约哥伦比亚大学写作硕士班的一次讲座中的文字，来介绍“奥斯卡”丛书中的这个新版。讲座原为英文，这里用的是意大利文本，它是以1972到1973年的两次访谈为基础的，并且大部分在意大利没有发表过。（这篇讲稿后来以“卡尔维诺在看不见的城市里”为题，发表在美国的文学刊物《哥伦比亚》1983年第8期上，第37页到第42页；意大利文本的一些部分以“幸福的和不幸的看不见的城市”为题，发表在1972年12月的《意大利时尚》第253期上，第150页到第151页。）\n</p><p>在《看不见的城市》里人们找不到能认得出的城市。所有的城市都是虚构的;我给它们每一个都起了一个女人的名字。这本书是由一些短小的章节构成的，每个章节都应提供机会，让我们对某个城市或泛指意义上的城市进行反思。\n</p>', '< p > \"invisible city\" of the first edition was in Turin, in November of 1972 by Mr Magdalena udinese publishing house. In the time of publication, this book, from the end of 1972 to early 1973, italo calvino has in many newspaper articles and interviews about it.\n< / p > < p > the following with calvino on March 29, 1983 in New York\'s Columbia University master in writing a lecture in the text, to introduce the \"Oscar\" series of the new version. Former English lecture, here is the Italian text, it is 1972 to 1973, on the basis of the two interviews and most not yet published in Italy. (this article notes later with \"calvino in invisible city\", published in the American literary journals \"Columbia\" issue 8, 1983, 37 pages to page 42. Some parts of the Italian text to \"happy and unhappy invisible city\", published in the December 1972 the 253th issue of Italian fashion, page 150 to page 151).\n< / p > < p > in the \"invisible city\" people could not find the city can recognize. All the cities are fictitious; I gave them each a woman\'s name. This book is composed of several short chapters, each chapter should provide the opportunity, let us in a city or a general sense of the city.\n< / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787121087097', '把时间当作朋友', 'images/把时间当作朋友.jpg', '电子工业出版社', '心理', '24', '32', '<p>这本书从心智成长的角度来谈时间管理，指出时间管理是成功的关键所在。作者引述自己从事的职业中所遇到的事例，告诉我们：如何打开心智，如何运用心智来和时间做朋友，如何理解时间管理的意义，在时间管理上取得突破，进而用心智开启自己的人生成功之旅。</p>', '< p > this book from the perspective of mind to talk about time management, and points out that the time management is the key to success. The authors cited cases encountered in his career, tell us: how to open mind, how to use the mind to make friends with time, how to understand the meaning of time management, make a breakthrough on time management, then with the mind to open its own life journey to success. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787535439765', '一句顶一万句', 'images/一句顶一万句.jpg', '长江文艺出版社', '文学', '22.35', '29.8', '<p>《一句顶一万句》的故事很简单，小说的前半部写的是过去：孤独无助的吴摩西失去唯一能够“说得上话”的养女，为了寻找，走出延津；小说的后半部写的是现在：吴摩西养女的儿子牛爱国，同样为了摆脱孤独寻找“说得上话”的朋友，走向延津。一走一来，延宕百年。书中的人物大部分是中国最底层的老百姓，偏偏安排了一个意大利牧师老詹。</p>', '< p > \"a top ten thousand words of\" the story is very simple, the first half of the novel is written in the past: lonely helpless wu Moses lost only to \"liberation\" of sons and daughters, to find, out of the delay Zimbabwe; Novel is written in the second half of now: wu NiuAiGuo, the son of Moses, sons and daughters, also in order to get rid of loneliness to find \"liberation\" of friends, to tianjin. A walk way, delays in one hundred. Most of the characters in the book is at the bottom of the common people in China, must arrange an Italian priest old zhan. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020049929', '天使与魔鬼', 'images/天使与魔鬼.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '科学', '22.35', '29.8', '<p>虔诚的上帝信徒——欧洲原子核研究组织的杰出科学家列奥纳多·维特勒毕生致力于以科学的手段证明神的存在。他和其养女、神秘妩媚的科学家维特多利亚在实验室里进行高度机密的试验，成功地制造出了一种极其强大的能量——“反物质”。</p><p>在这个重大发现尚未对外公布时，列奥纳多在实验室里惨遭杀害，一颗眼珠被凶手挖走，胸口上赫然印着一个神秘的标记——“光照派”！更令人震惊的是，藏在地下的反物质不翼而飞。哈佛大学的符号学专家罗伯特·兰登应欧洲原子核研究组织首领之邀，前来调查这个神秘的符号。就在他到达的当天，失踪的反物质在梵蒂冈城地下某处被人发现。离开了实验室的反物质，会在二十四小时之后自行爆炸。这天正是天主教教皇选举日。来自世界各地的天主教首领会聚在梵蒂冈城，藏在地下的反物质就如同一枚定时炸弹，如不能及时找到，整个梵蒂冈城便会在顷刻间灰飞烟灭。</p><p>形势刻不容缓，兰登与维特多利亚一起踏上了前往梵蒂冈的冒险之旅……</p>', '< p > devout believers god - CERN distinguished scientist leonardo da victor le lifelong committed to scientific means to prove that god exists. He and his sons and daughters, mysterious charm of the scientist vittoria highly confidential experiment was carried out in the laboratory, successfully created a very powerful energy -- \"antimatter\". < / p > < p > when this important discovery has not yet been announced, leonardo was killed in the laboratory, a eyes were killers poached, impressively printing a mysterious mark in the chest - \"illuminati\"! Even more shocking, hidden in the underground disappearance of antimatter. Harvard symbologist Robert langdon, at the invitation of the CERN leader to investigate this mysterious symbols. On the day he arrived, the disappearance of antimatter was found somewhere in the Vatican city underground. Left the lab of antimatter, will explode after 24 hours. It was the Catholic Pope election day. Catholic leaders from around the world gather in the Vatican city, hide in the ground antimatter would like a time bomb, such as is not found in time, the whole city will be swept away in the Vatican. < / p > < p > well, langdon with vittoria took to the Vatican\'s adventure... < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536023925', '第一炉香', 'images/第一炉香.jpg', '花城出版社', '文学', '8.625', '11.5', '<p>沉香屑---第一炉香沉香屑---第二炉香茉莉香片心经封锁琉璃瓦年轻的时候花凋中国的日夜</p>', '< p > the first furnace aloes crumbs - sweet aloes crumbs - the second furnace fragrant jasmine scented tea heart sutra block glazed tile young flower sent Chinese day and night from < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020056088', '尼罗河上的惨案', 'images/尼罗河上的惨案.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '16.5', '22', '<p>林内特·里奇维被一颗子弹打穿了头颅，尼罗河之旅的宁静也因此被打破。这位年轻，美丽，时尚——拥有一切的女孩，最终失去了自己的生命。</p><p>赫尔克里·波洛的耳边回响着早先一位旅伴的话语：“我真想用我那把亲爱的小手枪顶着她的头，扣动扳机。”然而在这异国他乡的场景中，一切并不像表面显示的那样平静……</p>', '< p > lynette Ritchie d by a bullet through the head, the Nile of peace has been broken. The young, beautiful, fashion, girl who has everything, eventually lost her life. < / p > < p > hull kerry poirot ears echoed the words of a companion earlier: \"I really want to use my dear little handgun under her head, pull the trigger.\" In this exotic scenario, however, everything is not like according to the surface of the calm... < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787509002780', 'ZOO', 'images/ZOO.jpg', '当代世界出版社', '魔幻', '15', '20', '<p>每天早上都有一张我女朋友尸体的照片放到我的收件箱里，照片显示着女朋友的尸体正在一天天地生蛆、腐化。她是在我们去过动物园之后失踪的。所有人都认为她只是失踪了，只有我知道她被杀了。我辞了职，拿着她生前的照片四处寻找凶手的线索，一副心力憔悴的模样。然而苦心寻找的背后隐藏的却是我不愿面对的真相，是我亲手杀了她……</p>', '< p > every morning there was a picture of my girlfriend body into my inbox, photo shows the girlfriend is day earth born maggots, decay. She is missing after we have been to the zoo. Everyone thinks she is just missing, only I know that she was killed. I quit my job, take her picture clues to search for the murderer, a pair of heart gaunt appearance. Yet it was hard to find hidden behind I don\'t want to face the truth, I have killed her... < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532726745', '国境以南太阳以西', 'images/国境以南太阳以西.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '魔幻', '10.125', '13.5', '<p>37岁的男主人公，在东京市区拥有两家兴旺的酒吧，还有娇美的妻子，可爱的女儿，他是一位真正的成功人士。但是，他的内心还是感到饥饿干渴，事业和家庭都填补不了，而让他那缺憾的部分充盈起来的，是他小学时的女友岛本。岛本不愿吐露自己的经历、身份、只希望他就这样接受眼前的自己，只把她当成小学时那个爱古典乐的女孩。然而，就在他接受了这不可能接受的条件时，两人却在箱根别墅度过了销魂的一夜。翌晨，她一去杳然、再无踪迹可寻了。</p>', '< p > 37, the hero, has two thriving bar in downtown Tokyo, and beautiful wife, lovely daughter, he is a real success. However, his heart still feel hunger, thirst, career and family are not fill, and make him the defects of filling up, this is his girlfriend elementary school island. Island this reluctant to give vent to their experiences, identity, and so I just hope he accept present themselves, just as her primary school when the girl love classical music. However, just when he accepted it can\'t be accept, but two people in hakone villa had a lovely night. Next morning, she a to hammer, no trace to be found. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787549530816', '文学回忆录（全2册）', 'images/文学回忆录（全2册）.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '文学', '73.5', '98', '<p>文学是可爱的。生活是好玩的。艺术是要有所牺牲的。</p><p>八十年代末，木心客居纽约时期，亦自他恢复写作、持续出书以来，纽约地面的大陆和台湾同行在异国谋饭之中，居然促成木心开讲“世界文学史”，忽忽长达五年的一场“文学的远征”——从1989年1月15日开课，到1994年1月9日最后一课，每位听课人轮流提供自家客厅，在座者有画家、舞蹈家、史家、雕刻家等等。</p><p>听课学生陈丹青说，“我们当年这样地胡闹一场，回想起来，近于荒谬的境界：没有注册，没有教室，没有课本，没有考试与证书，更没有赞助与课题费，不过是在纽约市皇后区、曼哈顿区、布鲁克林区的不同寓所中，团团坐拢来，听木心神聊。”</p><p>菜单开出来，大家选。从古希腊神话、新旧约，到诗经、楚辞，从中世纪欧洲文学，到二十世纪文学世界，东方西方通讲，知识灵感并作。其中听的听，讲的讲，“金句”纷披，兀自燃烧。“讲完后，一部文学史，重要的是我的观点。”木心说。古代，中世纪，近代，每个时代都能找到精神血统，艺术亲人。</p><p>他爱先秦典籍，只为诸子的文学才华；他以为今日所有伪君子身上，仍然活着孔丘；他想对他爱敬的尼采说：从哲学跑出来吧；他激赏拜伦、雪莱、海涅，却说他们其实不太会作诗；他说托尔斯泰可惜“头脑不行”，但讲到托翁坟头不设十字架，不设墓碑，忽而语音低弱了，颤声说：“伟大！”而谈及萨特的葬礼，木心脸色一正，引尼采的话：唯有戏子才能唤起群众巨大的兴奋。</p><p>木心开讲时六十二岁。多少民国书籍与读者，湮灭了。他的一生，密集伴随愈演愈烈的文化断层。他不肯断，而居然不曾断，这就是纽约世界文学史讲座潜藏的背景：在累累断层之间、之外、之后，木心始终将自己尽可能置于世界性的文学景观，倘若不是出走，这顽强而持久的挣扎，几乎濒于徒劳。</p><p>如今，听课学生陈丹青整理那五年那五册听课笔记，共八十五讲，逾四十万字，结集这本大书时，已不再将之仅仅看做“世界文学史讲座”。诚如木心所最早时设想的那样，这是他自己的“文学回忆录”，是一部“荒诞小说”，“在自己的身上，克服这个时代”。</p><p>这也是木心留给世界的礼物，文学的福音书。</p><p>本书首次披露的木心先生及其亲属的珍贵照片，由陈丹青先生和木心的外甥王韦先生提供。附印民国版本的世界文学书影，是一部民国出版史的私人旁证。</p>', '< p > literature is lovely. Life is fun. Art is to sacrifice. < / p > < p > in the late eighty s, wood heart away New York times, also since resume writing, his last book, New York, the ground of the mainland and Taiwan counterparts abroad for rice, heart to speak of \"world literature\" has contributed to wood, huhu for up to five years of a \"literature of the expedition\" - offered from January 15, 1989, to the last lecture on January 9, 1994, each class of people take turns to provide their own living room, here is a painter, dancer, historians, sculptor, and so on. < / p > < p > a class student Chen said, \"we had such a knock, looking back, almost ridiculous state: no registration, no classrooms, no textbooks, no test and certificate, more no sponsorship and purchases, but is different in New York City, Manhattan, brooklyn, queens abode, by gathering, listen to kill time wood heart.\" < / p > < p > menu out, you choose. From the ancient Greek myth, the new old testament to the book of songs, chu ci, from medieval European literature, to the literary world of the 20th century, the east west tong, inspiration and knowledge. Which listen to listen to, speak, golden words mixed and disorganized, bound to burn. \"Finished, after a history of literature, it is important to my point of view.\" Wood said. Ancient, medieval and modern times, each time can find spiritual heritage, artistic family. < / p > < p > he love the classics, for various literary talent; He thought all hypocrite, today still alive Confucius; He want to say to his love to Nietzsche: ran from the philosophy; He appreciate byron, Shelley, Heine, will say that they don\'t actually poetry; Tolstoy\'s a pity, he said, \"mind\", but when it comes to supporting weng tomb no cross, no tombstone, and weak voice low, warbling said: \"great!\" When it comes to Sartre\'s funeral, wood heart face a positive, Nietzsche\'s words: only player that can arouse the great excitement. < / p > < p > wood heart began at the age of sixty-two. How many books and readers of the republic of China, annihilation. His whole life, dense with intensified cultural fault. He will not break, and was never broken, this is the background of the New York world literature lecture hidden: outside, between faults and, after, wood heart always put himself as much as possible in the world literary landscape, if not, the tenacious and persistent struggle, almost to the very verge of futility. < / p > < p > now, listen to the teacher student Chen to sort out the five years that five volumes of notes in class, a total of eighty five speakers, more than four hundred thousand words, this big book collected, no longer will be just as lecture of \"world literature\". As wood heart wants when the earliest suppose, that this is his memoirs \"literature\", is a \"absurd novels\", \"on their own to overcome the age\". < / p > < p > this is wood heart for the gift of the world, the Gospel of literature. < / p > < p > this book disclosed for the first time Mr Wood heart and rare photographs of the relatives, by Mr Chen and Mr Wang wei\'s nephew wood heart. Transcript version of the world literature certificates of the republic of China, is a publishing private circumstantial evidence of the republic of China. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787530208687', '七夜雪', 'images/七夜雪.jpg', '北京十月文艺出版社', '情感', '18.75', '25', '<p>鼎剑阁霍展白为救治昔日恋人之子沫儿的病，用七年的时间拼死取得了药王谷主人薛紫夜开给他的七味绝世药引，魔教大光明宫排位第一的神秘杀手瞳为了自己能杀死魔教教主获得自由而抢夺龙血赤寒珠，霍展白和瞳在打斗中双双重伤，被薛紫夜送回药王谷治疗。沫儿的病事实上无法治疗，薛紫夜为一直隐瞒着霍展白而不安，不顾自己寒症孱弱之身而设法寻找疗法。与此同时，薛紫夜震惊地发现这个能用眼神控制人精神的杀手瞳竟然是失散多年的儿时伙伴明介……</p>', '< p > ding JianGe huo show white for the disease of cure the child of former lovers MoEr already spent seven years to get the valley who master Xue Zi night is always ready to his seven flavor medicine led, magic big bright palace mysterious killer pupil in the first position in order to teach you can kill the magic leader to be free and rob cold blood red dragon bead, Mr White and pupil both badly hurt in the struggle, be returned Xue Zi night who valley treatment. MoEr disease has no cure, in fact Xue Zi night show white and uncomfortable to have concealed the huo, regardless of their han zheng of the weak and tried to look for the therapy. Xue Zi night, meanwhile, shocked to find that killer can use the eyes to control people the spirit of the pupil is long-lost childhood friend MingJie... < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544268417', '没有色彩的多崎作和他的巡礼之年', 'images/没有色彩的多崎作和他的巡礼之年.jpg', '南海出版公司', '情感', '29.625', '39.5', '<p>“并不是一切都消失在了时间的长河里。那时，我们坚定地相信某种东西，拥有能坚定地相信某种东西的自我。这样的信念绝不会毫无意义地烟消云散”——十六年的彷徨迷惑，换来一场决然的巡礼之年，当最后一块拼图集齐，重回完满的正五边形，剩下最稀薄的人，重建大地。</p><p>人若真的受伤，通常会无法直视伤口，想隐藏它忘却它，把心门关起来。这是一个成长的故事。要成长，伤痛就得大一点，伤口就得深一点。——村上春树</p><p>----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p>在名古屋上高中时，多崎作有四个非常要好的朋友，两男两女，他们的姓氏都带有色彩——“赤”、“青”、“白”、“黑”，唯独多崎作的姓名中没有色彩，也只有他离开名古屋到东京读大学。大二假期返乡之际，多崎作突然被四位朋友告知要绝交，对原因没有任何说明。他深受打击，几至形销骨立，许久许久才恢复过来。</p><p>十六年来，他们始终没有见面.如今已经三十六岁的多崎作，在女朋友的劝告下，终于下决心去拜访抛弃自己的四个朋友，弄清真相。由此开始他的“巡礼之年”。当最后一块拼图集齐，谜底揭开，十六年前的秘密、十六年间的变化，以及十六年后的结局，都令人唏嘘伤痛。</p>', '< p > \"are not all disappear in the long river of time. At that time, we firmly believe in something, have to firmly believe something yourself. The belief never meaningless to dissipate \"- 16 years of hesitation, in exchange for a tour of the year and collected when the last piece of the puzzle, to return to full pentagon, left the thin person, reconstruction of the earth. < / p > < p > if a man really injured, usually can\'t look straight into the wound, he wants to hide it forget it, close the door. This is a growth story. To grow, and the pain is bigger, the wound is deeper. Haruki murakami < / p > < p > -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- < / p > < p > in Nagoya in high school, more battery as there are four very good friends, two men and two women, their surname with colour - \"red\", \"green\", \"white\" and \"black\", but more battery as no color in name, and only he left to go to university in Tokyo Nagoya. Sophomore year vacation home, suddenly more battery as told by the four friends want to break up, because no explanation. He just hit, a few to the bones, for a long time for a long time to recover. < / p > < p > for 16 years, they never meet. Now has more than 36, 43, under the advice of his girlfriend, finally determined to visit abandoned their four friends, find out the truth. Began his years of the \"tour\". Collected when the last piece of the puzzle, uncovered the answer, the secret of sixteen years ago, the change of 16 years, and the end of the 16 years, are moving. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787561334386', '京华烟云', 'images/京华烟云.jpg', '陕西师范大学出版社', '文学', '32.25', '43', '<p>《京华烟云》是林语堂旅居巴黎时于1938年8月至1939年8月间用英文写就的长篇小说，并题献给“英勇的中国士兵”，英文书名为MomentinPeking，《京华烟云》是它转译为中文后的书名，也有译本将本书译为《瞬息京华》。林语堂原本打算将《红楼梦》译作英文介绍给西方读者，因故未能译成，此后决定仿照《红楼梦》的结构写一部长篇小说，于是写出了《京华烟云》。</p><p>小说讲述了北平曾、姚、牛三大家族从1901年义和团运动到抗日战争30多年间的悲观离合和恩怨情仇，并在其中安插了袁世凯篡国、张勋复辟、直奉大战、军阀割据、“五四”运动、“三·一八”惨案、“语丝派”与“现代评论派”笔战、青年“左倾”、二战爆发等历史事件，全景式展现了现代中国社会风云变幻的历史风貌。《京华烟云》自1939年底在美国出版后的短短半年内即行销5万多册，美国《时代》周刊称其“极有可能成为关于现代中国社会现实的经典作品”。</p>', '<p> literature is lovely. Life is fun. Art is to sacrifice. </p> <p> in the late eighty s, wood heart away New York times, also since resume writing, his last book, New York, the ground of the mainland and Taiwan counterparts abroad for rice, heart to speak of \"world literature\" has contributed to wood, huhu for up to five years of a \"literature of the expedition\" - offered from January 15, 1989, to the last lecture on January 9, 1994, each class of people take turns to provide their own living room, here is a painter, dancer, historians, sculptor, and so on. </p> <p> a class student Chen said, \"we had such a knock, looking back, almost ridiculous state: no registration, no classrooms, no textbooks, no test and certificate, more no sponsorship and purchases, but is different in New York City, Manhattan, brooklyn, queens abode, by gathering, listen to kill time wood heart.\" </p> <p> menu out, you choose. From the ancient Greek myth, the new old testament to the book of songs, chu ci, from medieval European literature, to the literary world of the 20th century, the east west tong, inspiration and knowledge. Which listen to listen to, speak, golden words mixed and disorganized, bound to burn. \"Finished, after a history of literature, it is important to my point of view.\" Wood said. Ancient, medieval and modern times, each time can find spiritual heritage, artistic family. </p> <p> he love the classics, for various literary talent; He thought all hypocrite, today still alive Confucius; He want to say to his love to Nietzsche: ran from the philosophy; He appreciate byron, Shelley, Heine, will say that they don\'t actually poetry; Tolstoy\'s a pity, he said, \"mind\", but when it comes to supporting weng tomb no cross, no tombstone, and weak voice low, warbling said: \"great!\" When it comes to Sartre\'s funeral, wood heart face a positive, Nietzsche\'s words: only player that can arouse the great excitement. </p> <p> wood heart began at the age of sixty-two. How many books and readers of the republic of China, annihilation. His whole life, dense with intensified cultural fault. He will not break, and was never broken, this is the background of the New York world literature lecture hidden: outside, between faults and, after, wood heart always put himself as much as possible in the world literary landscape, if not, the tenacious and persistent struggle, almost to the very verge of futility. </p> <p> now, listen to the teacher student Chen to sort out the five years that five volumes of notes in class, a total of eighty five speakers, more than four hundred thousand words, this big book collected, no longer will be just as lecture of \"world literature\". As wood heart wants when the earliest suppose, that this is his memoirs \"literature\", is a \"absurd novels\", \"on their own to overcome the age\". </p> <p> this is wood heart for the gift of the world, the Gospel of literature. </p> <p> this book disclosed for the first time Mr Wood heart and rare photographs of the relatives, by Mr Chen and Mr Wang wei\'s nephew wood heart. Transcript version of the world literature certificates of the republic of China, is a publishing private circumstantial evidence of the republic of China. </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020035946', '哈姆莱特', 'images/哈姆莱特.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '5.25', '7', '<p>本书是大学生必读丛书中的一册，书中以教育部全国高等学校中文学科教学指导委员会指定书目为依据，收录了英国著名作家莎士比亚先生的话剧《哈姆莱特》。</p><p>本书具有很强的经典性及学术性，该书不仅是语言文学专业大学生从事专业学习和学术研究不可缺少的重要书籍，同时也是其他专业大学生加强人文素养、丰富文化底蕴、促进专业学习的重要读物。可供不同专业的大学生阅读收藏。</p>', '<p> ding JianGe huo show white for the disease of cure the child of former lovers MoEr already spent seven years to get the valley who master Xue Zi night is always ready to his seven flavor medicine led, magic big bright palace mysterious killer pupil in the first position in order to teach you can kill the magic leader to be free and rob cold blood red dragon bead, Mr White and pupil both badly hurt in the struggle, be returned Xue Zi night who valley treatment. MoEr disease has no cure, in fact Xue Zi night show white and uncomfortable to have concealed the huo, regardless of their han zheng of the weak and tried to look for the therapy. Xue Zi night, meanwhile, shocked to find that killer can use the eyes to control people the spirit of the pupil is long-lost childhood friend MingJie... </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806399057', '万水千山走遍', 'images/万水千山走遍.jpg', '哈尔滨出版社', '文学', '10.35', '13.8', '<p>大地啊，我来到你岸上时原是一个陌生人，住在你房子里时原是一个旅客，而今我离开你的门时却是一个朋友了。当飞机降落在墨西哥首都的机场时，我的体力已经透支得几乎无法举步。长长的旅程，别人睡觉，我一直在看书。眼看全机的人都慢慢地走了，还让自己绑在安全带上。窗外的机场灯光通明，是夜间了。</p>', '< p >, o earth: I came to your shore was a stranger, I lived in your house was a passenger, now when I leave your door is one of my friends. When the plane landed in the Mexican capital airport, my strength was almost not have overdraft life. The long journey, people sleeping, I have been reading. To see the person of whole machine is walking slowly, also let himself tied to the seat belt. The airport lights lit out of the window, it is night. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020026456', '海子的诗', 'images/海子的诗.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '11.55', '15.4', '<p>本书收录了已故诗人海子的诗作精华，其诗以独特的风格深受读者的喜爱，从这些诗中反映出诗人那对于一切美好事物的眷恋之情，对于生命的世俗和崇高的激动和关怀。</p>', '< p > this book included the essence the late poet of haizi\'s poems, his poems with unique style was deeply loved by readers, from the poems reflect the poet of attachment that for all the good things, for the secular and high excitement and care of life. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020123728', '芳华', 'images/芳华.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '29.25', '39', '<p>从军经历伴随了严歌苓整个的青春年华。当她后来成为了一个作家，这段经历成了她取之不竭的创作源泉。《一个女兵的悄悄话》《雌性的草地》《灰舞鞋》《白麻雀》《爱犬颗勒》，都以部队生活为题材，但多是以一个作家的客观视角来为那个时代的军人塑像。而她*创作的长篇小说《芳华》则具有浓厚的个人自传色彩，是以*人称描写她当年亲历的部队文工团生活：隐藏在西南部都城的一座旧红楼里、某部队文工团的内景中发生的军版“才子佳人”的故事。</p><p>《芳华》涵盖了严歌苓的青春与成长期，她在四十余年后回望这段经历，笔端蕴含了饱满的情感。青春荷尔蒙冲动下的少男少女的懵懂激情，由激情犯下的过错，由过错生出的懊悔，还有那个特殊的时代背景，种种，构成了《芳华》对一段历史、一群人以及潮流更替、境遇变迁的复杂感怀。今天的作者严歌苓与当时的小女兵萧穗子在作品里构成了理性与感性的对话关系，重新呈现了当时年代里青春的混沌、感性与蒙昧。生命的恣肆与人性的层次以及时代的的特征构成了《芳华》繁复的调性，它向读者打开了多层面的认识路径。</p>', '< p > while serving with the yan geling entire youth. When she later became a writer, this experience has become her limitless reserve. Whisper to a female, the female grass \"the gray shoes\" dog star \", \"white sparrow\" depicting the army life, but is more a writer\'s objective Angle of view for the soldier statues of that era. Her * creation novel \"the youth\", have a strong personal autobiography color is called * about life: she experienced troops ensemble hidden in the capital city in the southwest of an old red chamber, one army ensemble occurring in the interior of the version of the story of \"beauties\". < / p > < p > \"the youth\" covers the youth and growth period, yan geling her back at the experience, after more than 40 years, potentially contains a full of emotions. Hormones under the impulse of youth foolish passion of boys and girls, from passion committed fault, the fault of remorse, and the special time background, and constitutes the \"youth\" on a piece of history, a group of people as well as the trend of the change, complex shrine of weather change. Today the writer yan geling and small women xiao ears in work at that time the dialogue relationship between rationality and sensibility, re-render the s was in chaos, sensibility and ignorance of youth. The arrogant and the hierarchy of human nature of life and constitute the characteristics of the era of \"youth\" the tone of heavy and complicated, it opened the multifaceted understanding path to the readers. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787805674278', '教父', 'images/教父.jpg', '译林出版社', '文学', '17.475', '23.3', '<p>《教父》这部小说的不同凡响的艺术魅力就在于：尽管描写的全是坏蛋，但作者曲尽妙笔，竟然能让读者不痛恨个别坏蛋，而痛恨整个龌龊的社会结构。教父及其继承人——他的小儿子迈克尔本来都是坏透了的坏蛋，但是却并不显得令人痛恨，因为他们杀人是整个不合理的社会逼出来的，因为他们杀的也都是更坏的人，他们同那些在幕后“坐地分赃”的政客比较起来，在“坏”的程度上，可真是小巫见大巫了。</p><p></p><p>美国纽约五大黑势力集团之一的维托·考利昂一家采用多种极端手段，实现了在整个美国黑暗势力团体中的独尊地位。在这场斗争中有黑团伙之间的火拼；有走私贩毒的嚣张；有赌场的烟云；有红灯区的人欲横流。本书被认为是描写资本主义社会中黑社会现象的最具权威的作品。</p><p></p><p>&#34;&gt;教父英文版&gt;&gt;</p>', '< p > \"the godfather\" the outstanding artistic charm of the novel is that although the description is full of bad guys, but the author do far, he can let the reader individual bad guys, don\'t hate and hate the dirty social structure. Godfather and its successor, his youngest son Michael could have been a bad bad guys, but it does not seem to be hated, because they are killing people is the unreasonable social force, because they killed them were worse, they with those politicians who sit here \"spoils\" behind the scenes, on the degree of \"bad\", is dwarfed. < / p > < p > < / p > < p > in New York, one of the five big black power group Vito does Leon family USES the many kinds of extreme measures, implements the dark forces groups throughout the United States in the first place. In this struggle has black gang warfare between; Have the arrogance of drug trafficking; Casino smoke; The society where profit-worship became a red-light district. The book is considered to be describe underworld phenomenon in capitalist society the most authoritative works. < / p > < p > < / p > < p >', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532710942', '雾都孤儿', 'images/雾都孤儿.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '7.575', '10.1', '<p>孤儿奥立弗・退斯特从小在贫民习艺所受尽欺凌，逃到伦敦后又陷入贼窟。身边的世界像一台疯狂运转的机器，小奥立弗却努力坚守着心底深处的纯净与高贵。这份执著终于帮他等来了柳暗花明：布朗劳先生、梅里太太等人及时伸出援助之手；与此同时，奥立弗奇特的身世，也一步步真相大白。小说深刻揭示社会弊病的同时，也在英国文学史上留下一连串栩栩如生的人物形象，一百多年来深受读者爱戴。</p>', '< p > the orphan oliver ・ retreat, grew up in the poor abused by brouwer, fled to London after a thief wat. Around the world like a running machine, small oliver trying to stick to the bottom of the heart in the depth of the pure and noble. The persistent finally help him to materialise: Mr Brown\'s hand, mrs.merriwether and others in a timely manner; At the same time, oliver strange life, step by step, also the truth. Novel reveals social ills, also left a series of vivid characters in the history of British literature, more than one hundred years well liked by his readers. < / p >', '8.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506324298', '蔷薇岛屿', 'images/蔷薇岛屿.jpg', '作家出版社', '文学', '13.5', '18', '<p>《蔷薇岛屿》安妮宝贝的第四本书。内容为在上海、北京、香港、越南、柬埔寨一路旅途中拍摄的照片及写下的字，留下时光和幻觉的印记，是一本关于旅行、爱和生死的影像书。包括《再见，时光》、《赤道往北21度》、《在西贡》、《危险的美感》、《世俗生活》等17篇散文，以及小说《一场上海烟花》。</p>', '<p> while serving with the yan geling entire youth. When she later became a writer, this experience has become her limitless reserve. Whisper to a female, the female grass \"the gray shoes\" dog star \", \"white sparrow\" depicting the army life, but is more a writer\'s objective Angle of view for the soldier statues of that era. Her * creation novel \"the youth\", have a strong personal autobiography color is called * about life: she experienced troops ensemble hidden in the capital city in the southwest of an old red chamber, one army ensemble occurring in the interior of the version of the story of \"beauties\". </p> <p> \"the youth\" covers the youth and growth period, yan geling her back at the experience, after more than 40 years, potentially contains a full of emotions. Hormones under the impulse of youth foolish passion of boys and girls, from passion committed fault, the fault of remorse, and the special time background, and constitutes the \"youth\" on a piece of history, a group of people as well as the trend of the change, complex shrine of weather change. Today the writer yan geling and small women xiao ears in work at that time the dialogue relationship between rationality and sensibility, re-render the s was in chaos, sensibility and ignorance of youth. The arrogant and the hierarchy of human nature of life and constitute the characteristics of the era of \"youth\" the tone of heavy and complicated, it opened the multifaceted understanding path to the readers. </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563344970', '娱乐至死', 'images/娱乐至死.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '社会', '22.35', '29.8', '<p>《娱乐至死》是对20世纪后半叶美国文化中最重大变化的探究和哀悼：印刷术时代步入没落，而电视时代蒸蒸日上；电视改变了公众话语的内容和意义；政治、宗教、教育和任何其他公共事务领域的内容，都不可避免的被电视的表达方式重新定义。电视的一般表达方式是娱乐。一切公众话语都日渐以娱乐的方式出现，并成为一种文化精神。一切文化内容都心甘情愿地成为娱乐的附庸，而且毫无怨言，甚至无声无息，“其结果是我们成了一个娱乐至死的物种”。</p>', '< p > \"the entertainment to death\" is the most significant changes in the 20th century American culture to explore and mourning: printing era into decline, and the television era booming; Television has changed the content and meaning of public discourse; Politics, religion, education, and any other content in the field of public affairs, inevitably the expression of TV is redefined. The general expression for TV entertainment. All public discourse has appeared in the form of entertainment, and become a kind of cultural spirit. All cultural content willingly become subservient to the entertainment, and without complaint, even silent, \"as a result, we became an entertainment to death species\". < / p >', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544255264', '新参者', 'images/新参者.jpg', '南海出版公司', '悬疑', '21', '28', '<p>东野圭吾继《白夜行》《嫌疑人X的献身》之后最重磅作品！</p><p>日本两大推理榜年度冠军</p><p>东野圭吾“加贺恭一郎系列”迄今最高杰作</p><p>2010年“这本推理小说了不起！BEST10”年度第1名</p><p>2009年“《周刊文春》推理小说BEST10”年度第1名</p><p>日本《读卖新闻》“年度最佳图书”</p><p>日本亚马逊网站四星半高分评价</p><p>同名日剧由阿部宽主演，收视率超20%，高居榜首</p><p>《新参者》是东野圭吾“加贺恭一郎系列”的第8部，被公认为该系列迄今最高杰作。在本作品中，高手加贺能解开谜团，凭借的不是天马行空的想象，也不是严密逻辑的推理，而是“情”。</p><p>东京，洋溢着浓浓传统风情的日本桥地区，一个刚搬来的独身女子惨遭勒杀，刚调任此地警局的刑警加贺着手调查。</p><p>父女争吵、母子误解、婆媳矛盾……在市井生活的平凡表面下，加贺抽丝剥茧，不仅破解情感之谜，还原疑案真相，更秉持悲悯之心，疗治案件带来的创伤，给痛苦者鼓励，让受挫者前行……</p><p>关于加贺恭一郎：</p><p>他不抽烟，牙齿雪白，肩膀宽阔，轮廓分明，眼神犀利，笑容温暖。</p><p>他沉稳敏锐，细致执著，知识渊博，涉猎广泛。</p><p>他曾获日本剑道冠军，谦逊有礼，重情重义，强悍又温柔。</p><p>敬请关注加贺恭一郎系列：《毕业》《沉睡的森林》《谁杀了她》《恶意》《我杀了他》《又一个谎言》《红手指》《新参者》……</p>', '< p > tolo keigo following the \"white night\" \"suspect X dedication\" after the heavy works! < / p > < p > the list two reasoning annual title < / p > < p > tolo keigo \"add He Gong ichiro series\" so far the highest masterpiece < / p > < p > 2010 \"this mystery! BEST10 \"year 1 name < / p > < p > 2009\" the weekly bunshun, mystery novels BEST10 \"year 1 name < / p > < p > the yomiuri shimbun, Japan\" the year book \"< / p > < p > amazon\'s Japanese website four and a half high score evaluation < / p > < p > they of the same name starring Abe wide, at the top ratings than 20 � < / p > < p > the new parameter is tolo keigo\" add He Gong ichiro series \"the 8th, is recognized as the supreme masterpiece the series so far. In this work, the master of extras can unravel myths, with lofty thought, also is not a strict logical reasoning, but \"love\". < / p > < p > Tokyo, permeated with the thick region amorous feelings of the traditional Japanese bridge, just moved to a single woman were killed, police detective extras just moved here to investigate. < / p > < p > quarrel between father and daughter, mother and child misunderstanding, old woman daughter-in-law contradiction... Under the ordinary surface of community life, cobwebs extras, not only break the emotional mystery, mystery truth, adhere to the heart of compassion, heal the trauma case, encouragement, give the miserable setback let move on...... < / p > < p > about add He Gong ichiro: < / p > < p > he doesn\'t smoke, white teeth, broad shoulders, chiseled, sharp eyes and warm smile. < / p > < p > he composed, meticulous, knowledgeable, wide-ranging. < / p > < p > he had won the Japanese kendo, civility, a heavy feeling heavy righteousness, tough and gentle. < / p > < p > please pay attention to add He Gong ichiro series: \"the graduate\" sleeping \"wood\" malicious \"\" who killed her?\" \"I killed him\" \"and a lie\" \"red fingers\" new and \"... < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787503915864', '我的精神家园', 'images/我的精神家园.jpg', '文化艺术出版社', '文学', '14.1', '18.8', '<p>一九九七年六月，王小波逝世两个月后，他的杂文自选集《我的精神家园》出版。这是第一版的封面。相比于2002版出版的《我的精神家园》纪念版来说，这一版本没有纪念文章，只收有王自己的文字。当时这本书，和九七年五月第一次在大陆出版的《黄金时代》《白银时代》和《青铜时代》一起上架，十月又出版了《沉默的大多数》。一时间，大家都知道了，有一个王小波。可惜，那时他已辞世，只留下书店里满架的王小波，像一场喧哗无声的葬礼。</p>', '< p > in June 1997, wang has died two months later, his essays essays published \"my spiritual home\". This is the first version of the cover. Compared with the 2002 version of the publication of my spiritual home edition, this edition commemorative articles, only accept there\'s unfaithful text. At that time, the book, and published on the mainland for the first time in May 97 the \"golden age\" of \"the silver age\" and \"Bronze Age\" together, and published the \"silent majority\" in October. At that time, we all know, there is a wang. Unfortunately, at that time he has died, leaving only the bookstore full frame of wang-xiaobo, roar like a silent funeral. < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532127221', '妻妾成群', 'images/妻妾成群.jpg', '上海文艺出版社', '文学', '17.25', '23', '<p>《妻妾成群》借旧中国特有的封建家庭模式作小说的框架，一个男人娶了四个女人做太太。但作者关心的不是一个男人如何在四个女人中周旋，如何控制她们，而是关心四个女人怎会把她们一齐拴在一个男人的脖子上，并且像一棵濒临枯萎的藤蔓在稀薄的空气中相互绞杀而争得那一点点空气。</p><p>《妻妾成群》被改编为电影《大红灯笼高高挂》，张艺谋导演，获奥斯卡金像奖提名。</p>', '< p > in the \"harem\" borrow characteristic of the feudal family pattern as a novel framework, a man who had four women do wife. But the authors concern is not how a man in the four women, how to control them, but about four women how can them tied together in a man\'s neck, and vines wither like a tree close to kill each other in the thin air and fight for that little air. < / p > < p > \"harem\" was adapted for film raise the red lantern \", zhang yimou, won the academy award nomination. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563397648', '台北人', 'images/台北人.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '文学', '28.5', '38', '<p>作为20世纪中文小说100强的《台北人》，是一部深具复杂性的短篇小说集，由十四个一流的短篇小说构成，串联成一体，则效果遽然增加，不但小说之幅面变广，使我们看到社会之“众生相”，更重要的，由于主题命意之一再重复，与互相陪衬辅佐，使我们能更进一步深入了解作品之含义，并使我们得以一窥隐藏在作品内的作者之人生观与宇宙观。《台北人》之人物，可以说囊括了台北都市社会之各阶层：从年迈挺拔的儒将朴公（《梁父吟》）到退休了的女仆顺恩嫂（《思旧赋》），从上流社会的窦夫人（《游园惊梦》）到下流社会的“总司令”（《孤恋花》）。有知识分子，如《冬夜》之余嵚磊教授；有商人，如《花桥荣记》之老板娘；有帮佣工人，如《那血一般红的杜鹃花》之王雄；有军队里的人，如《岁除》之赖鸣升；有社交界名女，如尹雪艳；有低级舞女，如金大班。这些“大”人物、“中”人物与“小”人物，来自中国大陆不同的省籍或都市（上海、南京、四川、湖南、桂林、北平等），他们贫富悬殊，行业各异，但没有一个不背负着一段沉重的、斩不断的往事。而这份“过去”，这份“记忆”，或多或少与中华民国成立到大陆沦陷那段“忧患重重的时代”，有直接的关系。</p>', '< p > as the 20th century Chinese novel, \"100\" Taipei people \", is a profound complexity of short stories, made up of fourteen first-rate short story, the series as a body, the effect of spurt, novels of wide wide, not only make us to see the \"mixed\" of society, more important, because one of theme meaning to repeat, with foil for each other, enable us to further understand the meaning of work, and enables us to see the hidden within the work of the author\'s outlook on life and world view. Taipei people, \"characters, can include social from all walks of Taipei city: from elderly forceful RuJiang PiaoGong (Liang Fu songs) to retire the maid shun sister-in-law (\" nostalgia fu\"), and from the upper-class DouFuRen (\" the peony pavilion \") to the underworld \"commander-in-chief\" (\" the solitary flower \"). Intellectuals, such as \"winter\" of Qin lei professor; A businessman, such as flower bridge RongJi, \"the wife of shop-owner; There are domestic workers, such as the blood red azalea, \"hung king; Have the people in the army, such as New Year\'s eve, \"Lai Mingsheng; A society woman, such as Yin XueYan; A low-level dancer, such as king tai pan]. \"Characters in the\" big \"people,\" and \"small\", from the Chinese mainland different ethnic or city (Shanghai, nanjing, sichuan, hunan, guilin, Beijing, etc.) and their disparity between the rich and the poor, different industry, but no one does not carry a heavy and chop of the past. And the \"past\", the \"memory\", and more or less of the republic of China was set up to the mainland fell during the \"fraught times\", has a direct relationship. < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508607719', '激荡三十年（上）', 'images/激荡三十年（上）.jpg', '中信出版社浙江人民出版社', '历史', '26.25', '35', '<p>上卷记载1978-1992年间的企业变革。</p><p>《激荡三十年》的作者没有用传统的教科书或历史书的方式来写作这部作品，而是站在民间的角度，以真切而激扬的写作手法描绘了中国企业在改革开放年代走向市场、走向世界的成长、发展之路。改革开放初期汹涌的商品大潮；国营企业、民营企业、外资企业，这三种力量此消彼长、互相博弈的曲折发展；整个社会的躁动和不安……整部书稿中都体现得极为真切和实在。作者用激扬的文字再现出人们在历史创造中的激情、喜悦、呐喊、苦恼和悲愤。</p><p>尽管任何一段历史都有它不可替代的独特性，可是，1978年—2008年的中国，却是最不可能重复的。在一个拥有13亿人口的大国里，僵化的计划经济体制日渐瓦解了，一群小人物把中国变成了一个巨大的试验场，它在众目睽睽之下，以不可逆转的姿态向商业社会转轨。</p>', '< p > roll-up enterprise change records from 1978 to 1992. < / p > < p > author of agitate for 30 years, did not use the traditional textbooks or history book writing this book, but stand in the perspective of folk in the style of genuine and encouraging portrays the Chinese enterprise s reform and opening to the outside to the growth of the market, to the world, the road of development. The surge in the early years of the reform and opening up commercial tide; State-owned enterprises, private enterprises, foreign-funded enterprises, the three power eliminates and tortuous development game each other; The agitation of the whole society and upset... In the whole manuscript is very real and honest. The author with encouraging words shows the people in history to create passion, joy, scream, bitterness and grief. < / p > < p > although any period of history has its irreplaceable uniqueness, however, 1978-2008 of China, is the least likely to repeat. To build a country with a population of 1.3 billion, the rigidity of the planned economy system has collapsed, a group of people turned China into a huge range, it under the eyes of the public, with the attitude of irreversible transition to commercial society. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787208130500', '斯通纳', 'images/斯通纳.jpg', '上海人民出版社', '心理', '36.75', '49', '<p>《斯通纳》讲述了生命中最重要的部分：爱，认同，怜悯，志业，傲骨，信任与死亡。</p><p>一个勇者有过的失败不失意的人生：即使不能拥有完美的生活，所幸追求过完整的自我。</p><p>美国，密苏里州。来自偏远农场的农家子弟、19岁的威廉·斯通纳进入州立密苏里大学学习农学。自一堂选修文学课为起点，他的一生就此悄然改变。未来的斯通纳成为了一名大学老师，结婚、生子、教学、退休、衰老、死亡。在他生命的尽头，或许他可以坦然面对这个问题：你的一生，还要期望别的什么吗？</p><p>一部蕴含着真诚、激情与紧凑力量的小说，探究了历史洪流所忽视的人性之间的冲突、溃败与幸存，重新唤起思考每个个体独特存在的意义。作者约翰·威廉斯向世人展示了凡人中的勇者在如何生活。</p><p>----------------------------------------</p><p>威廉斯的写作显得澄澈、节制却准确。就像被打磨光滑的橡木上反射出本色、持久的光泽。它的行文结构潜藏得不为人察觉，且毫无瑕疵，像一栋房子，精妙绝伦到绝无仿制再建的可能。</p><p>《斯通纳》一书的伟大之处在于，它以不带一丝一毫悲喜的冷静洞察了生活本质的全部。它从本质上触及了预见期待的与真实体验的生活间的落差……《斯通纳》迟到五十年后畅销，是献给被亏欠的艺术一次迟来的正名。——《纽约客》</p><p>斯通纳活过，然后死去，如你我一样。他生活中发生的每一件事就发生在你我面前，看似平淡。然而，写出这种“简单”却需要天才才能完成。读这本书是一本令人难过却又美妙的阅读体验。——《星期日泰晤士报》</p><p>约翰·威廉斯的《斯通纳》刻画了一个将追求智识当作对抗无意义的战争、拒绝与外部世界作廉价妥协的人的一生。它的意义或许不只是一部伟大的小说——它简直是一部几近完美的小说，机构精巧，语言优美，故事动人，展示着一种夺人心魄的完美。——《纽约时报》</p><p>一件文学的珍宝。——《明镜周刊》</p><p>拥有超乎寻常的力量……直击生活的真相，语言清澈优美。它是一部献给所有热爱文学之人的传奇。——伊恩·麦克尤恩</p><p>一本精彩绝伦的小说，既丰富又忧郁，记录着伤痛与失去的同时也留存了美好温柔的时刻。这本小说完美展现了小说艺术的要素，它的叙事节奏与情节构架均堪称完美无缺。这本小说像一条河流，冷静而又流畅的平静笔调裹挟着磅礴延绵的力量。——亚当·福尔兹</p>', '< p > \"stone\", tells the story of the most important part of life: love, compassion, aspiration, pride, trust and death. < / p > < p > a brave before failure is not frustrated life: even if you can\'t have a perfect life, but the pursuit of a complete self. < / p > < p > the United States, Missouri. From a remote farm farmer families, 19, William stone into the state of Missouri university agronomy. A lesson since taking literature as the starting point, his life is changing. Stone in the future become a college teacher, get married, have children, teaching, retirement, aging and death. At the end of his life, maybe he can be calm in the face of this problem: your life, but also expect anything else? < / p > < p > a compact contains the sincerity, passion and strength of the novel, explores the historical flood ignored by the conflict between human nature and rout and survived, to arouse the thinking about the meaning of every individual is unique. The author John Williams to show the ordinary people of a brave man in how to live. < / p > < p > -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- < / p > < p > Williams\'s writing is splendidly, moderation is accurate. Like polished oak reflection on the nature and lasting luster. The prose structure underlying hidden, and flawless, like a house, no generic ring to build. < / p > < p >, author of stone\'s greatness lies in that it in without the slightest feeling of calm insight into the nature of life is all about. It touched the foresee expect from the essence and the gap between the real experience of life... \"Stone\", late fifty years later, is dedicated to be indebted to the art of a belated. - the New Yorker < / p > < p > stone, live, and die, like you and me. Happened in his life in everything that happens in your in front of me, seemingly insipid. Write the \"simple\", however, need to be a genius to complete. This book is a sad but beautiful reading experience. , the Sunday times < / p > < p > John Williams\' portrait of a \"stone\", will confront the pursuit of knowledge as a pointless war, refused to compromise with the outside world as a cheap one\'s life. The meaning of it may be not only a great novel, it is a nearly perfect novel, agency is exquisite, beautiful language, touching story, showing a seize the soul-stirring perfect. - the New York times < / p > < p > a literary treasures. - \"der spiegel\" < / p > < p > with extraordinary strength... Hitting the truth of life, clear and beautiful language. It is a tale of an to all love of literature. - Ian McEwan < / p > < p > a wonderful novel, both rich and melancholy, recording the pain and loss also retained a tender moment. Perfect show the elements of the art of novel in the novel, the narrative rhythm and the plot structure are in perfect shape. This novel is like a river, calm and smooth calm tone carrying sweep of the powerful force. - Adam foulds < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787305063749', '最初的爱情最后的仪式', 'images/最初的爱情最后的仪式.jpg', '南京大学出版社', '文学', '16.5', '22', '<p>全书由八个短篇组成，分别从八个位于童年、青春期和青年等不同阶段的男性视角出发，以意识和潜意识交接地带的经验为揭示对象，有时荒唐，有时伤感，有时温柔，有时骇人，有时魔幻，却都无限接近真实，接近每个人的内心。</p><p>麦克尤恩素来擅长以冷静细腻的笔触打磨幽暗题材，赋予其精妙无双的质感。八个故事各如黑晶棱镜之一面，折射出日常生活中平凡人性所可能误陷的种种魔怔与梦魇。平地与深渊，生与死，真实与玄幻，伦常与变态之间的界限恍若蛛丝般轻薄，看后令人或怅然或倒吸凉气，同时又觉得其魔力不可抗拒。</p><p>以如此短薄篇幅，麦克尤恩却惊才遽现，征服了文坛。所录每一篇都可谓杰作，令人过目难忘。此书是阅读和了解这位天才作家的最佳切入点。</p><p>《最初的爱情，最后的仪式》是麦克尤恩的处女作与成名作。</p>', '<p> as the 20th century Chinese novel, \"100\" Taipei people \", is a profound complexity of short stories, made up of fourteen first-rate short story, the series as a body, the effect of spurt, novels of wide wide, not only make us to see the \"mixed\" of society, more important, because one of theme meaning to repeat, with foil for each other, enable us to further understand the meaning of work, and enables us to see the hidden within the work of the author\'s outlook on life and world view. Taipei people, \"characters, can include social from all walks of Taipei city: from elderly forceful RuJiang PiaoGong (Liang Fu songs) to retire the maid shun sister-in-law (\" nostalgia fu\"), and from the upper-class DouFuRen (\" the peony pavilion \") to the underworld \"commander-in-chief\" (\" the solitary flower \"). Intellectuals, such as \"winter\" of Qin lei professor; A businessman, such as flower bridge RongJi, \"the wife of shop-owner; There are domestic workers, such as the blood red azalea, \"hung king; Have the people in the army, such as New Year\'s eve, \"Lai Mingsheng; A society woman, such as Yin XueYan; A low-level dancer, such as king tai pan]. \"Characters in the\" big \"people,\" and \"small\", from the Chinese mainland different ethnic or city (Shanghai, nanjing, sichuan, hunan, guilin, Beijing, etc.) and their disparity between the rich and the poor, different industry, but no one does not carry a heavy and chop of the past. And the \"past\", the \"memory\", and more or less of the republic of China was set up to the mainland fell during the \"fraught times\", has a direct relationship. </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787541142185', '一个叫欧维的男人决定去死', 'images/一个叫欧维的男人决定去死.jpg', '四川文艺出版社', '文学', '26.25', '35', '<p>来认识一下欧维，这个59岁的老头，脾气古怪，带着坚不可摧的原则、每天恪守的常规以及随时发飙的脾性在社区晃来晃去，被背地里称为“地狱来的恶邻”。他每天一大早就四处巡视，搬动没停进格线的脚踏车，检查垃圾是否按规定分类，抱怨谁家的草坪还不修剪，诅咒那只掉了毛的流浪猫。没完没了。</p><p>他想自杀。</p><p>直到一个十一月的早晨，当一对话痨夫妇和他们的两个话痨女儿搬到隔壁，不小心撞坏了他的邮筒……</p><p>“读这个故事，”《人物周刊》说，“你会笑，你会哭，会因此想搬到北欧去，因为那里的一切都更可爱一些。”这个发生在瑞典的故事，如生命庆典般绚丽斑斓，它让我们思考，自己是谁，以及我们要如何过这一生。</p><p>有的人称它是《一个的朝圣》瑞典版，读者评价它“令人愉悦又心碎”“搞笑之余让你感动且哭得稀里哗啦”“读到一本好小说的感觉真好”！</p><p>它已被拍成电影（传送门：https://movie.douban.com/subject/26628357/），这里有一个愤怒的恪守常规的普通邻家老头，一对话痨夫妇和话痨女儿、这里有一只掉了毛的乱蓬蓬的倒霉猫，这是一场人与人之间的迷人相遇。</p>', '<p> roll-up enterprise change records from 1978 to 1992. </p> <p> author of agitate for 30 years, did not use the traditional textbooks or history book writing this book, but stand in the perspective of folk in the style of genuine and encouraging portrays the Chinese enterprise s reform and opening to the outside to the growth of the market, to the world, the road of development. The surge in the early years of the reform and opening up commercial tide; State-owned enterprises, private enterprises, foreign-funded enterprises, the three power eliminates and tortuous development game each other; The agitation of the whole society and upset... In the whole manuscript is very real and honest. The author with encouraging words shows the people in history to create passion, joy, scream, bitterness and grief. </p> <p> although any period of history has its irreplaceable uniqueness, however, 1978-2008 of China, is the least likely to repeat. To build a country with a population of 1.3 billion, the rigidity of the planned economy system has collapsed, a group of people turned China into a huge range, it under the eyes of the public, with the attitude of irreversible transition to commercial society. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787806767245', '野火集', 'images/野火集.jpg', '文汇出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>龙应台常常针对一种社会现象，一类具体事物，甚至于一个人、一句话、一件事，给予无情的透视和直接的批评，马上让人心有戚戚焉。这些事，就发生在周围，看得见，摸得着，那么具体、实在、确切；而内中的缘由、涵义、影响、作用，常人似乎无所感，一经点破；立时豁然开朗。</p><p>此次重新编整后推出的《野火集》，除了保留作者当年的“野火”文字，附加了作者对此文的感言，或对当时时代背景的补充说明，或观照了对文章产生的现实意义。并邀请二十位华语文学名人如柏杨、余秋雨等，为文或追忆或评析走过“野火时代”的台湾。</p>', '< p > lung ying-tai often aimed at a kind of social phenomenon, a kind of specific things, even a person, a word, a thing, to give ruthless perspective and direct criticism, let the heart have creates immediately. These things happened in the surrounding, see, touch it, so specific, really, exactly; In the cause, meaning, influence and role, ordinary people seems to be no feeling, once discover; Immediately be suddenly enlightened. < / p > < p > the rewrite the whole after the launch of the \"wild fire\", in addition to retain the author of \"fires\" words, the addition of the authors of this article of speech, or added to the era background, or a witness to generate the realistic significance of the article. And invited 20 Chinese literary celebrities such as Mr Bo, yu qiuyu, for text or recall or evaluation through Taiwan \"wildfire era\". < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787801876942', '九州·缥缈录', 'images/九州·缥缈录.jpg', '新世界出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>当这个世界都要崩溃；当星辰和阳光也熄灭，当马蹄踏过弱者的尸骨，当黑暗的血色吞噬人心，不死的鹰再次降落在草原，英雄还在哭泣，在铁铸的摇篮中成长……《九州·缥缈录》的故事就发生在这里，游牧部落内部的权力争夺激烈，青阳与东陆王朝间恩怨重重。这是乱世的英雄史诗，当古老的王朝日渐衰微，掌管着星辰命运的神秘宗教走入了政治斗争的漩涡，年轻的王朝继承者崭露出耀眼的锋芒。</p>', '< p > when the world will collapse; When the stars and the sun is out, when the hoofs through the bones of the weak, when blood to gobble up the heart of darkness, undead eagle landing on the grasslands, again hero also crying, grow in the cradle of cast iron... Story took place in the kyushu, dimly discernible record here, nomadic tribes internal power struggle is intense, qingyang and feud between east dynasty lu. This is gone with the epic hero, when the ancient dynasty declining, presides over the fate of the mysterious religious stars into the swirl of political struggle, young inheritors dynasty come with dazzling. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532733323', '生活在别处', 'images/生活在别处.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>《生活在别处》是一个年轻艺术家的肖像画。昆德拉以其独到的笔触塑造出雅罗米尔这样一个形象，描绘了这个年轻诗人充满激情而又短暂的一生，具有“发展小说”的许多特点。就其题材而言，表现一个艺术家（或知识分子）是本世纪文学的一个重要领域，因为展示我们这个复杂的时代也只有复杂的人物才能承担。在这部作品中，作者对诗人创作过程的分析是微妙而精细的。创作过程当然不仅指下笔写作的过程，而且更广义地指一个诗人的全部成长过程。用作者自己的话说，这部小说是“对我所称之为抒情态度的一个分析。”正是在这样的创作意图下，这部书最初曾被题名为《抒情时代》。作者所要表现和所要探究的是，人的心灵所具有的激情，它的产生和它的结果。因而这本书又是一本现代心理小说，表现了一个诗人的艺术感觉的成长。书中每一章节的名称都展示了诗人生命历程的一个阶段。他的童年、少年和青年时代，他怎样读书，怎样恋爱，以及怎样做梦等等。关于时代的全貌和他人的活动都迟到了远处，一切观察的焦点都集中在主人公身上，并且与他的内心活动有关。有如激情的涧水，在时间的乱山碎石中流过，两岸的景致并不重要，重要的是溪流将流向沃野还是沙漠。换句话说，作者在这里所关心的是诗人心理和精神上的发育。为了潜入到人物意识中最隐秘的角落，作者采用了一种我们可以称之为客观意识流的叙述方式：时间与空间交织（不同时期不同地点所发生的事常常出现在同一段叙述中），现实与梦幻交织（第二章《泽维尔》完全是一个梦套一个梦），情节的跳宏，思考的猝然与不连贯，故意模糊主语的陈述，这些都使此书更接近于诗歌而不是小说。假如我们把书中这些抒情性的因素去掉，这部作品的内容就剩不下什么了。这种形式使我们更能切近诗人的内心活动，感触到诗人的激情是怎样产生和燃烧的。</p>', '< p > \"life is elsewhere\" is a young artist\'s portrait. Mr Kundera, with its unique writing style out of the club, so an image, describes the young poet is full of passion and short life, has many characteristics of \"the development of novel\". Performance in terms of its subject matter, an artist (or intellectuals) is an important area of the century literature, for showing us the complicated era also can only bear complex characters. In this work, the authors analysis the process of poets are subtle and delicate. The creative process, of course, not only refers to the process of writing, writing and more broadly refers to all the growth of a poet. In the words of the author himself, the novel is \"an analysis of what I call emotional attitude.\" It is in this creation intention, the book initially was named \"lyric era\". The author to performance and to explore is that a person\'s heart has passion, and its production and its results. Thus this book is a modern psychological novel, shows a growth of the poet\'s artistic feeling. The name of each chapter in the book are shows a stage of the poet\'s life experience. His childhood, juvenile and youth, how to read, how to love, and how to have a dream, and so on. About the outline of the era and the activities of others are late in the distance, the focus of all observations were focused on the character, and is associated with his inner activities. Like a passion of countless water, flows around the time of mountain rock, on both sides of the scenery is not important, important is streams will flow to you or desert. In other words, the authors are concerned with here is a poet when he is mental and spiritual development. To infiltrate into the consciousness of characters in the corner of the most secretive, the author adopted a we can call objective stream-of-consciousness narrative: time and space (what happened at different sites at different periods are often appear in the same period of narrative), reality and dream weaving (chapter 2 \"Xavier\" completely is a dream a dream), jump to the plot macros, thinking and incoherent, unexpectedly intentionally vague subject statement, these all make the book more akin to poetry rather than novels. If we put these lyricism factors removed in the book, the content of the work won\'t leave us anything. This form can make us more close the poet\'s heart activity, feeling to the poet\'s passion is how to generate and burning. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787209041065', '设计中的设计', 'images/设计中的设计.jpg', '山东人民出版社', '设计', '36', '48', '<p>设计到底是什么？作为一名从业二十余年并且具有世界影响的设计师，原研哉对自己提出了这样一个问题。为了给出自己的答案，他走了那么长的路，做了那么多的探索。“RE-DESIGN——二十一世纪的日常用品再设计”展真是一个有趣的展览，但又不仅仅是有趣，它分明是为我们揭示了“日常生活”所具有的无限可能性。若我们能以满怀新鲜的眼神去观照日常，“设计”的意义定会超越技术的层面，为我们的生活观和人生观注入力量。</p>', '< p > what design? As an industry more than 20 years and has the world influence designers, the original zai put forward such a question to myself. In order to give his answer, he walked so long way, done so many exploration. \"RE - DESIGN - the 21st century daily necessities DESIGN\" is really an interesting exhibition at the show, but it is not only fun, it is clear for us to reveal the \"daily life\" has infinite possibilities. If we can get filled with fresh eyes to meditate daily, the meaning of \"design\" will go beyond the level of technology, outlook and outlook on life into power for us. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787542621344', '心是孤独的猎手', 'images/心是孤独的猎手.jpg', '上海三联书店', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>《心是孤独的猎手》作者麦卡勒斯的第一部长篇小说，也是她一举成名的作品和最具震撼力的代表作，居“现代文库20世纪百佳英文小说”第17位，曾被评为百部最佳同性恋小说之一。</p><p>故事的背景类似于《伤心咖啡馆之歌》中炎热的南方小镇。小说中两个聋哑男子的同性之爱令人感动，而同性之恋又是若有若无的，时而激烈，时而沉默。主旨凸显的是麦卡勒斯式的主题：孤独是绝对的，最深切的爱也无法改变人类最终极的孤独。绝望的孤独与其说是原罪，不如说是原罪的原罪。</p>', '<p> when the world will collapse; When the stars and the sun is out, when the hoofs through the bones of the weak, when blood to gobble up the heart of darkness, undead eagle landing on the grasslands, again hero also crying, grow in the cradle of cast iron... Story took place in the kyushu, dimly discernible record here, nomadic tribes internal power struggle is intense, qingyang and feud between east dynasty lu. This is gone with the epic hero, when the ancient dynasty declining, presides over the fate of the mysterious religious stars into the swirl of political struggle, young inheritors dynasty come with dazzling. </p>', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787505417670', '琅琊榜', 'images/琅琊榜.jpg', '朝华出版社', '文学', '37.35', '49.8', '<p>一卷风去琅琊榜，囊尽天下奇英才。他远在江湖，却能名动帝辇，只因神秘莫测而又言出必准的琅琊阁，突然断言他是一麒麟之才，得之可得天下一。然而，身为太子与誉王竞相拉拢招揽的对象，他竟然出人意料地舍弃了这两个皇位争夺的热门人选，转而投向默默无闻、最不受皇帝宠爱的靖王。</p><p>这是想挑战自己的麒麟之才？还是其中内有隐情？那雪夜薄甲、逐敌千里的少年将军，和病骨支离、年寿难永的阴沉谋士，究竟哪一个是他最真实的一面？宫廷内外，无数的谜团交织在刀光血影中，尔虞我诈中带出一段段离奇的故事。太子、誉王与靖王，互相的势力此消彼长，精彩绝伦的权术争斗你来我往。大江南北，各路精英纷纷登场，有背负双重身份的贵公子，有统帅南境铁骑的美丽郡主，有手握禁军的国中第二高手，有身陷家仇国恨的烟花女子，有性格乖戾的影子高手，有默默隐忍的朝中要臣……权谋、仇恨、感情……互相交织，层层发展，逐渐撕开事实的真相。然而，一切真相大白后，故事却又朝着不可思议的方向继续发展……</p>', '< p > a devil to reed {langya}, sac talent to the best of the world. He in river\'s lake, but can move emperor chariot, yet mysterious and say out the will of reed {langya} cabinet, suddenly to assert that he is a kirin, one of the available under heaven. However, as the prince and the king of reputation vied to solicit the object, he unexpectedly unexpectedly abandoned both the throne for the front-runner, defected to the unknown, most beloved emperor jing wang. < / p > < p > this is the kirin want to challenge yourself only? Or which contains the catch? The hakodate BoJia young general of one by one, thousands of miles, and disease bone mangled, hard to his gloomy, but deathless my renown which is his most true side? Inside and outside the court, countless mysteries intertwined in a bloody, graft brings out the series of extraordinary story. Prince, king of reputation and jing wang, influence each other, wonderful politics fight to you. Great river north and south, various elite, have bear the childe of double identity, commander in chief south boundary fighters, beautiful country, and the hand imperial kingdom in the second, there are fireworks in the midst of a family business countries hate woman, have soured the shadow of the player character, have toward the silently swallowed to I... The tactics, hate, affection... Interweave each other, layer upon layer development, gradually to tear apart the truth of the matter. After all the truth, however, the story is to continue to develop in the direction of the incredible... < / p >', '8.5');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787208062153', '乡土中国', 'images/乡土中国.jpg', '上海人民出版社', '社会', '28.5', '38', '<p>著名社会学家费孝通教授，一生行行重行行，实地调查和考察总结中国农村经济发展的各种模式，写下了诸多不朽篇章。本书推出的是学界共认的中国乡土社会传统文化和社会结构理论研究的代表作《乡土中国》、《生育制度》、《乡土重建》和《皇权与绅权》四篇著作，可供社会学工作或教学、研究者参考。</p>', '< p > famous sociologist fei xiaotong, a professor at the life line do the heavy line, field survey and investigation summarizes China\'s rural economic development patterns, wrote many immortal chapter. Book introduced the consensus of the academic community of rural society of China traditional culture and social structure theory to study the representative work of \"rural China\" and \"system\", \"the rural reconstruction\" and the imperial power and the right of gentlemen and four works, can be used for reference in the sociology work or teaching, researchers. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787802255036', '占星术杀人魔法', 'images/占星术杀人魔法.jpg', '新星出版社', '魔幻', '21', '28', '<p>四十年前，一桩占星术连续杀人案件轰动全日本！先是画家梅泽平吉在密室被人重击致死，接着是他早已出嫁的长女在家中被奸杀，最后甚至连与他同住的六个女儿也全部失踪。尸体陆续被发现埋在日本各地，而每个人身上都被切掉一部分！</p><p>梅泽平吉遗留的手记上写明他要依据“占星术”肢解重组六个女儿！难道他死而复活来完成幻异的艺术创作？当又没有证据与动机指向其他与本案相关的人——这可说是一桩找不到凶手的命案……</p><p>四十年后，眼见这桩诡谲至极的凶案变成邪灵的诅咒，本职占星师兼职侦探的御手洗洁却意外的得到一封告白遗书！悬宕四十年无解的奇案终于现出一线曙光，御手洗洁决定在一星期内破解这件史上最不可思议、超大规模的占星术杀人魔法！</p>', '< p > 40 years ago, a pile of astrology and continuous murder sensation across Japan! First painter MeiZePing auspicious in the chamber of secrets was hit to death, then he has married the eldest daughter was raped and murdered in the home, finally even with his six daughters are all missing. Body was found buried in the continue throughout Japan, and every man a part was cut off! < / p > < p > MeiZePing ji legacy\'s note on what he should be based on \"astrology\" dismember restructuring six daughters! Does his death and resurrection to complete phantom vision art? When there is no evidence and motives to other people associated with the case - this is a can not find the murderer kills... < / p > < p > after forty years, seeing the whole complex of crime into the curse of the evil spirits, the labor of astrologers part-time detective equestrian detergent was surprised to get a confession letter! Hang down forty years unsolved mystery finally reveal a gleam of dawn, equestrian detergent decided to crack this within a week in the history of the most incredible, vlsi astrology\'s magic to kill! < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787563383870', '我执', 'images/我执.jpg', '广西师范大学出版社', '文学', '26.25', '35', '<p>本书为梁文道先生所撰写的散文随笔集，是以香港《成报》文采版专栏“秘学笔记”的文字为主，谈及爱情婚姻、日常生活、疾病经历、信仰感悟、城市文化、文学艺术、历史记忆等个人生活体验和人生感受诸多方面。读来清新自然，体贴入微，在淡雅简约的叙述中往往给人意外的启迪。</p>', '<p> a devil to reed {langya}, sac talent to the best of the world. He in river\'s lake, but can move emperor chariot, yet mysterious and say out the will of reed {langya} cabinet, suddenly to assert that he is a kirin, one of the available under heaven. However, as the prince and the king of reputation vied to solicit the object, he unexpectedly unexpectedly abandoned both the throne for the front-runner, defected to the unknown, most beloved emperor jing wang. </p> <p> this is the kirin want to challenge yourself only? Or which contains the catch? The hakodate BoJia young general of one by one, thousands of miles, and disease bone mangled, hard to his gloomy, but deathless my renown which is his most true side? Inside and outside the court, countless mysteries intertwined in a bloody, graft brings out the series of extraordinary story. Prince, king of reputation and jing wang, influence each other, wonderful politics fight to you. Great river north and south, various elite, have bear the childe of double identity, commander in chief south boundary fighters, beautiful country, and the hand imperial kingdom in the second, there are fireworks in the midst of a family business countries hate woman, have soured the shadow of the player character, have toward the silently swallowed to I... The tactics, hate, affection... Interweave each other, layer upon layer development, gradually to tear apart the truth of the matter. After all the truth, however, the story is to continue to develop in the direction of the incredible... </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787540541903', '子不语1', 'images/子不语1.jpg', '新世纪出版社', '漫画', '27', '36', '<p>实力派人气漫画家夏达第五届金龙奖最佳少女漫画优胜作品！收录《子不语》第1回至第8回的完整剧情，并收录一则番外篇《虎》。0</p><p>《子不语》讲述了9岁的小语跟随父母搬家到古老的小镇麟趾镇，善良而又天真的她用心去探索着身边那些神奇的事物，而它们又给小语带来小小的大自然的启迪的故事。</p><p>全书除了收录了《子不语》漫画外，更有姚非拉＋风息神泪倾力作序，此外还有更多新鲜插画，以及每一回《子不语》背后的故事都由夏达亲笔一一道来，最后还有传说中的麟趾镇，现实中夏达父母曾经工作过的古老小镇的照片等你来细细分享，绝对好看又精彩哦！</p><p>《子不语》壹-贰册除了夺人眼球的众多漫画内容外，更随书附赠精美素描本＋AB两套每套两款书签，绝对是粉丝们的珍藏首选！</p><p>目录</p><p>《子不语1》目录：</p><p>序</p><p>第一回茧</p><p>第二回木芙蓉</p><p>第三回影</p><p>第四回老木匠</p><p>番外篇虎</p><p>《子不语2》目录：</p><p>序</p><p>第五回狐嫁</p><p>第六回中秋</p><p>第七回候鸟</p><p>第八回白蛇</p>', '<p> famous sociologist fei xiaotong, a professor at the life line do the heavy line, field survey and investigation summarizes China\'s rural economic development patterns, wrote many immortal chapter. Book introduced the consensus of the academic community of rural society of China traditional culture and social structure theory to study the representative work of \"rural China\" and \"system\", \"the rural reconstruction\" and the imperial power and the right of gentlemen and four works, can be used for reference in the sociology work or teaching, researchers. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532739233', '枪炮、病菌与钢铁', 'images/枪炮、病菌与钢铁.jpg', '上海世纪出版集团', '社会', '33.75', '45', '<p>为什么是欧亚大陆人征服、赶走或大批杀死印第安人、澳大利亚人和非洲人，而不是相反？为什么么小麦和玉米、牛和猪以及现代世界的其他一些“不了起的”作物和牲畜出现在这些特定地区，而不是其他地区？在这部开创性的著作中，演化生物学家贾雷德.戴蒙德揭示了事实上有助于形成历史最广泛模式的环境因素，从而以震撼人心的力量摧毁了以种族主义为基础的人类史理论，因其突出价值和重要性，本书荣获1998年美国普利策奖和英国科普书奖，并为《纽约时报》畅销书排行榜作品。</p><p>本书是理解人类社会发展史方面的一个重大进展，它记录了现代世界及其诸多不平等所以形成的原因，也是一部真正关于全世界各民族的历史，是对人类生活的完整一贯的叙述，娓娓道来，具有很强的可读性。</p>', '< p > why is the conquest of Eurasia, drive, or a large number of killing off the indians, Australia and Africa, not the other way round? Why yao wheat and corn, cattle and pigs, and the other of the modern world \"not the\" crop and livestock in these specific areas, rather than the other parts? In this groundbreaking book, evolutionary biologists Mr Reid. Diamond history reveals the fact helps to form the most extensive model of environmental factors, thus destroyed by force of stunning racism based theory of human history, because of its outstanding value and importance of this book was awarded the Pulitzer prize in 1998 and the UK science book award, and works for the New York times bestseller list. < / p > < p > this book is to understand the history of human society in terms of a significant progress, it records the reason for the formation of the modern world and its many inequality so that is a true, about the history of all nationalities in the world is full of human life consistent narrative, talk, have very strong readability. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536025097', '白银时代', 'images/白银时代.jpg', '花城出版社', '文学', '7.5', '10', '<p>《白银时代》是《时代三部曲》之二。这是由一组虚拟时空的作品构成的长篇。这组作品写的是本世纪长大而活到下世纪的知识分子，在跨世纪的生存过程中，回忆他们的上辈、描述他们的上辈、描述他们自己的人生。与其说这是对未来世界的预测，不如说是现代生活的寓言。</p>', '< p > \"the silver age\" is the second time trilogy \". It is composed of a set of virtual space and time work long. This piece, is written in this century grew up and lived to the next century intellectuals, in the process of cross century survival, memories of their generation, describe their generation and describe their own life. This is not so much the predictions for the future of the world, as the parable of modern life. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787539921624', '红拂夜奔', 'images/红拂夜奔.jpg', '江苏文艺出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>《红拂夜奔》这书题就会让读者认为是写隋末杨素家妓红拂敬慕大军事家李靖，私奔相从的风流逸事。然而，这本书它以现代人的眼光去观照历史，又以历史文化原型来建构现代小说的结构。历史的重建和复归在于人类有共同的心理品质、共同的生存状态和共同的生存困境。王小波在序言中说：“我写的是内心而不是外形，是神似而不是形似。”人类自身的进化是在不断循环、重演的历史中进行的，唯有如此，那些世代相传的古典名著才能震撼现代读者的心灵，引起共鸣；那些借鉴历史原型的现代作品才能激发读者真正的兴趣。王小波写的就是这样一部把历史和现实进行双向建构的小说。</p>', '< p > \"red stroke night rush\" the title of the book will make readers to think is to write sui end Yang Sujia prostitutes red stroke admire big strategist oxidase, elopement from affair. However, this book it with modern people to witness history, and historical and cultural prototype to construct the structure of the modern novel. The reconstruction of the history and the return is that humans have a common psychological quality, common survival state and the common survival plight. Wang said in the preface: \"I write is not appearance, inner is may not like.\" Human evolution is in cycle, the repeat of the history, the only way, those who pass on from generation to generation classic to shake the soul of modern readers resonate; Those who draw lessons from history prototype of the modern literature can inspire readers genuine interest. Written by wang is such a two-way construct the history and the reality of the novel. < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787544238212', '偷书贼', 'images/偷书贼.jpg', '南海出版公司', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>1939年的德国，9岁的小女孩莉赛尔和弟弟被迫送往慕尼黑远郊的寄养家庭。6岁的弟弟不幸死在了路途中。在冷清的葬礼后，莉赛尔意外得到她的第一本书《掘墓人手册》。</p><p>这将是14本给她带来无限安慰的书之一。她是个孤苦的孩子，父亲被打上了共产主义者的烙印，被纳粹带走了；母亲随后也失踪了。在弹奏手风琴的养父的帮助下，她学会了阅读。尽管生活艰苦，她却发现了一个比食物更难以抗拒的东西——书。她忍不住开始偷书。莉赛尔，这个被死神称为“偷书贼”的可怜女孩，在战乱的德国努力地生存着，并不可思议地帮助了周围同样承受苦难的人。</p><p>这是个讲述书是如何振奋灵魂的令人难忘的故事。</p>', '<p> why is the conquest of Eurasia, drive, or a large number of killing off the indians, Australia and Africa, not the other way round? Why yao wheat and corn, cattle and pigs, and the other of the modern world \"not the\" crop and livestock in these specific areas, rather than the other parts? In this groundbreaking book, evolutionary biologists Mr Reid. Diamond history reveals the fact helps to form the most extensive model of environmental factors, thus destroyed by force of stunning racism based theory of human history, because of its outstanding value and importance of this book was awarded the Pulitzer prize in 1998 and the UK science book award, and works for the New York times bestseller list. </p> <p> this book is to understand the history of human society in terms of a significant progress, it records the reason for the formation of the modern world and its many inequality so that is a true, about the history of all nationalities in the world is full of human life consistent narrative, talk, have very strong readability. </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532745159', '爱的艺术', 'images/爱的艺术.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '心理', '11.25', '15', '<p>《爱的艺术》是德裔美籍心理学家和哲学家、法兰克福学派重要成员艾里希-弗洛姆最著名的作品，自1956年出版至今已被翻译成32种文字，在全世界畅销不衰，被誉为当代爱的艺术理论专著最著名的作品。</p><p>在这本书中，弗洛姆认为，爱情不是一种与人的成熟程度无关，只需要投入身心的感情。如果不努力发展自己的全部人格并以此达到一种创造倾向性，那么每种爱的试图都会失败，如果没有爱他人的能力，如果不能真正谦恭地、勇敢地、真诚地和有纪律地爱他人，那么人们在自己的爱情生活中也永远得不到满足。</p><p>弗洛姆进而提出，爱是一门艺术，要求想要掌握这门艺术的人有这方面的知识并付出努力。在这里，爱不仅仅是狭隘的男女爱情，也并非通过磨练增进技巧即可获得。爱是人格整体的展现，要发展爱的能力，就需要努力发展自己的人格，并朝着有益的目标迈进。</p><p>此版特别收录弗洛姆学术助手纪念文章《弗洛姆生命中的爱》。</p>', '< p > \"the art of love\" is a German American psychologist and philosopher, important member of Frankfurt school, airy - fromm\'s most famous work, since 1956 has been translated into 32 languages, remains popular all over the world, has been hailed as a contemporary art theory monographs and one of the most famous works of love. < / p > < p > in this book, fromm\'s thought, love is not a kind of has nothing to do with the degree of maturity to which a person, only need to put in physical and psychological feelings. If not all efforts to develop his own personality and to achieve a kind of creation tendency, so each love trying to will fail, if you don\'t have the ability to love others, if you can\'t really humbly, brave, sincere and disciplined to love others, then people in your love life is always not satisfied. < / p > < p > fromm put forward that love is an art that requires those who want to master this art has the knowledge and the effort. Here, love is not just a narrow love, men and women are not hone in skills improvement can be achieved. Love is an expression of personality as a whole, to develop the ability of love, you need to try to develop their own personality, and to work toward the aim of the good. < / p > < p > this topic special commemorative articles included academic assistant frome the fromm\'s love in the life. < / p >', '8.8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787532728893', '舞！舞！舞！', 'images/舞！舞！舞！.jpg', '上海译文出版社', '文学', '18.75', '25', '<p>六具白骨摆列在一间亦真亦幻的死亡之屋里。“我”的老朋友“鼠”已经死于寻羊冒险。“我”好不容易找到了投缘的老同学五反田，可这位被演艺界包装得精神分裂的电影明星，却接连勒死了两名高级应召女郎，自己也驾着高级跑车“玛莎拉蒂”葬身大海。孤独的女孩“雪”和她孤傲的母亲“雨”，虽然还能在这疯狂世界上勉强生存，可“雨”的守护神笛克，却也躲不过一场莫名的车祸。度过了一段死亡陪伴的惊魂日子，“我”终于在宾馆女服务员由美吉那里找到了安全感，也有了在安静城市过安静生活的具体计划。可是，那第六具白骨到底意味着谁呢？“我”依然脱不出死亡之屋。</p><p>“高度发达的资本主义社会，”村上春树把这句话重复了不知多少遍，他是想寻找所有这些死亡和罪恶的源头吧？</p>', '< p > six other bones on the table in a room with the real or imagined the house of death. \"My\" old friend \"rat\" has died of sheep adventure. \"I\" to find the right chemistry field, old classmate three antis can be acting of schizophrenia packed the movie star, but have strangled two senior call girl, oneself also driving the senior sports car \"maserati\" died in the sea. Lonely girl \"snow\" and \"rain\" the mother of her aloof, although also can barely survive in this crazy world, but the patron saint of \"rain\" flute, but also hide but a strange car accident. Had a death with fright day, \"I\" finally in the hotel waitress with beauty there found a sense of security, have a quiet life in quiet city concrete plans. But, with the sixth bones who really mean? \"I\" is still not out of the house of death. < / p > < p > \"highly developed capitalist society,\" he repeated this sentence I don\'t know how many times, he is looking for the source of all this death and evil? < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787106020750', '动物凶猛', 'images/动物凶猛.jpg', '中国电影出版社', '文学', '11.625', '15.5', '<p>他们逃课、泡妞、打群架，他们由于“不必学习那些后来注定要忘掉的无用的知识”而使自身的动物本能获得了空前的解放；他们深知自己的未来已被框定于固定的范畴之内，所以他们一点也不担心自己的前程。“一切都无须争取，我只要等待，十八岁时自然会轮到我。”因此他们在现实生活中就只剩下随处发泄的精力、四处寻找刺激的欲望、自以为是的狂傲、随波逐流漂泊不定的心灵。在“我”的世界里，高氏兄弟是山大王、汪若海是贰臣、于北蓓是狐狸精、米兰是交际花；在“我”的心中，家长令人厌恶、学校无聊乏味，而用钥匙入室窥私或顺手拿走不超过十元钱以上的物品，是一种兴趣爱好。也有发自内心的对异性的迷恋，但这种浪漫的感情最终还是被无法控制的兽欲所吞噬。</p>', '< p > they skip class, pick up hot chicks and cluster, because they \"don\'t learn later destined to forget those useless knowledge\" and make their own animal instinct gained unprecedented liberation; They know that their future is framed within a category of fixed, so they don\'t worry about his future. \"Everything don\'t have to fight for, I just wait, naturally it was my turn at the age of 18.\" So they are commonly found in real life leaves out of energy, looking for stimulation of desire, self-righteous, haughty, drift with the current precarious state of mind. In the world of \"I\", the king\'s brother is a high mountain, ruo-hai wang is ErChen, in north page is fox, milan is a social butterfly; In the heart of the \"I\", parents are disgusting, the school boring, and with a key to enter into the private or conveniently take not more than ten yuan, is a kind of hobby. Also have a genuine love of the opposite sex, but this kind of romantic feelings eventually devoured by uncontrollable animal desire. < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787503945434', '佛祖在一号线', 'images/佛祖在一号线.jpg', '文化艺术出版社', '社会', '18.75', '25', '<p>千呼万唤的李海鹏首部专栏集，中国当下最好的专栏作家之一。</p><p>本书是著名新闻人和评论人李海鹏在《第一财经周刊》、《南方周末》和《智族GQ》上的专栏集结。涉及社会、经济、文化、生活的时评和杂文。语言睿智幽默、见解险直犀利，让民众听到一种最清醒有力的声音。</p><p>李海鹏的身份并不是作为《南方周末》的高级记者记，或者《第一财经周刊》的专栏名家，或者《GQ》的专题总监而被大家记住的，他被人尊敬和认识，是因为他近乎天真的对自由的执着，对伟大社会成形的关注及焦心。抽丝剥茧的分析，吹毛断发的文字，掷地成声的观点，恣肆放达的叙述，这些都注满了李海鹏的所有文章，其间到处安放着才情、思想、和对自由美好世界的向往，以至于除此之外，他几乎一无所有了。</p><p>图书品牌：磨铁——文治图书</p><p>请海鹏写专栏是《第一财经周刊》做的最好的决定之一。很多时候我们怯于表达，海鹏有勇气；很多时候我们的表达不够准确，海鹏对语言和逻辑的把握让他的文字充满力量；最关键的是，海鹏的优雅和从容，于是有了我们这个时代最值得阅读的文字。</p><p>——伊险峰《第一财经周刊》执行总编</p><p>海鹏把第一篇专栏《台风》给我时，不确定地说“不知道是不是GQ要的”。至今我都很感谢他，那篇专栏是我第一次看到他回望内心的写作，感受到他“手指触及真理核心时的极度快感”，那声音好古怪。我想，这些细碎、微妙、不经意又很本质的描述，才是生命最原本的光辉啊。</p><p>——王锋《智族GQ》编辑总监</p><p>在世界到处是光的今天，我们缺少另一种光。李海鹏的书像一颗小钻石，清醒、隐蔽，光芒四射。</p><p>——马莉诗人、画家、《南方周末》高级编辑</p><p>无论作为记者还是专栏作家，李海鹏都长于发现无所不在的荒诞，但他文字的底色是悲悯，悲民生之多艰，悲世人昏庸而不自知。因此他刻薄、幽默、不羁却温热。汉语被他如此高妙自如地运用，像一个狡黠而骄傲的小男孩把玩他心爱的弹弓。</p><p>——杨瑞春《中国新闻周刊》执行主编</p>', '< p > the long-awaited li first column sets, one of China\'s best current columnist. < / p > < p > this book is a famous news and comment on li in the China Business Weekly magazine, \"south weekend\", and concentrating column of the journal of GQ intellectual family. Involving social, economy, culture, life of editorial and essays. Language humor, insight straight sharp intelligence, let people hear one of the most powerful voice wake. < / p > < p > li\'s identity is not as southern weekend, a senior reporter, or famous, the first financial weekly column or GQ project director and be remembered, he was respected and understanding, because he was almost innocent of the freedom of perseverance, of great social attention and alarming. The analysis of the whole, blow hair to send word, throw into acoustic point of view, arrogant with narrative, these are filled with all the posts that li, which sits around talents, ideas, and the yearning for freedom and beautiful world, that in addition to that, he almost nothing. < / p > < p > book brand: grinding iron -- sandwiches books < / p > < p > the sea peng, please write a column is the first financial weekly to do one of the best decisions. Many times we afraid to express, the sea peng has courage; The expression of many times we not accurate enough, the sea peng mastery of language and logic to let his words is full of power; Crucially, elegant and calm sea peng, hence the most worthy of our time reading the text. < / p > < p > - the perilous peak managing editor of the China Business Weekly magazine < / p > < p > the sea peng give me the first column \"typhoon\", not sure to say \"I don\'t know whether GQ\". Today I am very grateful to him, that column is the first time I saw him back at the heart of writing, his \"fingers touch the core truth of extreme pleasure\", that sounds good. I want to, the finely, and it\'s a description of the nature, subtle, casual life is the most original glory. < / p > < p > - Wang Feng \"wise family magazine editor director < / p > < p > in today\'s world is full of light, we need another light. Li book is like a small diamond, sober, concealment, radiant. < / p > < p > -- -- Mary poets, painters, southern weekend, a senior editor < / p > < p > as a journalist and columnist, longer than li found the ubiquitous absurdity, but the impression of his text is grief, sadness of hard livelihood, sad the fatuous and don\'t even know it. So he mean was warm, humorous, unruly. Chinese is he so safe use freely, like a cunning and proud of the little boy playing with his beloved slingshot. < / p > < p > - rui-chun Yang executive editor of the China news weekly magazine < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9789571350813', '告白', 'images/告白.jpg', '時報文化', '悬疑', '187.5', '250', '<p>日本銷售破67萬冊</p><p>獲獎記錄</p><p>★2009年本屋大賞第1名</p><p>★第29回小說推理新人獎</p><p>★週刊文春「2008年MysteryBest10」第1名</p><p>★寶島社「2009年這本推理小說真厲害！」第4名</p><p>當倫理和正義分歧，你該選哪邊？</p><p>殺人者的與復仇者的心理演進，輪番敲擊著我們內心的道德尺度</p><p>一位中學女老師在校園游泳池內發現自己的四歲女兒意外溺斃，後來經她私下調查，原來是班上兩位學生謀殺的，但殺人動機實在荒唐。痛失愛女的老師辭職，不向警方申請重新調查，而在結業式那天向全班學生告白真相，並透露了她的復仇計畫，在學生們的心底種下恐懼的因子……</p><p>作者利用《罪與罰》的反推理手法來心理分析新世代教育和校園犯罪，各篇章由受害者親人、嫌疑犯學生、嫌犯的家人及女同學等主觀視角分別告白，一步步逼近犯罪動機的核心，藉此也提出許多重要問題，像是師生親子關係如何有效溝通、校園犯罪的法律面和道德面的懲罰該如何拿捏、如何與疑似有問題的學生相處來預防犯罪、如何落實個別化人格教育、青少年犯罪的法律規章是否該檢討等等，小說適切地用個人的自白故事點出當今教育出了問題的因果所在。</p><p>全書的結局極具爭議，是「考驗大家的倫理觀和正義感」（本書日文版編輯平野優佳的話），《讀賣新聞》報導說很多人就是因為想跟別人討論一下這個結尾，而向身邊的人推薦此書。</p>', '< p > selling 670000 copies Japan < / p > < p > the winning record < / p > < p > to end in 2009, the house is great reward of 1 < / p > < p > u back 29 novel reasoning newcomer \"< / p > < p > u weekly bunshun MysteryBest10\" 2008 \"first place < / p > < p > u island club\" in 2009, the reasoning novel really fierce!\" 4 < / p > < p > when ethical differences and justice, you should choose which side? < / p > < p > the killers and psychological evolution of the avengers, take turns to hit our inner moral dimension < / p > < p > a middle school teacher in the school swimming pool found his four-year-old daughter accidentally drowned, by her private inquiry, later turned out to be the murder of two students in our class, but motive was absurd. The loss of her daughter\'s teacher\'s resignation, does not apply to the police to investigate, but on the day of the honors day to the class students to tell the truth, and revealed her revenge, fear factor in students\' heart... < / p > < p > the author use \"crime and punishment\" reverse reasoning technique education and campus crime to psychological analysis of the new generation, each chapter by the victims\' relatives, the suspect students, their families and female classmate subjective perspective respectively confessions, step by step close to the core of the crime motive, take this and put forward many important problems, such as parent-child relationship between teachers and students how to communicate effectively, campus crime law and moral punishment below how to take hold, how to get along with suspected problematic students to prevent crime, how to carry out the individualized personality education, juvenile crime is whether the laws and regulations of the review, and so on, novel aptly points with personal confessions of story in today\'s education out of the question of causation. < / p > < p > the book for the end of a controversial, is \"test everyone\'s ethics and sense of justice\" (Japanese book editor hirano is preferred), the yomiuri shimbun reported that a lot of people just because want to discuss with others the end, and recommend the book to the people around. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787121139512', '浪潮之巅', 'images/浪潮之巅.jpg', '电子工业出版社', '经济', '41.25', '55', '<p>近一百多年来，总有一些公司很幸运地、有意识或无意识地站在技术革命的浪尖之上。在这十几年间，它们代表着科技的浪潮，直到下一波浪潮的来临。</p><p>从一百年前算起，AT&amp;T公司、IBM公司、苹果公司、英特尔公司、微软公司、思科公司、雅虎公司和Google公司都先后被幸运地推到了浪尖。虽然，它们来自不同的领域，中间有些已经衰落或正在衰落，但是它们都极度辉煌过。本书系统地介绍了这些公司成功的本质原因及科技工业一百多年的发展。</p><p>在极度商业化的今天，科技的进步和商机是分不开的。因此，本书也系统地介绍了影响到科技浪潮的风险投资公司，诸如KPCB和红杉资本，以及百年来为科技捧场的投资银行，例如高盛公司，等等。</p><p>在这些公司兴衰的背后，有着它必然的规律。本书不仅讲述科技工业的历史，更重在揭示它的规律性。</p>', '<p> they skip class, pick up hot chicks and cluster, because they \"don\'t learn later destined to forget those useless knowledge\" and make their own animal instinct gained unprecedented liberation; They know that their future is framed within a category of fixed, so they don\'t worry about his future. \"Everything don\'t have to fight for, I just wait, naturally it was my turn at the age of 18.\" So they are commonly found in real life leaves out of energy, looking for stimulation of desire, self-righteous, haughty, drift with the current precarious state of mind. In the world of \"I\", the king\'s brother is a high mountain, ruo-hai wang is ErChen, in north page is fox, milan is a social butterfly; In the heart of the \"I\", parents are disgusting, the school boring, and with a key to enter into the private or conveniently take not more than ten yuan, is a kind of hobby. Also have a genuine love of the opposite sex, but this kind of romantic feelings eventually devoured by uncontrollable animal desire. </p>', '9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506342490', '小姨多鹤', 'images/小姨多鹤.jpg', '作家出版社', '文学', '21', '28', '<p>二战进入尾声，日本战败投降，大批当年被移民来中国东北企图对中国实施长期殖民统治的普通日本国民被抛弃。十六岁的少女多鹤即为其一，在死难多艰的逃亡中，她依靠机智和对生的本能的渴望逃过了死亡，被装进麻袋论斤卖给了东北某小火车站站长的二儿子张俭作为传宗接代的“工具”。张俭的哥哥据传因为抗日而被日本人杀害，张俭的老婆朱小环因日本鬼子的惊吓导致流产，从此不能生育。国仇家恨的大背景下，日本少女多鹤的介入，使得整个家庭的关系变得暧昧和怪异。</p><p>新中国成立后，日本女人多鹤的身份不仅在张家成为重大的情感和伦理问题，在整个社会主义新中国的民间生活中也成了巨大的政治问题。因为多鹤是张俭欲拒还休、欲罢不能的另一个女人，是生活在朱小环身边的情敌，也是张家三个孩子的生身之母，她的身份和地位成了纠缠张家几十年的头疼事。同时，如何掩盖多鹤的日本人身份也成了张家挥之不去的梦魇。张俭的解决之道是，让多鹤成为朱小环的“妹妹”，孩子们的“小姨”；然后再通过不断的搬迁来遮掩多鹤的日本身份以及畸形的家庭关系。这个奇特的家庭组合在动荡的政治环境和困窘的经济生活中飘摇度日。</p><p>几十年下来，日本人多鹤默默而固执地以“整洁、较真”等品质影响着这个家庭，而朱小环等张家人则以“随遇而安”、“凑合活着”等生活理念改变着多鹤。残酷无奈而又充满吸引力的生活因着他们善良的本性使他们活成了不能分开的一家人。</p>', '< p > enter the end of world war ii, the Japanese surrendered, large quantities of the imposed on China by immigrants to attempt to northeast China ordinary Japanese colonial rule abandoned for a long time. Sixteen-year-old girl more crane is one of, in the dead more difficult escape, she rely on wit and opposite the instinctive desire to escape death, was in his sack sold to the northeast by weight of a little train station master of the second son jian zhang as the reincarnation of the \"tool\". Jian zhang\'s brother reportedly killed by Japanese because of the anti-japanese, jian zhang\'s wife Zhu Xiaohuan abortion caused by Japanese devils terrors, from now on. Cia hate country, against the background of the Japanese girl crane\'s intervention, make whole family relationship became vague and strange. < / p > < p > after the founding of new China, Japanese women more than the identity of the crane not only in the changs to become serious emotional and ethical issues, in the whole socialist new China folk life also became a big political problem. Because many cranes are jian zhang messenger Hugh, fascinating one another woman, is around Zhu Xiaohuan rival in love, life is also the zhangs\' own mother of three children, her identity and status became entangled the zhangs\' decades of headache. At the same time, how to cover up the crane more Japanese identity also became the zhangs\' lingering nightmare. Jian zhang solution is that make more cranes Zhu Xiaohuan \"sister\", the children\'s \"sister\"; And then by constantly move to cover more cranes Japanese identity and family relationships. This strange family combination in the turmoil of the political environment and embarrassing to hold sway in the economic life to live. < / p > < p > for decades, the Japanese cranes more quietly and stubbornly to \"clean, negligence, and other quality affects the family, while zhang family, such Zhu Xiaohuan, such as\" settling \", \"make alive\" life concept more than changing the crane. Cruel helpless and attractive life because of their good nature to make them live a cannot be separated from the family. < / p >', '8.6');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020139927', '失踪的孩子', 'images/失踪的孩子.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '46.5', '62', '<p>“我的整个生命，只是一场为了提升社会地位的低俗斗争。”</p><p>全球畅销近千万册被翻译成40多种语言</p><p>《我的天才女友》《新名字的故事》《离开的，留下的》——</p><p>那不勒斯四部曲NO.4令人欲罢不能的大结局</p><p>穷尽友谊对一个人*极致的塑造</p><p>《失踪的孩子》是“那不勒斯四部曲”的第四部，小说聚焦了莉拉和埃莱娜（“我”）的壮年和晚年，为她们持续了五十多年的友谊划上了一个令人心碎的句号。</p><p>“我”为了爱情和写作，离开丈夫带着两个女儿回到了那不勒斯，不可避免地与莉拉，还有我曾想要逃离的城区再度变得亲密。“我”和莉拉甚至在同一年怀孕、生子，并经历了恐怖残暴的那不勒斯大地震，一切都分崩离析，一切又将被重建。</p><p>“我”在不自觉中卷入莉拉秘密的企图——她希望利用我的名声和写作技巧来对抗城区陈腐而猖獗的恶势力。但在经历了生命*恐怖的打击之后，莉拉选择以一种怪异夸张的方式在城区彻底将自己流放。</p><p>而“我”也将以惊人的韧性和诚实面对写作、爱情、家庭的失败。在经历了多年的自我怀疑之后，“我”决定忤逆（罔顾？）莉拉的告诫，将“我”和她一生的友谊写成一本小说，却招来了深深的背叛……</p>', '< p > \"my whole life, just a fight in order to improve the social status of vulgar.\" < / p > < p > the world\'s bestselling nearly thousands of books have been translated into more than 40 languages < / p > < p > \"my girlfriend genius,\" the story of a new name \"leave, leave\" -- -- < / p > < p > Naples quartet NO. 4 in the obsessive < / p > < p > all the shape of the friendship to a person * acme < / p > < p > \"the missing child\" is \"napoli tetralogy\" fourth, novel focusing the Lila and Elena (\" I \") in the prime of life and old age, for their friendship lasted for more than fifty years on a heartbreaking end. < / p > < p > \"I\" for love and writing, and left her husband with her two daughters back to Naples, inevitably with Lila, and I used to want to escape from the city to become intimate again. \"I\" and Lila even in the same year to be pregnant, have children, and terrorist brutality of Naples earthquake, everything is falling apart, all will be rebuilt. < / p > < p > \"I\" in the unconscious attempt to involved in secret Lila - she wanted to use my reputation and writing skills against city banal, rampant evil forces. But after the life * terrible blow, Lila choice in urban areas in the form of a strange exaggerated exile himself completely. < / p > < p > and \"I\" will also with amazing tenacity and honest in the face of writing, the failure of love, family. After years of self-doubt, \"I\" decision \"(ignore)? Lila warned, \"I\" and \"friendship wrote a novel, her life has brought deep betrayal... < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020056293', '罗杰疑案', 'images/罗杰疑案.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '悬疑', '15.75', '21', '<p>罗杰·艾克罗伊德是个知道得太多的人。</p><p>他知道他爱着的女人毒死了她的第一个丈夫。他知道有人在敲诈她——现在他知道她因服用过量药物而自杀身亡。</p><p>晚班邮件很快就会让他知道那个神秘的敲诈者是谁。但是罗杰没能把信读完就死了——他坐在书房里被人用刀抹脖子……</p>', '< p > Roger Ike Lloyd is a person of knowing too much. < / p > < p > he knew that he loved a woman killed her first husband. He knew someone in blackmail - now he knows she committed suicide due to drug overdose. < / p > < p > evening mail will soon let him know who is the mysterious blackmailer. But Roger didn\'t died after reading the letter, he was sitting in the library people commit suicide with a knife... < / p >', '8.9');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787536053281', '夹边沟记事', 'images/夹边沟记事.jpg', '花城出版社', '纪实', '25.5', '34', '<p>这是一段尘封四十年的历史，当年的幸存者散落在各个角落，没有人问过他们到底发生了什么，当年的死难者早已化为白骨，连他们的后代也不知道埋在何处。幸亏杨显惠这位有良知的作家，不辞辛劳，四处寻访，历经数载，终于揭开了历史的盖子。</p><p>本书是《定西孤儿院纪事》的姊妹篇，被誉为“中国的《古拉格群岛》”。书中所指的夹边沟，为甘肃酒泉一个羁押右派分子的劳改农场，从1957年开始关押的近三千人，至1960年底幸存者已不足一半，是一处充满了苦难、饥饿和死亡的伤痛之地。作者历经数年，大海捞针般搜寻和采访了近百名当事人，并在高度忠于历史事实的基础上，完成了这部极具震撼历的纪实性小说。全书通过近20个故事，对众多受难者命运的来龙去脉进行了深沉的揭示，对绝境中的人性有着十分出色的绘状，更直视了这一历史悲剧的精神本质和深刻教训。</p><p>从2000年春季《上海文学》开始连载《夹边沟记事》至今，时间已经过去了九年。其间天津古籍出版社出过一册《夹边沟记事》，但其内容不全是“夹边沟”，还有几篇作者早期的中短篇小说。后来上海文艺出版社出版了全部的“夹边沟”故事，书名变成了《告别夹边沟》。现在花城出版社要重新出版这本书，且恢复了它的原名。</p>', '< p > this is a period of 40 years of history, concealed survivors of scattered in every corner, no one asked them what happened, already reduced to bones was dead, and doesn\'t even know where buried in their offspring. Fortunately, though the conscientious writer, hard-working, touring around, after several years, finally opened the lid of the history. < / p > < p > this book is the companion piece \"dingxi orphanage chronicle\", known as \"the gulag archipelago\" of China. Referring to clip ditches in the book, for the jiuquan a custody right penal farm, a number of nearly three thousand people since 1957, until the end of 1960 survivors had less than half, is a place full of misery, hunger, and death pain. The author after several years, a search for a needle in a haystack and interviewed hundreds of the parties, and on the basis of highly loyal to the historical facts, completed the extremely ambitious through realistic novels. Encyclopedia by nearly 20 stories, on the fate of many victims deep reveal, to the despair of human nature has a very good painting, more look straight into the spiritual essence of this historical tragedy and profound lessons. < / p > < p > since spring 2000 \"Shanghai literature\" serial \"clip ditches chronicle\" so far, the time has in the past nine years. Ancient books publishing house in tianjin a copies of the ditches to chronicle \", but the content is not all \"ditches\", there are a few author early novellas. Later, Shanghai: Shanghai wenyi press all the \"clip ditches\" story, the title becomes a farewell to clamp the edge \". Huacheng publishing house published the book again now, and back to it\'s original name. < / p >', '9.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787508051000', '非暴力沟通', 'images/非暴力沟通.jpg', '华夏出版社', '社会', '21.75', '29', '<p>作为一个遵纪守法的好人，也许我们从来没有想过和“暴力”扯上关系。不过如果稍微留意一下现实生活中的谈话方式，并且用心体会各种谈话方式给我们的不同感受，我们一定会发现，有些话的确伤人！言语上的职责、嘲讽、否定、说教以及任意打断、拒不回应、随意出口的评价和结论给我们带来的情感和精神上的创伤，甚至比肉体的伤害更加令人痛苦。这些无心或有意的语言暴力让人与人变得冷漠、隔阂、敌视</p>', '< p > as a law-abiding good man, maybe we never thought and \"violence\". But if a little attention to the way the conversation in real life, and feel different way of talking to our feelings, we must find some words really hurt! Words on the responsibility of the preaching, ridicule, negation, and any interrupt, refused to respond, casual export evaluation and conclusion to emotional and mental trauma, even more painful than the harm of the body. These inadvertent or intentional language violence make people become indifferent, estrangement and hostile to < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787500649038', '高效能人士的七个习惯（精华版）', 'images/高效能人士的七个习惯（精华版）.jpg', '中国青年出版社', '励志', '21.75', '29', '<p>史蒂芬・柯维（StephenR.Covey）哈佛大学企业管理硕士，杨百翰大学博士。他是柯维领导中心的创始人，也是富兰克林柯维公司（FranklinCovey）的联合主席，曾协助众多企业、教育单位与政府机关培训领导人才。柯维博士曾被《时代》杂志誉为“人类潜能的导师”，并入选为全美二十五位最有影响力的人物之一。在领导理论，家庭与人际关系，个人管理等领域久负盛名。本书自出书以来，高居美国畅销书排行榜长达七年，在全球七十个国家以二十八种语言发行共超过一亿册。富兰克林柯维公司是为组织和个人提供培训和管理咨询的世界顶尖级公司，与财富（Fortune）500强中80%以上的公司和成千上万个中小型企业以及政府职能部门都有建设性的合作关系。富兰克林柯维公司的服务与产品遍布全球，在全球38个国家设有44个分支机构。关于本书企业领导人都知道：只有每一位员工成为高效能人士，企业才会真正成高效率企业。这本书几乎覆盖所有美国成年人，它是美国成年人中最具影响力的书。一个强大的美国是由每一位高效能的美国人决定的，不能不说与这本书有重要的关系。FrankinCovey富兰克林柯维公司简介当您阅读完《高效能人士的七个习惯》（The7HabitsofHighlyEffectivePeople）这本书后，是否希望获得更多的学习资讯，与更多的职业经理人探讨成功的心得？富兰克林柯维公司的培训《高效能人士的七个习惯》使您更加深入地了解书中的理论，彻底地改变思维模式，从而为您走得成功之路奠定坚实的基础。富兰克林柯维公司擅长于通过使用先进的培训方法和系统、完善的内容帮助个人和组织提高效能，其最著名的课程《高效能人士的七个习惯》就源于史蒂芬・柯维（StephenR.Covey）的同名著作。它所传授的内容不是某种流行时尚或管理技巧，而是经过时间的考验并且能够指导行为的基本原则。通过彻底思维的改变达到行为的改变从而加强了组织内部的管理机制、培养组织内部的共同语言和价值观；在全球每年有七十五万人次参加富兰克林柯维公司的培训，而该公司也因其优异表现连续五年入选中国三大培训公司，并在2000年被《ChinaStaff》（中国人事杂志）评为中国最杰出的培训公司。</p>', '< p > Stephen ・ Covey (StephenR. Covey) master\'s in business administration from the university of harvard, Dr. Brigham young university. He was the founder of the covey leadership center and franklin covey company (FranklinCovey) chairman of the joint, helped many enterprises leadership training, education institutions and the government. Dr Covey had known by time magazine as \"human potential mentor\", was named as one of America\'s 25 most influential people. In leadership theory, family and interpersonal relationship, personal management, and other fields. This book since book, high on the bestseller list for seven years, in seventy countries issued a total of more than one hundred million copies in 28 languages. Franklin covey company is to provide training and management consulting to organizations and individuals of the world\'s top companies, and wealth (Fortune) on the 80 � in the top 500 companies and tens of thousands of small and medium-sized enterprises and government departments have constructive relations of cooperation. Franklin covey company\'s services and products all over the world, has 44 branches in 38 countries around the world. Business leaders know about the book: only every employee to become a highly effective people, enterprises will truly into high efficiency. This book covers nearly all adults in the United States, it is the most influential books in American adults. A powerful the United States is determined by the americans of every effective, have to say is important relationship with the book. FrankinCovey franklin covey company profile when you read \"the seven habits of highly effective people\" (The7HabitsofHighlyEffectivePeople) after this book, if you want to get more learning information, and more professional managers to investigate successful experience? Franklin covey company\'s training \"the seven habits of highly effective people\" make you more in-depth understanding of the theory in the book, thoroughly change the mode of thinking, so as to lay a solid foundation for you go the road to success. Franklin Covey company is good at through the use of advanced training method and system, perfect content to help individuals and organizations to improve efficiency, its most famous, of course \"the seven habits of highly effective people\" comes from Stephen ・ Covey (StephenR. Covey) book of the same name. Its teaching content is not a fashion or management skills, but after the test of time and ability to direct the behavior of the basic principles. Through a thorough thinking changed to behavior to strengthen the management of an organization, cultivate the organization of the common language, and values; Around the world each year, seven hundred and fifty thousand people participate in franklin covey company\'s training, and the company also because of its excellent performance for five consecutive years in China\'s big three training company, and in 2000 by the ChinaStaff personnel magazine (China) rated as China\'s most outstanding training company. < / p >', '8.2');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108041531', '邓小平时代', 'images/邓小平时代.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '历史', '66', '88', '<p>邓小平深刻影响了中国历史和世界历史的走向，也改变了每一当代中国人的命运。解读邓小平的政治生涯及其行为逻辑，就是解读当代中国，解读个人命运背后的历史变局。</p><p>哈佛大学傅高义教授倾十年心力完成的权威巨著《邓小平时代》，是对邓小平跌宕起伏的一生以及中国惊险崎岖的改革开放之路的全景式描述。作者对邓小平个人性格及执政风格进行了深层分析，并对中国改革开放史进行了完整而独到的阐释。书中涵盖丰富的中外档案资料和研究成果，以及为数众多的作者独家访谈。对中美建交、华国锋历史评估、改革开放的幕后曲折、邓小平和诸多当时关键人物之关系、香港问题、邓小平南巡等重大议题均有详述及剖析。本书既具学院研究的严谨专精，又对中国现实政治与事理人情有透彻把握，被誉为邓小平研究“纪念碑式”的著作。</p>', '< p > deng xiaoping profoundly influenced Chinese history and the history of the world, also changed the fate of every modern Chinese. Interpretation of deng xiaoping\'s political career and its behavior logic, that is, a reading of contemporary China, interpreting the history behind the personal fate of change. < / p > < p > harvard professor vogel pour heart ten years to complete the authority of the magnum opus \"deng xiaoping\", is the deng xiaoping\'s ups and downs of life as well as China\'s breathtaking panoramic description of the rough road of the reform and opening to the outside. Author of deng xiaoping\'s personality and leadership style has carried on the deep analysis, and the history of China\'s reform and opening up a complete and original interpretation. The book covers the wealth of the Chinese and foreign documents and research results, and the author of numerous exclusive interview. For the establishment of diplomatic ties between China and America, hua guofeng history evaluation, reform and opening up behind the twists and turns, deng xiaoping and was a key figure in the relationship, the Hong Kong question, deng xiaoping and other major issues are described and analyzed. Book is both rigorous specialization of college study, and on China\'s political reality and things human have a thorough grasp of known as deng xiaoping\'s study of \"monument\". < / p >', '9.1');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787308108584', '观念的水位', 'images/观念的水位.jpg', '浙江大学出版社', '社会', '27', '36', '<p>作为国内公共领域最重要的声音之一，刘瑜的文字向来拥趸众多，之前的作品更多关注美国民主，与中国相关度不高。而本书更多关注东亚、中东欧、南美洲以及非洲国家的政治与民主化，比如英国、俄罗斯、委内瑞拉、赞比亚等，这些国家的民主化进程参差不齐，而很多情况与现今中国有较强的可比性，这无疑让这本书更生动，更接地气。</p><p>喜欢刘瑜文字的人，在本书中仍然可以找到惊喜，她是幽默的：“所谓民主，就是选一个人上去挨骂。”她还是犀利的：“别说什么‘关了灯都一样’，21世纪了，为什么总要关着灯呢。”书中内容，包括、国际时政、政治书评影评以及一些个体化思考的杂论，更为多样化，阅读上带有跳跃感，但并不会有断裂之感，相反，用刘瑜自己的话说：“我相信这些文章集结在一起所传递的信息，相比它们零散的存在，其重量和清晰度是不一样的，而这些信息在今天的中国值得被反复和清晰地传递。”</p><p>一个更好的社会，更好的制度的降临并不是“自动”的，观念的变化是必要环节，而本书最终要达到的目的，就是“将过于霸道的声音拧小，将被屏蔽的声音放大，将司空见惯的思维方式打上一个问号，将盒子里的光释放”，“告诉他人他们不知道自己知道的观念”。</p>', '< p > as one of the most important voice of the public sector, domestic Liu Yu writing has always been a fan of numerous, previous works focus more on American democracy, and China is not high correlation. And book pay more attention to east Asia, central and eastern Europe, South America and Africa\'s political and democratization, such as Britain, Russia, venezuela, Zambia, the democratization process in these countries is uneven, and many of the situation and now China has strong comparability, it certainly make this book more vivid and more ground. < / p > < p > Liu Yu text of the person you like, can be found in this book still surprise, she is humorous: \"the so-called democracy, is to choose a man scolded.\" She was sharp, \"say what \'closed the lamp are all the same, the 21st century, why always closed the lamp.\" Content in the book, including, international politics, political book reviews and some individual thinking ZaLun reviews, more diversified, reading with jerky, but will not has the feeling of fracture, on the contrary, in the words of Liu Yu himself: \"I believe that these essays together\'s message, compared to loose their existence, their weight and clarity is different, and these information in today\'s China deserves to be repeated and clear.\" < / p > < p > a better society, better system, is not \"automatic\" arrival of the change of the idea is a necessary link, finally to achieve the purpose of the book, is \"would be too domineering voice small twist, amplify the voices of blocked, will play on the common way of thinking a question mark, to release light box\", \"to tell others they don\'t know if I know the idea of\". < / p >', '8.3');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787506341110', '云中歌1', 'images/云中歌1.jpg', '作家出版社', '文学', '18.6', '24.8', '<p>西汉时期，八岁的汉昭帝刘弗陵被追逼到万里荒漠，走投无路之际，一个骑着天山雪驼的绿衫女孩云歌凭空降临，将其带出荒漠。冷漠似冰的刘弗陵最终被精灵可爱的云歌打动，互赠礼物后相约十年后的长安相会。十年后，云歌带着儿时的诺言来到长安寻找刘弗陵，无奈此时的刘哥哥不仅不记得儿时的大漠诺言，而且身边还多了个贤惠美丽的女子许平君。伤心的云歌正欲返回西漠，却遇上了难缠的绝世美男孟珏，云歌以为幸福的生活从此开始，谁知又卷入了一场宫廷王位之争……</p>', '< p > the western han dynasty period, eight off of han emperor liu ling pursue to the desert, desperate, a girl riding a tianshan snow TuoDe green unlined upper garment cloud song coming out of thin air, it out of the desert. Cold as ice, liu ling has finally been lovely elf cloud song impress, gifts after meet meet after ten years of changan. Ten years later, the cloud song a childhood promise came to changan for liu ling, liu brother of helpless at this moment not only don\'t remember my childhood desert promise, and beside more than an empress xu pingjun is virtuous and beautiful woman. Sad cloud song is to return to the west desert, but encountered a difficult beautiful beautiful male Meng Jue, cloud song think happy life began, but also involved in a court Wang Weizhi contend for... < / p >', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787108034731', '巨流河', 'images/巨流河.jpg', '生活·读书·新知三联书店', '文学', '29.25', '39', '<p>巨流河，在清代被称为巨流河；哑口海位于台湾南端，是鹅銮鼻灯塔下的一泓湾流。这本书写的是一个并未远去的时代，关于两代人从巨流河到哑口海的故事。那立志将中国建设成现代化国家的父亲，在牧草中哭泣的母亲，公而忘私的先生；唱着《松花江上》的东北流亡学子，初识文学滋味的南开少女，含泪朗诵雪莱和济慈的朱光潜；那盛开铁石芍药的故乡，那波涛滚滚的巨流河，那暮色山风里、隘口边回头探望的少年张大飞……六十年来，作者读书、教书，写评论文章，却一直念念不忘当年事——郭松龄在东北家乡为厚植国力反抗军阀的兵谏；抗战初起，二十九军浴血守卫华北，牺牲之壮烈；南京大屠杀，国都化为鬼蜮的悲痛；保卫大武汉，民心觉醒，誓做决不投降的中国人之慷慨激昂；夺回台儿庄的激励；一步步攀登跋涉湘桂路、川黔路奔往重庆，绝处逢生的盼望；在四川、在滇缅公路上誓死守土的英勇战士的容颜，坚毅如在眼前；那一张张呼喊同胞、凝聚人心的战报、文告、号外，在作者心中仍墨迹未干……作者给我们讲述了一个埋藏着巨大悲伤的时代，同时也是所有中国人引以为荣的，真正存在过的，最有骨气的中国！</p>', '< p > where river, the river in qing dynasty is called rivers; The dumb mouth sea located at the southern tip of Taiwan, is a beacon goose process under a congested the Gulf Stream. This book is an era of not far away, about two generations from where the river to the dumb mouth sea stories. That aspires to build China into a modern country\'s father, mother crying in the grass, Mr Selfless, dedicated; Singing \"in the songhua river\" of the northeast exiled students, first literary taste of nankai, tearful recitation of Shelley and Keats zhu guangqian; The home of the bloom of stone herbaceous peony, the waves roll where the river, and that the wind, go back to visit young Zhang Dafei pass...... 60 years, the author study, teach and write a review article, has been not forget for a moment that year - kuo sung-lin hometown in northeast China to strengthen the national strength against the warlord forced remonstration. At the beginning of the war of resistance against Japan, 29 army fighting guard in north China, heroic sacrifice; The nanjing massacre, countries into quotations grief; Defend the big wuhan, the awakening, shi tub-thumping Chinese do not surrender; Retake the taierhchuang incentive; Climb step by step walk xiang-gui road, sichuan road to chongqing, hope of rescue. In sichuan, on the Burma road between staying to the heroic soldiers, determined as in sight; That fellow shouted, solidarity of the grand, proclamation, extra, in the heart is still the ink is... The author told us a buried era of great sadness, but also all the Chinese people proud of, really exist, most Chinese character! < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787802281127', '来不及说我爱你', 'images/来不及说我爱你.jpg', '新世界出版社', '文学', '15', '20', '<p>已订婚的她，在无意间救下了一个英俊又权倾一方的贵公子，原本以为这只是一场擦肩而过的邂逅，谁知道他居然甘冒奇险，在婚礼上把她抢了过来，而等待他们的却不是王子与灰姑娘走入城堡的童话……</p><p>人这一生能有多少个时刻会爱上一个人，而爱情中最大的悲剧就在于当那句“我爱你”还没来得及说出口的时候，你爱的那个人已消失在人海中。这本由悲情小天后匪我思存演绎的生死之恋波澜起伏、语言凄美，道出了爱情的隐痛，把一份刻骨铭心的爱情留在了世人心中。</p>', '<p> as one of the most important voice of the public sector, domestic Liu Yu writing has always been a fan of numerous, previous works focus more on American democracy, and China is not high correlation. And book pay more attention to east Asia, central and eastern Europe, South America and Africa\'s political and democratization, such as Britain, Russia, venezuela, Zambia, the democratization process in these countries is uneven, and many of the situation and now China has strong comparability, it certainly make this book more vivid and more ground. </p> <p> Liu Yu text of the person you like, can be found in this book still surprise, she is humorous: \"the so-called democracy, is to choose a man scolded.\" She was sharp, \"say what \'closed the lamp are all the same, the 21st century, why always closed the lamp.\" Content in the book, including, international politics, political book reviews and some individual thinking ZaLun reviews, more diversified, reading with jerky, but will not has the feeling of fracture, on the contrary, in the words of Liu Yu himself: \"I believe that these essays together\'s message, compared to loose their existence, their weight and clarity is different, and these information in today\'s China deserves to be repeated and clear.\" </p> <p> a better society, better system, is not \"automatic\" arrival of the change of the idea is a necessary link, finally to achieve the purpose of the book, is \"would be too domineering voice small twist, amplify the voices of blocked, will play on the common way of thinking a question mark, to release light box\", \"to tell others they don\'t know if I know the idea of\". </p>', '8');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787020132003', '离开的，留下的', 'images/离开的，留下的.jpg', '人民文学出版社', '文学', '46.5', '62', '<p>两个女人50年的友谊和战争</p><p>那不勒斯四部曲NO.3</p><p>全球畅销近千万册被翻译成40多种语言</p><p>“我希望她在场，这是我写作的目的。”</p><p>《我的天才女友》《新名字的故事》后续，</p><p>意大利最神秘的作家费兰特（ElenaFerrante）</p><p>探索中年的虚无、困惑、野心和近乎残暴的爱</p><p>《离开的，留下的》是埃莱娜·费兰特的“那不勒斯四部曲”的第三部，聚焦“我”（埃莱娜）和莉拉躁动、紧密相依的中年。</p><p>“我”在未婚夫彼得罗一家人的帮助下，出版了第一本小说，享受着成功的喜悦，而留在那不勒斯的莉拉却身陷贫困而卑贱的工厂生活。“我”像个骑士一样，再度介入莉拉的生活，并动用丈夫一家人的关系，让莉拉和恩佐的生活有了转机——他们成了那不勒斯地区最早学习、掌握计算机技术的人，他们顽强、坚韧的学习能力让他们开始积累了巨大的财富。</p><p>我和莉拉之间再次胜负难辨。婚后的“我”开始面临自己的创作危机，而平静的、中产阶级式的婚姻也令“我”疲惫不堪。对社会变革颇为冷淡的彼得罗希望“我”放弃作家的身份，而“我”在扮演“母亲”、“妻子”这些角色时，总是避免不了内心的分裂、紧张。</p><p>莉拉对“我”的新作品的指责更是让我产生彻底的自我怀疑：我接受的教育和拥有的知识是否只是让我的作品徒有其表，没有真正的思想，也永远无法拥有莉拉近乎粗野的表达中那些令人不安的真相。直到有一天，“我”丈夫突然将尼诺带回了家……</p>', '< p > two women 50 years of friendship and war < / p > < p > Naples quartet NO. 3 < / p > < p > the world\'s bestselling nearly thousands of books have been translated into more than 40 languages < / p > < p > \"I hope she is present, it is the purpose of my writing.\" < / p > < p > \"my girlfriend genius,\" the story of a new name follow-up, < / p > < p > the most mysterious Italian writer fee rand (ElenaFerrante) < / p > < p > explore middle-aged emptiness and confusion, ambitions and almost cruel love < / p > < p > the left, the left is Elena, rand \"napoli tetralogy\" third, focus on \"I\" (Elena) and Lila agitation, closely dependent of the middle-aged. < / p > < p > \"I\" in the fiance Peter take his family\'s help, published the first novel, enjoy the joy of success, and stay in Naples Lila is factory in a poor and humble life. \"I\" like a knight, once again involved in the life of Lila, and use the husband\'s family relations, let Lila and enzo life have change, they become Naples area the first to learn and master the computer technology, their tenacity, perseverance, ability to learn to let them start accumulated great wealth. < / p > < p > I resembles again between la and the outcome. After marriage \"I\" crisis began to face their own creation, and calm, the middle class type marriage also makes me tired. Peter luo hope of social change was cool \"I\" give up the identity of the author, and \"I\" in \"mother\", \"wife,\" the role, can\'t always avoid inner division, tension. < / p > < p > Lila to blame the \"I\" new works but also let me have a thorough self doubt: I accept the knowledge of education and has just let my work eauty, no real thoughts, also never have Sally LaJinHu rough expression in the unsettling truth. Until one day, my husband will suddenly nino home... < / p >', '8.7');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787550025103', '默读', 'images/默读.jpg', '百花洲文艺出版社', '社会', '33.75', '45', '<p>童年，成长经历，家庭背景，社会关系，创伤……</p><p>我们不断追溯与求索犯罪者的动机，探寻其中最幽微的喜怒哀乐，不是为了设身处地地同情、乃至于原谅他们，不是为了给罪行以开脱的理由，不是为了跪服于所谓人性的复杂，不是为了反思社会矛盾，更不是为了把自己也异化成怪物——</p><p>我们只是在给自己、给仍然对这个世界抱有期望的人——寻找一个公正的交代。</p>', '< p > childhood, growing up, family background, social relations, trauma... < / p > < p > we keep back and search for the motivation of offenders, and explore one of the most casual attitudes of joys and sorrows, is not to put themselves in sympathy, and even forgive them, not to give offence to exculpate reason, not to kneel to the so-called human nature is complex, not for the reflection of social contradictions, and more alienation is not to put himself into a monster -- < / p > < p > we\'re just for yourself, to those who still have expectations of the world, looking for a fair. < / p >', '8.4');
INSERT INTO `book_info` VALUES ('9787040406641', '数据库系统概论', 'images/数据库系统概论.jpg', '高等教育出版社', '计算机', '30', '39.6', '《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》第1版于1983年出版，至今已修订至第5版。第5版被列入“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材。相应课程于2004年被评为北京市精品课程，2005年被评为国家精品课程，2014年被批准为国家级精品资源共享课。\r\n\r\n《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》系统全面地阐述了数据库系统的基础理论、基本技术和基本方法。全书分为4篇16章。第一篇基础篇，包括绪论、关系数据库、关系数据库标准语言SQL、数据库安全性和数据库完整性，共5章；第二篇设计与应用开发篇，包括关系数据理论、数据库设计和数据库编程，共3章；第三篇系统篇，包括关系查询处理和查询优化、数据库恢复技术、并发控制和数据库管理系统，共4章；第四篇新技术篇，包括数据库技术发展概述、大数据管理、内存数据库系统和数据仓库与联机分析处理技术，共4章。\r\n\r\n《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》可以作为高等学校计算机类专业、信息管理与信息系统等相关专业数据库课程的教材。也可供从事数据库系统研究、开发和应用的研究人员和工程技术人员参考。\r\n《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》第1版于1983年出版，至今已修订至第5版。第5版被列入“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材。相应课程于2004年被评为北京市精品课程，2005年被评为国家精品课程，2014年被批准为国家级精品资源共享课。\r\n\r\n《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》系统全面地阐述了数据库系统的基础理论、基本技术和基本方法。全书分为4篇16章。第一篇基础篇，包括绪论、关系数据库、关系数据库标准语言SQL、数据库安全性和数据库完整性，共5章；第二篇设计与应用开发篇，包括关系数据理论、数据库设计和数据库编程，共3章；第三篇系统篇，包括关系查询处理和查询优化、数据库恢复技术、并发控制和数据库管理系统，共4章；第四篇新技术篇，包括数据库技术发展概述、大数据管理、内存数据库系统和数据仓库与联机分析处理技术，共4章。\r\n\r\n《数据库系统概论（第5版）“十二五”普通高等教育本科国家级规划教材》可以作为高等学校计算机类专业、信息管理与信息系统等相关专业数据库课程的教材。也可供从事数据库系统研究、开发和应用的研究人员和工程技术人员参考。\r\n\"', 'The first edition of the 12th five-year Plan textbook for undergraduate students in General higher Education was published in 1983 and has been revised to the fifth edition. The fifth edition is included in the National Planning textbook of General higher Education in the 12th five-year Plan. The corresponding course was appraised as Beijing excellent course in 2004, national excellent course in 2005 and national excellent resource sharing course in 2014. Introduction to Database system (5th Edition) the basic Theory, basic Technology and basic methods of Database system are systematically and comprehensively expounded in the 12th five-year Plan textbook for undergraduate students in General higher Education. The book is divided into 4 articles and 16 chapters. The first basic part, including introduction, relational database standard language SQL, database security and database integrity, a total of five chapters; the second part of design and application development, including relational data theory, database design and database programming, a total of three chapters, the third part of the system, including relational query processing and query optimization, database recovery technology, concurrency control and database management system, a total of 4 chapters. The fourth part of new technology, including database technology development overview, big data management, memory database system and data warehouse and online analytical processing technology, a total of four chapters. Introduction to Database system (5th Edition) the textbook of National Planning for undergraduate students in General higher Education in the 12th five-year Plan can be used as a textbook for database courses of computer major, information management and information system in colleges and universities. It can also be used as a reference for researchers and engineers engaged in database system research, development and application.', '9.9');
